Crafted from cotton, the piece is outfitted with front zip fastening and button cuffs and hem tabs that allow for minor alterations. Pockets are incorporated at the chest and sides of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ghost Piece Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Produced in cotton, the Ghost Piece Jacket is a monochromatic outerwear style offered in a versatile beige colorway. It is outfitted with two-way front zip fastening that allows for minor adjustments to styling, in addition to two zippered pockets at the chest. Press stud fastening is incorporated at the cuffs and hem for additional alterations, as the piece is finished with Stone Island's signature removable logo badge on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hidden Pleasures Bomber Jacket Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Hidden Pleasures Bomber is a reversible outerwear style constructed using nylon on the outer and polyester for the lining. On one side you will find a solid gray color, while the other is adorned with all-over, vintage-inspired graphics. Details include front zip fastening and rib knit trims at the collar, cuffs, and hem, with pockets incorporated at the front of the jacket as well as the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Jet Bomber Jacket Deep Depths
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Patta's Jet Bomber pairs a nylon outer with a resin finish for a more technical hand feel and improved water-resistance, alongside 80gsm Primaloft filling that is fast drying and windproof. The garment features a classic bomber shape, detailed with a fold-down collar, two-way front zip fastening, and ribbed cuffs and hem. Pockets are incorporated at the sides and sleeve, as the jacket is decorated with a Velcro Patta patch at the chest, complementary Patta branding at the back, and hand-drawn Tiger Lady artwork at the interior.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: OG Chore Coat Black/Heavy Stone Wash
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A stone washed take on a classic workwear style, this version of the OG Chore Coat is constructed from Norco denim, a robust cotton twill fabric. The outerwear is cut in a loose fit that caters to layering, featuring traditional front button closure and adjustable button cuffs. Four functional pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette, which is finished with a small Carhartt label stitched to the left chest pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Beachcomb Jacket Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Beachcomber is a sophisticated outerwear style predominantly produced in a waxed cotton material. The body is complemented by a contrasting corduroy collar, which matches the faux leather strap patch pockets on the front, the latter of which are accented with gold buckles. The buttons that line the front of the silhouette and are used on the cuffs are detailed with an engraved Thames logo, as the style is then finished with an embroidered crown motif at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Detroit Jacket Black/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt’s Detroit Jacket is as OG as it gets. One of the most beloved styles from the workwear brand, the silhouette is a symbol of hard-wearing design, having been adopted by the working class and fashion elite alike. Durable yet lightweight, the Detroit Jacket is constructed from Carhartt’s signature 12 oz dearborn canvas, which is now made from 100% organic cotton. The canvas fabric gets softer with wear, in turn offering a fit that adapts to you. As with most Carhartt garments, you can easily wear this piece on the job site, in the streets, and anywhere in between.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Risar Jacket Dark Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Risar is a technical outerwear style by Ranra, emerging for year-round wear in a Dark Olive colorway. Predominantly constructed using a non-stretchy nylon fabric, the jacket is outfitted with an adjustable drawcord hood for added protection, two-way front zip fastening that allows for various styling options, and elasticated ribbed cuffs and hem. Slanting zippered pockets are incorporated onto the front of the garment, ultimately serving as the defining design element.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Collared Bomber Petrol
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Collared Bomber is a new standout Martine Rose style featuring the brand's "Expect Perfection" beer towel on the internal lining. Predominantly constructed using a satin faced nylon, the jacket is padded for superior comfort and warmth, while featuring a new fold-down collar. Additional details include ruched sleeves, elasticated ribbed cuffs and hem, and pockets at the front and left sleeve, with a Martine Rose screenprinted signature logo applied to the back of the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Bomber Jacket Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by American college campus style from the 1950s, this Kenzo bomber is detailed with oversized bouclé patches that ultimately define the garment. Further embellishment then emerges by way of a faux fur leopard print collar. The jacket is made from a polyester and nylon blend fabric with polyester fill lining. Additional details include ribbed trims at the cuffs and hem, as well as front flap pockets and a zippered pocket on the sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mini Jacket Dinner Date Check
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Mini Jacket is an elevated take on a familiar outerwear style. Produced in a blended Japanese checked fabric, the garment is then fully lined with viscose and acetate. It is cut for a short, boxy fit and detailed with RiRi two-way zip closure, as well as front jet pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Modular Jacket Lumber/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Modular Jacket is Carhartt’s take on the classic Harrington silhouette, which is a staple in any proper outerwear arsenal. Constructed from 8.8oz poly-cotton twill, the jacket is both lightweight and durable, while being unlined for frequent wear in the warmer months. It is offered here in a neutral colorway, outfitted with front zip closure and adjustable button cuffs and hem for minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Vinz-S Bomber Jacket Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The D-Vinz-S is Diesel's update to the bomber jacket. Predominantly constructed using organic cotton, the outerwear is then cut for a relaxed fit. It features ribbed trims at the collar, cuffs, and hem, all while being outfitted with two-way front zip closure that makes way for various styling options. Welt pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette, which is finished with the brand's oval D logo embroidered onto the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Back Zip Bomber Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This standout Dries van Noten bomber is defined by an extension panel on the back of the silhouette, which is activated by two-way zip fastening. Around front, you will find two-way zip closure and flap pockets with snap button fastening. Striped rib knit trims are implemented at the collar, cuffs, and hem to complete the look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Embroidered Denim Jacket Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made in India from 100% cotton, this standout Bode piece is based on a vintage denim smock circa the 1970s to 1980s. The brand in turn reproduced the defining embroidered detail along the collar, sleeves, pockets, and hem for this elevated workwear silhouette. The garment features a large spread collar, front button fastening with oversized buttons, and two front pockets. In addition to the geometric embroidery, the piece is embellished with a Bode monogram on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Metal Overshirt Sky Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: In true Stone Island fashion, the Nylon Metal Overshirt is characterized by the brand’s distinctive garment-dyeing treatment. The feathery outerwear is crafted using a light, durable, resin-coated fabric composed of mechanically spun nylon. Featuring two-way center zip closure, the water- and wind-resistant overshirt is outfitted with a single chest pocket with zip fastening.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hooded Nylon Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like many other styles from the brand, this Stone Island jacket is designed to perform. Predominantly constructed from a durable nylon fabric, the garment features an internal wind- and water-resistant membrane that is also considerably breathable. An adjustable hood offers added protection against the elements, while the cuffs and hem are also outfitted with adjustable components for further coverage. The piece is finished with the brand's signature removable logo badge incorporated onto the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Metal Hooded Jacket Dark Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like many Stone Island garments, the Nylon Metal Hooded Jacket is designed to perform. Predominantly constructed from a durable nylon fabric, the outerwear style is wind- and water-resistant to help withstand the elements. The jacket boasts a metallic sheen and crinkle finish, all while being branded with the label's signature removable logo badge, which is applied to the left sleeve. Additional design details include a drawstring hood, two-way front zip fastening, an elasticated hem, raglan sleeves with ribbed cuffs, and front zip pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon-TC Jacket Natural Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Nylon-TC Jacket is a lightweight Stone Island outerwear style executed in a blend of nylon and linen materials. It arrives in a light-colored beige look, with a two-button collar, two-way front zip closure, and button cuffs and hem tabs. Hand pockets are incorporated onto the front of the garment, which is finished with the brand's signature removable logo badge at the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Real Down Jacket Dark Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: It doesn’t get any more convenient than a packable jacket. This signature style from Stone Island is produced in a lightweight recycled nylon that boasts a shiny finish for a more distinctive look. Duck down padding is used on the interior to ensure superior comfort, as the outerwear is outfitted with a standing collar edged in elasticized tape, as well as elasticized cuffs and hem for added protection. The jacket, which folds down and packs into an inner pocket, is then finished with the brand’s trademark logo badge featured on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Regenerated Denim Moonogram Working Jacket Medium Dark Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Regenerated from nine pairs of jeans, the Moonogram Working Jacket showcases Marine Serre’s trademark moon logo in a repeat pattern at the shoulders and sleeves. The outerwear style is cut for a regular fit from 100% cotton and outfitted with a straight point collar, front zip fastening, and elasticated cuffs and hem for comfort. Multiple pockets are incorporated throughout the silhouette to increase functionality.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crinkle Nylon Coat Dove Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Stone Island coat is constructed from a lightweight yet durable nylon fabric. It is made with concealed front zip and snap button fastening for a more streamlined look, while also featuring a a classic collar and a rear vent with snap closure. Pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, which is finished with the label's signature removable logo badge on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Real Down Vest Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This signature style from Stone Island is produced in a lightweight recycled nylon that boasts a shiny finish for a more distinctive look. Duck down padding is used on the interior to ensure superior comfort, as the outerwear is outfitted with a standing collar edged in elasticized tape, as well as elasticized armholes and hem for added protection. The vest is then finished with the brand’s trademark logo badge featured at the chest.

Pockets are incorporated at the waist and chest to provide you with space for carrying small essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twisted Denim Jacket Light Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A playful update to the classic denim jacket, this JW Anderson style is defined by a twisted silhouette. The garment is made from a non-stretch cotton denim fabric with a faded finish, while also featuring contrasting stitching and logo-engraved hardware. Additional iconography emerges on the front and back of the silhouette where you will find a leather logo patch as well as logo embroidery.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rib Debardeur Smoky Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Lemaire has updated the classic tank top, offering the style in an enticing Smoky Green colorway for the new season. It is made from a midweight jersey that is knitted into a flexible rib with a textured quality. The fitted silhouette features a straight cut, with a scoop neck and twin needle stitching at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Touchstone Tracker Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An elevated take on the classic track top, the Touchstone is expertly crafted from a soft velvet fabric. It is defined by a preppy all-over pattern and further embellished with complementary Thames iconography at the chest. Additional details include a stand collar and front zip fastening, as the garment is cut for a comfortable, relaxed fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Shrunken Track Jacket Black/Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Martine Rose's pieces often incorporate an element of sportswear into the mix and the Shrunken Track Jacket is the perfect example of the designer's prowess. Crafted from warped knit polyester, the top is detailed with seasonal prints, a funnel neck collar, and features contrasting piping down the spacious sleeves. The track jacket is finished with a zip closure as well as an embroidered logo on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Detroit Jacket Hamilton Brown/ Tobacco/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt WIP's Detroit Jacket is as OG as it gets. The garment is rinsed to create a softer feel without compromising durability. Cotton poplin lines the body of the silhouette and nylon lines the sleeves, while cinching rib knit cuffs and hem offer added insulation. The jacket is finished with a front kangaroo pocket that is branded with a small woven logo label.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vermont Bomber Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Vermont is a cropped bomber style by Dries van Noten, arriving in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear. It is crafted from a nylon and wool blend on the outer, with cotton and viscose lining. Two-way front zip closure makes way for various styling options, as the jacket is detailed with ribbed trims at the collar and cuffs, as well as a trio of zippered pockets on the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Marge-S Jacket Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The D-Marge-S is Diesel's biker-inspired take on a denim jacket. Crafted from a cotton-hemp blend fabric with cotton lining, the outerwear style is washed to create a distinctive appearance. It features a band collar, two-way front zip closure that makes way for various styling options, and zippered cuffs. Pockets are incorporated at the sides to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Poly Smooth Track Jacket Ivy Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple piece from the brand's seasonal offerings, Needles' Track Jacket is defined by its stretchy and breathable silhouette. The athleisure style is detailed with taping along the sleeves and body and features a two-way zip closure, front zip pockets, and the brand's papillon logo embroidered on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Poly Smooth Track Jacket Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple piece from the brand's seasonal offerings, Needles' Track Jacket is defined by its stretchy and breathable silhouette. The athleisure style is detailed with taping along the sleeves and body and features a two-way zip closure, front zip pockets, and the brand's papillon logo embroidered on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cavalry Twill Sport Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ideal for transitional weather, this Needles Sports Jacket is crafted with a durable twill weave that compliments its straightforward design. Lightweight and breathable, the jacket is cut in a regular fit with a partially elasticated waistband and features an embroidered logo on the chest, a two-way zip closure, and front zip pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Stadium Jacket Olive Drab
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Stadium Jacket is a vintage-inspired design by Nigo and Human Made, arriving for the season in an inviting Olive Drab colorway. Predominantly constructed from wool and lined and padded in polyester, the sporty outerwear style features front snap button closure and rib knit trims at the cuffs. Hand pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette, which is branded with logo detailing at the left chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wool Blended Boa Fleece Work Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Human Made Work Jacket is a cozy style produced in a polyester-wool blend fabric with polyester lining. A comfortable take on a classic silhouette, the outerwear is fit with front button closure, button cuffs, and adjustable button tabs at the hem. Flap pockets emerge on the front of the silhouette, which is embellished with large logo detailing on the back to complete the look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Paxon Bomber Black/Stone Washed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This version of the Paxon Bomber is made using two of Carhartt WIP's signature fabrics, Maitland denim and Dearborn canvas, all while being stone-washed to create a softer feel and distinctive, worn-in appearance. The garment is then lined with cotton poplin diamond-quilting in the body and nylon in the sleeves. Triple-stitched details enhance overall durability, as the jacket incorporates side welt pockets as well as an interior chest pocket. Carhartt's script logo is embroidered at the chest to subtly brand the piece.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Denim Sports Jacket American Classic
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Maison Margiela delivers a luxe, high-fashion take on the classic denim jacket, here offered in a versatile blue colorway with a noticeable distressed effect. Crafted from 100% cotton, the style features traditional design elements including a point collar, front button closure, button cuffs, and adjustable button tabs at the hem, with two chest flap pockets. The fashion house's iconic four stitches moniker is incorporated onto the back of the silhouette to brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Star Cross Quilt Jacket Multi

Featuring a distinctive patchwork design, the cozy outerwear is constructed from a cotton-viscose blend fabric, with full plain woven lining. It features a spread collar and front button closure, in addition to patch pockets on the front and a flap pocket at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Storytime Quilt Jacket Red Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Bode excels in making the most sought-after quilted jackets. This particular style features antique-inspired detailing, animated with an illustrated patchwork technique that closely resembles a blanket. The jacket pairs a cotton outer with polyester fill for added warmth and comfort, while incorporating a point collar and front button closure. Patch pockets then emerge on the front of the silhouette to round out the intricate design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Himalayan Down Parka Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Rugged, visible, and outfitted with a slew of tech features, The North Face’s Himalayan Parka draws from a jacket originally created for mountain rescue teams. This particular style pays homage to the OG, with updated functional elements and a contemporary aesthetic, making it perfect for wear in the streets and on mountain tops. It’s made from nylon and recycled polyester, and filled with recycled down for superior warmth, while featuring a full-length zip, snap button closure, and hook and loop adjustment, as well as a hood attached with snaps for added protection. Large secure pockets allow you to safely carry all your essentials, as the design is made complete with bold The North Face logos on the front and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: MML Puffer Pupil
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The MML Puffer is Entire Studios' contemporary update to a classic outerwear style. Arriving in neutral colorways for effortless matching, the jacket pairs a lightweight polyester outer shell with ethically sourced duck down and feather fill for added warmth and insulation. It features front zip fastening as well as Velcro closure, adjustable hem drawcords, and three compartments. The puffer's cropped fit ensures a standout look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D.N. Coverall Back Sateen Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to a classic work jacket, this Needles style is constructed from a lightweight back satin fabric that is considerably comfortable and has a shirt-like feel. The garment features a fold-down collar, front button fastening, and button cuffs, with a trio of pockets incorporated on the front of the silhouette. The brand's butterfly logo is embroidered onto the chest to playfully brand the piece.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Leather Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A stylish leather jacket is a must in any proper outerwear arsenal. Acne Studios comes through accordingly with a new option predominantly crafted from supple lamb leather with polyester lining and fill. The moto style offers a classic fit and features a snap button collar as well as front zip fastening. Acne Studios iconography is incorporated onto the left shoulder to subtly brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Carduelis Down Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Carduelis Jacket is the ideal alternative for keeping warm during winter without the added bulk from larger puffer jackets. Made with a wind and water-repellent shell, the jacket is insulated with an 800 down/feather fill and is detailed with a quilted construction. The padded collar ensures you'll be protected from any winds and the zip side pockets keep your belongings secure on the go.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Oversized Denim Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An oversized denim jacket will instantly bring an added dimension to your wardrobe. This particular take by Acne Studios arrives in a versatile black wash, constructed from organically grown cotton. Cut for an oversized unisex fit, the jacket is further defined by its extra long sleeves. Additional details include a classic collar, dropped shoulders, front button closure, button cuffs, and button tabs at the hem. Pockets are not only incorporated at the chest but also at the sides for your hands.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Acne Studios outerwear style pairs a nylon-cotton shell with nylon lining and duck down filling for added warmth and insulation. It arrives for the season in a stealthy all-black colorway, outfitted with front zip fastening and snap button cuffs. Zippered pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, while an additional compartment is featured on the interior. The garment is finished with a small Acne Studios logo tag at the seam.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ripstop Padded Jacket Olive Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Acne Studios outerwear style arrives in an enticing Olive Green colorway. It is constructed from lightweight yet durable ripstop cotton and cut for a regular fit at hip length. A fixed hood offers added protection from the elements, while full-zip entry makes way for easy on and off. Additional details include ribbed cuffs and hem, as well as Acne Studios logo embroidery implemented at the front placket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Zip-Up Blouson Marine
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing from classic varsity styles, this Jil Sander blouson is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a cropped fit to ensure a more stylish look. Two-way front zip closure makes way for various styling options, as the outerwear is further detailed with ribbed trims at the collar, cuffs, and hem. Flap pockets with snap button fastening are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, while an additional zippered pocket is featured on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 Down Center Jacket Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Building off the brand's 5.0+ design, this new iteration arrives with a goose-down fill and 2L ripstop shell that boasts a water-resistant membrane. The warm, yet lightweight 5.1 Down Jacket Center is detailed with an asymmetric two-way front zip that runs from the hood to the hem and features zip pockets at the chest, front, and interior.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 DOWN RIGHT JACKET
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Order your regular size.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 Down Right Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Building off the brand's 4.0 design, the 5.1 Down Right is detailed with 180 bartacks and elastane inside the jacket to create irregular wrinkles. Crafted from a custom South Korean 2L fabric with a water-resistant membrane, the jacket features a padded stand collar, front and interior zip pockets, and an adjustable hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 Technical Jacket Center Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The 5.1 Technical Jacket Center by Post Archive Faction combines functionality and aesthetics with its insulated, mesh overlay design. Made using a lightweight nylon ripstop with a water-resistant finish, the jacket is detailed with raglan sleeves and 4 concealed zip pockets at the front with one at the rear. Adjustable drawstrings at the hem and hoodie allow you to style it to your liking, while a main zip closure and partially elasticated cuffs put the finishing touches on this outerwear style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rusta 2.0 Puffer Jacket Khaki Stone/Utility Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An updated take on a classic outerwear style, the Rusta 2.0 Jacket is built to handle winters with ease. Crafted using the brand's durable water-repellent shells, the jacket features 100% recycled insulation that offers the same level of warmth and comfort without the additional weight. The puffer is executed in a neutral colorway and features an adjustable hem, zip closure, and zip pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: List Jacket Sand
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The List is a midweight outerwear style that's characterized by its tonal sand hue and large zip chest pockets. Made in a cropped fit with a durable textile shell and wool-blend fleece lining, the jacket features a high neck with a detachable hood, concealed fastening, and elasticated cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twill Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This casual Acne Studios outerwear style is crafted from a twill cotton blend fabric. It arrives in a versatile black colorway that lends itself to repeat wear, outfitted with ring snap closure. Additional details include a classic point collar and snap cuffs, with two snap pockets incorporated at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Newhaven Jacket Sable/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Newhaven Jacket is an update to a familiar outerwear style, constructed from a polyester-cotton blend fabric with full nylon lining. It is cut for a relaxed fit and features a classic point collar, front zip closure, an elasticated hem, and button cuffs. Hand pockets are incorporated at the sides of the garment, which is then finished with a miniature logo tab at the left pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Field Maple Coat Brown/Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A standout outerwear style, the Field Maple Coat by Bode is defined by intricate embroidery and scalloped detailing throughout. The garment is constructed from 100% cotton and cut for an oversized fit to allow for layering during the colder months of the year. Additional details include a spread collar, raglan sleeves, front button fastening, and two patch pockets incorporated onto the front of the coat.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleece Tie-Up Pullover Caramel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: HIGHArt Mixed Panel Canvas Painter Jacket Off-White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Canvas Painter Jacket utilizes both mid- and heavy-weight cotton drill fabric in a panel construction with a point collar and long sleeves. A reference to classic workwear styles, it also features patch pockets at the chest and body. Embossed logos can be found at the front button closure along with a removable woven HIGHArt flag at the front pocket. Drawing inspiration from a blank canvas, this jacket arrives as part of a larger HIGHArt collection including matching painter pants and limited-edition adidas sneakers.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Super Light Ripstop Down Blouson Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Adept for cold and inclement weather, this puffer jacket by Auralee is made using 15D nylon yarn to craft its ripstop shell. The interior is lined with white duck down that has undergone a re-humidifying process, resulting in a lightweight and fluffy feel. A large padded stand collar ensures you remain protected from strong winds, while two large patch pockets provide ample storage space on the go. Drawstrings at the hem and the adjustable cuffs allow you to modify this outerwear style that's crafted with a wind and water-resistant finish.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Spidi Rider Jacket Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Rider Jacket is a standout KUSIKOHC style made in collaboration with Spidi, an Italian manufacturer of protective and race clothing for motorcycle riders. This version of the garment is predominantly crafted from leather and technical materials, as it showcases contrasting paneled construction. It features zip hardware and a standing collar, with logo lettering implemented at the collar and the front of the jacket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Co-Ted Goggle Down Jacket Ivy Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, this C.P. Company outerwear style is characterized by the brand's signature goggle hood. The jacket is predominantly constructed from a lightweight yet durable nylon material and padded with duck feather for superior warmth and comfort. A garment-dyeing technique creates a more distinctive appearance, as the interior of the garment is then treated with a water and dye-resistant coating. Additional details include front double zip closure, an adjustable hem, and angular zippered hand pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: MA-1 Bomber Steel Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Alpha Industries sees the iconic MA-1 bomber jacket re-designed in a '90s silhouette, custom colorway, and co-branded detailing. The outerwear style arrives with a custom-dyed flight stain and is cut in a boxy, oversized fit with dropped shoulders. The updated bomber comes padded with a tonal lining, tonal matte nylon panels at the underarm, and a thick ribbed hem. Front snap welt pockets and interior button-down pockets provide ample storage space, while the sleeve’s utility pocket is accented with a woven Highsnobiety flag label and flight ribbon. The front zip closure features exposed zipper tape on the outside of the jacket for an alternative take on this enduring silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: MA-1 Bomber Golden Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Alpha Industries sees the iconic MA-1 bomber jacket re-designed in a '90s silhouette, custom colorway, and co-branded detailing. The outerwear style arrives with a custom-dyed flight stain and is cut in a boxy, oversized fit with dropped shoulders. The updated bomber comes padded with a tonal lining, tonal matte nylon panels at the underarm, and a thick ribbed hem. Front snap welt pockets and interior button-down pockets provide ample storage space, while the sleeve’s utility pocket is accented with a woven Highsnobiety flag label and flight ribbon. The front zip closure features exposed zipper tape on the outside of the jacket for an alternative take on this enduring silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: N3B Parka Dusty Olive Drab
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Originally produced in the 1950s for the U.S. military, the N3B Parka isone of two stylesfrom our latest collaboration with Alpha Industries. The updated parka is cut in a boxy, oversized fit with dropped shoulders and is dyed with our custom flight stain. Detailed with a faux mouton-lined hood and a removable faux fur trim, the fully-lined jacket arrives with dual chest and lower welt snap pockets. Branded logos can be found on the interior storm flap and front zip closure, while the underarm panels are accented with tonal matte nylon. A custom Highsnobiety woven flag label sits on the signature sleeve utility pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: N3B Parka Midnight Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Originally produced in the 1950s for the U.S. military, the N3B Parka isone of two stylesfrom our latest collaboration with Alpha Industries. The updated parka is cut in a boxy, oversized fit with dropped shoulders and is dyed with our custom flight stain. Detailed with a faux mouton-lined hood and a removable faux fur trim, the fully lined jacket arrives with dual chest and lower welt snap pockets. Branded logos can be found on the interior storm flap and front zip closure, while the underarm panels are accented with tonal matte nylon. A custom Highsnobiety woven flag label sits on the signature sleeve utility pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Down Puffer Vest Houndstooth
tshirts_and_tops.Description: PUMA and Rhuigi continue their collaboration with this Puffer Vest that serves as an ode to NYC. Cut in a relaxed fit and crafted with a textile shell packed with down-certified fill, this puffer vest is detailed with an allover houndstooth pattern. Appliques on the chest and embroidered graphics on the back compliment the overall design that's finished with front pockets, a roll neck, and a full zip closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Spidi Burn Rider Jacket Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Rider Jacket is a standout KUSIKOHC style made in collaboration with Spidi, an Italian manufacturer of protective and race clothing for motorcycle riders. This version of the garment is predominantly crafted from leather and technical materials, as it showcases contrasting paneled construction. It features zip hardware and a standing collar, with logo lettering implemented at the chest and a graphic print at the back of the jacket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Spidi Rider Jacket Black/Dark Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Rider Jacket is a standout KUSIKOHC style made in collaboration with Spidi, an Italian manufacturer of protective and race clothing for motorcycle riders. This version of the garment is predominantly crafted from leather and technical materials, as it showcases contrasting paneled construction. It features zip hardware and a standing collar, with logo lettering implemented at the collar and the front of the jacket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: ’92 Reversible Nuptse Jacket Sulphur Moss/Coal Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Nuptse is an iconic The North Face outerwear style that’s been around for decades. Designed for mountain and city life alike, this particular variation is reversible and produced in nylon with a durable water-repellent finish for protection against the elements, all while featuring 600 fill recycled down for increased warmth. The jacket is outfitted with center front zip closure, side zip pockets, and a collapsible hood for added coverage. The North Face logos emerge on the front as well as the back to complete the look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Versa Velour Jacket Almond Butter/TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This version of The North Face's Versa Jacket is executed in a super-soft recycled velour fabric, with ripstop overlays at the collar, shoulders, and chest. It is outfitted with two-way front zip closure, as well as a bungee-style drawstring at the hem. Zippered pockets are incorporated at the sides and chest of the silhouette, which is finished with an embroidered TNF logo on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Versa Velour Nuptse Jacket Almond Butter
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Nuptse is an iconic The North Face outerwear style that’s been around for decades. Designed for more casual, lifestyle wear, this particular variation is produced in a super-soft recycled velour fabric, with recycled down and feather fill for increased warmth and comfort. The jacket is outfitted with two-way zip closure, side zip pockets, and a funnel neck for added coverage. The North Face logos emerge on the front as well as the back to complete the look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Versa Velour Nuptse Jacket TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Nuptse is an iconic The North Face outerwear style that’s been around for decades. Designed for more casual, lifestyle wear, this particular variation is produced in a super-soft recycled velour fabric, with recycled down and feather fill for increased warmth and comfort. The jacket is outfitted with two-way zip closure, side zip pockets, and a funnel neck for added coverage. The North Face logos emerge on the front as well as the back to complete the look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Versa Velour Nuptse Jacket Coal Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Nuptse is an iconic The North Face outerwear style that’s been around for decades. Designed for more casual, lifestyle wear, this particular variation is produced in a super-soft recycled velour fabric, with recycled down and feather fill for increased warmth and comfort. The jacket is outfitted with two-way zip closure, side zip pockets, and a funnel neck for added coverage. The North Face logos emerge on the front as well as the back to complete the look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Water-Repellent Quilted Jacket Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This outerwear style is one of several pieces from PUMA and Noah's ongoing partnership and is crafted for inclement weather. Made using a water-repellent nylon shell with a padded lining, the jacket is detailed with a diamond-quilted construction and a point collar. Two front pockets with contrasting ribbing embellish the overall design that's finished with a zip closure, drawstring hem, and embroidered logos above the ribbed cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Modular Jacket Rinsed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Modular Jacket is Carhartt’s take on the classic Harrington silhouette, which is a staple in any proper outerwear arsenal. Constructed from 8.8oz poly-cotton twill, the jacket is both lightweight and durable, while being unlined for frequent wear in the warmer months. It is offered here in a versatile black colorway, outfitted with front zip closure and adjustable button cuffs and hem for minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Stonewashed Canvas Bomber Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Detailed with tonal embroidery, this outerwear style is part of our collaboration with NTS. The jacket features a durable, canvas shell that arrives with a stonewashed texture, quilted lining, and classic collar. Across the back, you’ll find NTS and Highsnobiety graphics designed by artist George Addy embroidered in navy along with a smaller rendition at the chest. A zip closure with front and interior pockets along with elasticated cuffs and hem add the finishing touches to this bomber jacket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Nylon Track Jacket Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Brushed Nylon Track Jacket is part of our collaboration with NTS, the music platform pushing culture forward since 2011. Detailed with a smooth, matte texture, the jacket is crafted from a cotton and nylon blend with embroidered graphics designed by artist George Addy on the sleeve. A co-branded logo at the chest along with a zip closure and stand collar further embellish the look, while two front pockets complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Nylon Track Jacket Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Brushed Nylon Track Jacket is part of our collaboration with NTS, the online radio station and media platform that's been at the forefront of obscure music since 2011. Detailed with a smooth, matte texture, the jacket is crafted from a cotton and nylon blend with embroidered graphics designed by artist George Addy on the sleeve. A co-branded logo at the chest along with a zip closure and stand collar further embellish the look, while two front pockets complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Polyester Down Jacket Olive Gold
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Jil Sander Down Jacket is a collarless style predominantly made from recycled polyester. The regular-fitting garment is water-repellent and padded with goose down as well as goose feather for added warmth and comfort. It is detailed with front button closure and a drawstring waist, while featuring in-seam pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: WRKS Jacket Washed Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fenrir Parka Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our Legacy's Fenrir Parka is an insulated jacket made from recycled polyester and features a water-repellent coating to aid in keeping you dry. Multiple pockets on the exterior and interior provide you with adequate space for carrying valuables and warming hands when the temperature drops. With its oversized, relaxed fit, the Fenrir Parka is sure to keep you nice and cozy no matter the conditions.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Varsity Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This varsity jacket arrives as part of our collection with Pixar, the pioneering animation studio with 18 Academy Award wins. The wool-blend jacket is detailed with a large, chenille patch of Pixar’s Lamp appliqued on the back along with an embroidered logo. Further detailing can be found on both sleeves above the ribbed cuffs with Pixar’s Ball appliqued. An additional chain-stitched logo at the chest adds the finishing touches to this outerwear piece, while interior and front slant pockets provide a space for your belongings.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Zaman Puffer Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: In line with the brand's ethos, the Zaman Puffer Jacket is crafted with a recycled polyester shell and padding in a versatile all-black hue with a semi-matte finish. The jacket is detailed with an asymmetric paneled construction, featuring a diagonal zipper with a debossed logo and a stand collar. Contrasting stitching can be found throughout the outerwear style that's finished with an adjustable hem, front pockets and Gmbh hardware on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Down Puffer Jacket Seal Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Gramicci Down Puffer is equal parts functional and stylish, showcasing a minimal design with inconspicuous branding on the front. It is made using high-density, soft-textured taffeta to ensure long-lasting durability and warmth when you need it most. An elasticized waistband and cuffs increase comfortability, as the classic outerwear style is equipped with two side zip pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Down Jacket Poppy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving in a bright red colorway, the Jil Sander Down Jacket will instantly inject vibrant energy into your winter wardrobe. The boxy style is made from a lightweight recycled nylon ripstop and filled with a blend of polyester, goose down, and goose feather for superior warmth and comfort. Drawstrings are incorporated into the hood and hem to allow for minor adjustments to styling, as the jacket is made complete with hidden zippered pockets on the sides.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Liquid Track Top Grey/Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to a classic outerwear style, the Liquid Track Top showcases a distinctive paneled design. The lightweight jacket is cut for a relaxed fit and detailed with elasticized cuffs and hem. Pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette to complete the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cavaty Jacket Dark Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Cavaty Jacket showcases a distinctive appearance that almost looks as if it's inside-out, as the garment is made from sheer nylon ripstop mesh with overlaying nylon panels. It features a stand-up collar and front zip closure, in addition to raglan sleeves with elastic cuffs and a drawcord hem that makes way for minor adjustments to styling. Pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette by way of vertical in-seal compartments.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Zip Work Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic NEIGHBORHOOD outerwear style, the Zip Work Jacket is crafted for year-round wear and arrives in collaboration with Ballantine's Scotch Whisky and RZA as part of their ongoing creative partnership. The neutral, black jacket features co-branded graphic prints on the back, along with an embroidered patch across the chest bearing both brands’ slogans. Further detailing includes a contrasting Ballantine’s chevron embroidered at the chest pocket, a zip closure, and a woven Pantone patch at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Checked Oversized Down Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This season, Marni plays heavily with checked patterns. The Oversized Down Jacket showcases one of the label's latest designs, arriving in a versatile black colorway. Predominantly constructed from polyester, with lamb leather application, the puffy outerwear style is designed to offer maximum protection and look good while doing it. It features a high neck, two-way front zip closure, and toggle adjusters at the hem for minor alterations to fit and styling. Zippered pockets are then incorporated on the exterior and interior to provide you with a secure place for carrying essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Arlington Coat Black Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt WIP’s Arlington Coat is as classic as it gets. One of the most beloved styles from the workwear brand, the silhouette is a symbol of hard-wearing design. Durable yet midweight, the Detroit Jacket is constructed from Carhartt WIP’s signature 9 oz Marshall canvas with a rinsed finish. The canvas fabric gets softer with wear, in turn offering a fit that adapts to your circumstances.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Padded Hooded Jacket Ivy Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This C.P. Company outerwear style is crafted from a midweight, non-stretch nylon fabric and padded with duck down for increased warmth and comfort. Two-way front zip fastening allows you to make minor alterations to styling, while a drawstring hood helps shelter you from the elements. The waistband and sleeve cuffs are elasticized, as four patch pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette. The piece is then finished with the brand's signature lens detail, which emerges at the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Études Jacket Cotton Check Orange/Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This lightweight Wales Bonner jacket showcases an all-over check pattern. It is constructed from 100% cotton and cut for a classic boxy fit. Details include a point collar, front zip closure, button cuffs, and a straight hem, with a single pocket at the chest. A small logo tag is incorporated into the side seam to minimally brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Down Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Trussardi delivers a new down jacket style for the cold weather season, arriving in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear. It is constructed from nylon with polyester padding and cut for a standard fit. The outerwear features a stand collar with a stowable hood, front zip closure, adjustable Velcro cuff tabs, and pockets incorporated onto the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Full-Zip Wool Melton Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing from bomber styles, this Jil Sander outerwear garment is produced in a wool melton fabric. It arrives in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear, featuring rib knit trims at the collar and cuffs, as well as front full-zip fastening.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Danville Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Danville Jacket is a water-repellent outerwear style made from 100% polyester on the outer, lined with nylon taffeta, and filled with feather down for added warmth. It features concealed fastening and elasticated cuffs, with hand pockets incorporated onto the front of the silhouette. A script Carhartt logo is implemented at the chest to subtly brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Valko Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Valko is a cold weather layering piece by Dries van Noten, arriving for the season in a versatile black colorway. This particular iteration is constructed from soft wool and features a classic point collar as well as front button closure. Flap button pockets are incorporated at the chest to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Single-Breasted Coat Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A wool coat is a cold weather essential, particularly one that is versatile enough to wear with any outfit. This seasonal style from Acne Studios arrives in a black colorway that caters to effortless matching. Featuring a wool shell that boasts a soft, rich handfeel, the single-breasted coat is lined in a polyester blend. It is detailed with a notched collar and three-button closure, while being outfitted with two cozy hand pockets to offer reprieve from the cold.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Owen Zip-Up Jacket Weimaraner Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Owen draws workwear inspiration, being crafted from a sturdy cotton canvas material, with a contrasting corduroy collar. It is cut for a relaxed fit and features two-way front zip closure, button cuffs, and hand pockets at the sides. Available in a neutral grey colorway, you can easily dress the jacket up or down from season to season.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Alain Cashmere Blouson Weimaraner Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Alain Cashmere Blouson arrives this season in a neutral Weimaraner Grey colorway that encourages repeat wear. The unlined garment is made from 100% Italian cashmere and features a saddle shoulder and two-way front zip closure for various styling options. Additional details include an elasticated hem and a slit pocket at each side.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Polar Coat Murkey Clay
tshirts_and_tops.Description: With a long profile produced in a technical polyester weave, the Polar Coat is Our Legacy's take on the outerwear style that features a single back vent and flapped jet pockets. The coat is detailed with a faux fur lining and collar that appears at the cuffs, hem, and storm flap closure with mother-of-pearl buttons.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J115-GT Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Engineered with an asymmetrical design, Acronym's J115-GT Jacket is crafted for all outdoor excursions. The hardwearing outerwear style utilizes a new 3-layer GORE-TEX Pro shell, the lightest laminate ever offered by the brand, that provides a robust wind and waterproof finish that excels in breathability. Cut in a parka-like fit, the jacket features multiple closures at the collar with a removable Sound ForceLock velcro tab to attach your earbuds, a removable storm hood, and the brand's signature TensionZip dump pockets with 3L taping for increased protection against the elements. Further detailing includes an Auxiliary Zip subsystem for modular design with a removable color-blocked sleeve that can be swapped for a retroreflective one to increase visibility in low-light settings. A ZipSling subsystem allows you to transform the jacket on the go, while the EscapeZip is employed for easy on/off access.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J110TS-GT Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Executed in a stealthy all-black colorway that juxtaposed with retroreflective graphics at the rear, Acronym's J110TS-GT can do it all. The outwear style employs an updated 3-layer Gore-Tex Pro fabric that's more lightweight and hardwearing than previous versions to offer wind and waterproof protection. Acronym's ForceLock and ZipSling subsystems allow you to store your earbuds and convert the jacket into a carry sling on the go, while a two-way zip closure, removable logo tape, and 4 external pockets add the finishing touches to this utilitarian jacket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: High Loft Fleece Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made using high loft Polartec fleece, this And Wander jacket is designed to keep you warm whether you’re out on the trails or downtown in the city. It features reflector prints and stitches for nighttime visibility, with zip pockets at the sides and chest for securely carrying small essentials. A drawcord is incorporated into the hem of the garment to allow for minor adjustments to the fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Diamond Stitch Down Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Diamond Stitch Down Jacket is made using Pertex Quantum, an ultra-thin nylon that is lightweight, water-repellent, and has excellent tear resistance and seam strength. The interior of the garment is then padded with goose down feather for superior warmth and comfort when you need it most. Additional details include a high neck with a classic hood, elasticated cuffs, and side zip hand pockets. Reflector prints are implemented to enhance nighttime visibility.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Himalayan Down Parka Pine Needle/Summit Needle
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Rugged, visible, and outfitted with a slew of tech features, The North Face’s Himalayan Parka draws from a jacket originally created for mountain rescue teams. This model pays homage to the original, but with updated utilitarian aspects and a modern aesthetic, making it ideal for wearing on the streets and on mountain summits. It's composed of nylon and recycled polyester and filled with recycled down for warmth, with a full-length zip, snap button fastening, hook and loop adjustment, and a hood fastened with snaps for further protection. Large secure pockets let you carry all of your belongings safely, and the design is finished with prominent The North Face branding on the front and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Draper Liner Tamarind
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Draper Liner is here to make your cold weather season a walk in the park. Constructed from heavyweight polyester fleece with a mesh lining, the jacket arrives with two zip pockets, a stand collar, and zip closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double-Breasted Trench Coat Black/Washed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This season, Maison Margiela comes through with an elevated take on an outerwear staple. The high-fashion trench coat is made from a cotton-nylon blend fabric, with double-breasted detailing. It features a notched collar, a belted waist and cuffs, and a central back vent. Pockets are incorporated at the sides of the silhouette, as the piece is finished with the iconic Margiela four stitches moniker on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Godor Hooded Jacket Sand
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Godor is a midweight outerwear style featuring a distinctive color-blocked design. Made from 100% cotton, the jacket features a high neck with a slouchy hood, concealed fastening, and ribbed cuffs and hem. Two flap pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: La Doudoune Cocon Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: La Doudoune Cocon is a contemporary update to the classic puffer jacket. Predominantly constructed from water-repellent nylon with a wadded interior, the stealthy outerwear style features an asymmetric stand-up collar, front zip closure with snap button placket, elasticated cuffs, and a drawstring hem. Welt pockets with snap buttons are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, which is finished with a grosgrain logo ribbon on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Work Varsity Bomber Deep Hamilton Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt WIP's Work Varsity Bomber is constructed from a heavyweight blend of polyester and wool fabrics. It arrives this season in the brand's signature Deep Hamilton Brown colorway, with front button closure and rib knit trims at the collar, cuffs, and hem. Welt pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette, as the piece is embellished with graphic embroidery on the front and the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Saikuru Jacket TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Saikuru combines heritage-inspired design with recycled fabrics. Predominantly crafted using recycled polyester, the functional garment harnesses Heatseeker Eco synthetic insulation for lightweight warmth and WindWall technology to reduce the effects of wind chill and provide flexibility and breathability. Designed for outdoor use and casual wear alike, the jacket is then detailed with an oversized collar, elasticated cuffs and hem, and secure-zip pockets, with logo embellishments on the front and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rusta 2.0 Puffer Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An updated take on the classic outerwear style, the Rusta 2.0 Jacket is built to handle winters with ease.  Crafted using the brand's durable water-repellent shells, the jacket features 100% recycled insulation that offers the same level of warmth and comfort without the additional weight. The puffer jacket is finished in an all-black colorway and features an adjustable hem, zip closure, and zip pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Salt Zip Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Bonsai's Salt Zip Jacket draws immediate attention with a distinctive all-over graphic. Constructed from terry cloth, the eye-catching outerwear style is outfitted with a stand collar, front zip closure, and elasticized cuffs and hem. It is cut for an oversized fit to allow for layering during the cold weather months.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Varsity Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: For our fourth collaboration with BAPE, we teamed up with the pioneering brand on a range of elevated essentials in three distinct hues. The Nylon Varsity Jacket is a classic outerwear style in a monochrome colorway with striped, tonal hues at the collar, hem, and cuffs. An appliqué STA can be found on the chest along with a co-branded logo at the rear, both detailed with intricate edge stitching. The jacket is finished with a button closure, front welt pockets, and a woven brand tag above the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Varsity Jacket Ivory
tshirts_and_tops.Description: For our fourth collaboration with BAPE, we teamed up with the pioneering brand on a range of elevated essentials in three distinct hues. The Nylon Varsity Jacket is a classic outerwear style in a monochrome colorway with striped, tonal hues at the collar, hem, and cuffs. An appliqué STA can be found on the chest along with a co-branded logo at the rear, both detailed with intricate edge stitching. The jacket is finished with a button closure, front welt pockets, and a woven brand tag above the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Softshell Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: ROA's Softshell Jacket is a hybrid design that's ideal for layering and transitional weather. The jacket is detailed with contrasting tape at the seams for additional water resistance and features a fleece lining to ensure your core remains warm. Organically shaped sleeves are employed for overall comfort, while a high collar with a two-way zip closure works to protect you against the elements. The outerwear style is finished with slanted front pockets for easy access, an additional sleeve pocket, and adjustable drawstrings at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hug Me Thight Fleece Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carne Bollente's Hug Me Thight Fleece Jacket is decorated with a playful all-over print. Like all styles from the brand, the garment is characterized by the sex-positive artwork, encouraging people to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The fleece outerwear style combines an organic cotton outer with polyester lining, as it is detailed with full-zip closure, a stand collar, and side welt pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Fleece Jacket Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: And Wander's Light Fleece Jacket is made from a soft polyester blend fabric. It features a stand collar with full-zip fastening, elasticated cuffs, and a zippered pocket at the left chest. Small hits of reflective branding are incorporated on the front and back of the silhouette to aid in nighttime visibility.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Water-Repellent Light Coat Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Light Coat is a technical take on a classic outerwear style. Constructed from matte nylon, the garment is then subjected to a durable water-repellent finish for wear in inclement weather conditions. It features traditional front button closure, adjustable cuff tabs, and flap pockets incorporated onto the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reverse Piping Insulated Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Constructed from a densely woven poplin blend fabric, the Reverse Piping Insulated Jacket is characterized by its smooth, vintage texture and reverse piping. The jacket features a water-repellent finish that is enhanced by the internal butt stitching along the seams and arrives with a contrasting quilted lining. Further detailing includes a snap closure with metal hardware, elasticated cuffs, and a traditional spread collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Insulated Eco-Poly Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Eco-Poly Jacket is an updated take on the classic coach jacket that features a water-repellent finish. The jacket arrives with a light layer of insulation and is detailed with customary design elements like a spread collar, adjustable cuffs, front pockets, and a snap button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Insulated Eco-Poly Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Eco-Poly Jacket is an updated take on the classic coach jacket that features a water-repellent finish. The jacket arrives with a light layer of insulation and is detailed with customary design elements like a spread collar, adjustable cuffs, front pockets, and a snap button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Insulated Eco-Poly Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Eco-Poly Jacket is an updated take on the classic coach jacket that features a water-repellent finish. The jacket arrives with a light layer of insulation and is detailed with customary design elements like a spread collar, adjustable cuffs, front pockets, and a snap button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Insulated Eco-Poly Trench Coat Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Eco-Poly Trench Coat is a full-length outerwear style that features a water-repellent finish. The fully lined coat arrives with a storm flap closure with a hidden zipper that ends halfway at the chest. Further detailing includes both internal and external pockets, metal hardware, and a traditional spread collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Insulated Eco-Poly Trench Coat Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Eco-Poly Trench Coat is a full-length outerwear style that features a water-repellent finish. The fully lined coat arrives with a storm flap closure with a hidden zipper that ends halfway at the chest. Further detailing includes both internal and external pockets, metal hardware, and a traditional spread collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reverse Piping Insulated Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Constructed from a densely woven poplin blend fabric, the Reverse Piping Insulated Jacket is characterized by its smooth, vintage texture and reverse piping. The jacket features a water-repellent finish that is enhanced by the internal butt stitching along the seams and arrives with a contrasting quilted lining. Further detailing includes a snap closure with metal hardware, elasticated cuffs, and a traditional spread collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: GORE-TEX Mountain Jacket Denim Blue/TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Blending mountain technologies with urban style, this TNF jacket offers superior waterproof and windproof protection. It is made using sealed-stitched GORE-TEX to keep you warm and dry no matter the conditions. Adjustments can be made by way of the drawstring hood, hook and loop cuffs, and drawstring hem, while zippered pockets provide you with a secure space to carry essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Himalayan Down Parka Coal Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Rugged, visible, and outfitted with a slew of tech features, The North Face’s Himalayan Parka draws from a jacket originally created for mountain rescue teams. This model pays homage to the original, but with updated utilitarian aspects and a modern aesthetic, making it ideal for wearing on the streets and on mountain summits. It's composed of nylon and recycled polyester and filled with recycled down for warmth with a full-length zip, snap button fastening, hook and loop adjustment, and a hood fastened with snaps for further protection. Large secure pockets let you carry all of your belongings safely, and the design is finished with prominent The North Face branding on the front and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ercan Fleece Jacket Black/Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Ercan is a cozy fleece style made from a wool and recycled nylon blend fabric. Cut true to size, the jacket features a funnel neck and front zip closure, while being subtly branded with contrasting GmbH iconography at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Shearling Collar Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Acne Studios bomber is made from a technical plain weave fabric with a semi-shiny surface. It is defined by a detachable wool-blend shearling collar, while also featuring front zip closure, ribbed trims, and side welt pockets. The garment is cut for a relaxed fit at hip length.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Shearling Collar Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Acne Studios bomber is made from a technical plain weave fabric with a semi-shiny surface. It is defined by a detachable wool-blend shearling collar, while also featuring front zip closure, ribbed trims, and side welt pockets. The garment is cut for a relaxed fit at hip length.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Contrast Zip Front Blouson Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Contrast Zip Front Blouson is a versatile outerwear style that can easily be dressed up or down to adhere to most any occasion. Made from nylon, the jacket is then lined in polyester and features a high rib knit collar. The signature J.W. Anderson zipper puller is attached to the front fastening, as complementary iconography emerges at the chest and back neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Signature Denim Jacket Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Signature Denim Jacket arrives this season in a classic indigo colorway, defined by a custom sound-wave print that is laser etched into the fabric. To complement, the iconic smiley face is also printed onto the garment, which is cut from recycled organic cotton denim. The style is fit with two flap chest pockets with button closure and adjustable buttons at the cuffs and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mini Jacket Hunterbrown Tartan
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Mini Jacket is an elevated take on a familiar outerwear style. Produced in a Scottish BCI cotton fabric with a water-repellent finish, the garment is then fully lined with cupro. It is cut for a short, boxy fit and detailed with RiRi two-way zip closure, as well as front jet pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Haven Jacket Black/Moss Fuzz Wool
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Haven Jacket is a seasonal Our Legacy outerwear style produced in a soft, fuzzy Italian virgin wool and linen blend fabric. Cut for a relaxed, boxy fit, the garment then features a spread collar, wide placket with mother of pearl buttons, and vented side seams. Patch pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ripstop Nylon Metal Down Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Ripstop Nylon Metal Down Jacket arrives as part of Stone Island's latest collection and is your solution for the cold-weather season.  Engineered using the brand's  ECONYL® regenerated yarns in a thick ripstop weave, the bomber jacket is treated with its special anti-drop agent that repels wind and water. The interior of the jacket is lined with down feathers while the exterior exhibits an iridescent, garment-dyed finish. Further detailing includes front flap pockets and button closure, along with ribbed cuffs, hem, and a square collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: David-TC Down Jacket Maroon/Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Stone Island jacket arrives in a seasonal maroon colorway with a contrasting internal gilet for increased warmth and comfort. The exterior layer is crafted with Stone Island's anti-drop agent making it wind-resistant and slightly water-resistant, while the detachable down-filled lining can be worn on its own. Both layers are subjected to the brand's unique dyeing process while the jacket is finished with an array of pockets, a button-up collar, adjustable cuffs, and two-way zip closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Real Down Jacket Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Real Down Jacket is your stylish solution for the harsh winter months, featuring a garment-dyed treatment with the addition of a special PFC-free anti-drop agent. Wind- and water-resistant, the outerwear is capable of handling whatever comes your way, with zippered side pockets that provide you with ample room to carry your everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Leather Jacket Burgundy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from soft sheep skin, this limited edition leather jacket arrives as part of our Neu York collection. The design takes cues from traditional workwear silhouettes and features a button closure, two side slant pockets, and button cuffs. The interior is finished with a satin lining, an internal hang loop, and an internal pocket, while the back of the jacket is detailed with an embroidered Neu York logo.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Jean Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: After opening its first NYC store 30 years ago, A.P.C. and Highsnobiety have teamed up to celebrate the pioneering French brand’s success with a limited-edition denim jacket that arrives with a washed finish and co-branded logos on the chest. The unlined jacket is crafted from Japanese denim and is detailed with an embroidered Big Apple graphic on the back along with two chest and side pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: RefrigiWear Iron-Tuff® Polar Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar is constructed using RefrigiWear’s Iron-Tuff fabric that boasts weather-resistant and anti-tear properties. This durable jacket is embellished with embroidered logos and patches, an array of patch pockets, and arrives with a button and zip closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: RefrigiWear Iron-Tuff® Vest Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar is constructed using RefrigiWear’s Iron-Tuff fabric that boasts weather-resistant and anti-tear properties. This hardwearing vest is detailed with embroidered logos and patches, an array of patch pockets, and arrives with a zip closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rhuigi T7 Summer Jacket Inky Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A part of the latest PUMA x Rhuigi collaboration, the Summer Jacket is a tribute to New York, the city that shapes youth culture like no other. Constructed using a polyester-cotton blend fabric in a jacquard weave, the garment features sporty textures, stripe detailing, and retro branding. Design elements include two-way zip fastening, elasticated cuffs and hem, and two side pockets, with an embroidered logo applied to the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Thjorsar Striped Pullover Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ranra's Thjorsar Pullover is a comfy style produced in a wool-polyester blend fabric with recycled nylon lining. Cut for a relaxed fit, the fleece is adorned with a horizontal stripe pattern, while featuring a funnel neck with half-zip closure. A flap pocket is incorporated at the chest to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wool Bomber Jacket Black/Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This multicolored Missoni bomber will instantly inject vibrant energy into your cold weather wardrobe. Made from soft and insulating virgin wool, the relaxed-fitting jacket showcases a fun stripe pattern, while featuring rib knit trims and two side slip pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Padded Nylon Jacket Olive Night
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary take on the classic down jacket, this C.P. Company outerwear style uses an opaque seven denier nylon outer shell and a finer, uncoated nylon, paired with the direct down injection process to make the garment even softer. It features an adjustable hood and hem to allow for minor alterations to the overall look and fit, while being outfitted with full zip fastening and zippered pockets. The brand’s signature lens detail is incorporated into the sleeve pocket to finish the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Padded Vest Black/White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ideal for chilly days or simply when you need an extra layer, the Padded Vest is an essential wardrobe piece. Crafted entirely from recycled polyester, the full-zip vest arrives with a stand collar to protect you from any harsh winds, along with front zip pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Torrent Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Torrent Jacket by J.L-A.L is made from a bespoke three-layer cotton-nylon blend fabric developed in Italy. Waterproof, the technical outerwear style features distinctive asymmetric zipper construction, with a three-point adjustable hood and Velcro cuff and hem adjusters, all implemented for minor alterations to styling. Zipped pockets are incorporated throughout the silhouette to provide you with space for securely carrying small essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vonac Bis Jacket Anthracite
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Vonac Bis Jacket is an eye-catching Dries van Noten outerwear style showcasing a captivating all-over motif, Produced in a cotton-polyester blend fabric, the relaxed-fitting garment is outfitted with multiple flap pockets on the front and sleeves, while being detailed with adjustable straps at the chest and sleeves.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Puffer Jacket Coffee Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Acne Studios puffer is predominantly made from polyester and nylon, and filled with recycled down and recycled feathers for increased warmth when the weather takes a turn for the worst. A high collar provides you with added protection from the elements, as the front is then outfitted with snap buttons and full-zip fastening. The piece is finished with hand pockets incorporated at the sides and a small Acne Studios logo applied to the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Barcy-T Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The D-Barcy-T is Diesel’s update to the cold weather trucker jacket. It is washed to create a more distinctive appearance and detailed with traditional design elements including front button closure, button cuffs and waist adjusters, and pockets at the chest and sides. The style is fit with a soft ecru teddy collar and finished with a small red D logo embroidered at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Puffer Jacket Jet Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Lemaire puffer is made from a technical cotton blend fabric and cut to an oversized fit. It features a high collar, concealed zip and front button closure, and elasticated cuffs. Pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reversible Nylon Metal Down Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This reversible down jacket from Stone Island is produced in the brand’s patented Nylon Metal material to give it a metallic and iridescent look, following an intricate garment-dyeing process. Duck down padding ensures a comfy wear, as the outerwear is then outfitted with a drawstring hood for protection from the elements. On the sleeve of the reverse side of the jacket, you will find Stone Island lettering in contrasting embroidery. The jacket is made complete with hand pockets on both sides of the silhouette for securely storing small essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment-Dyed Recycled Nylon Down Jacket Navy Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Recycled Nylon Down Jacket is your stylish solution for those harsh winter months, boasting a resin treatment that gives the exterior a standout crinkled look. Wind- and water-resistant, the garment is capable of handling whatever comes your way, while slanting, flap side pockets provide you with ample room to carry your everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3 Layer Taped Nylon Jacket Ruby
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This lightweight jacket is crafted from waterproof 3-layer nylon to keep you comfortable during wet weather. Its practical design includes a waterproof zipper at the front and on two zipped pockets. Reinforced with branded waterproof tape along the inside seams, this jacket is also detailed with adjustable toggles on the neck and bottom of the jacket, allowing you to tailor the fit. The jacket comes with a matchingtote bagandcrossbody bag, available in the latest HS05 collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3-Layer Taped Nylon Jacket Black

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Leather Jacket Blue
