Borrowing its shape from classic workwear styles, the design includes button cuffs and two side slant pockets, while the inside is detailed with a satin lining along with an internal hang loop and pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sierpinski 3-in-1 Vest Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from their love of nature, Moncler and Salehe Bembury have joined forces to create a collection that sees Bembury’s ideology infused with Moncler’s mountaineering heritage. The 3-in-1 vest is a practical two-piece that can be worn both together and separately. The interior features a down-filled vest made from lightweight materials and Moncler’s longue saison lining that protects against water. The utility vest on top is crafted in canvas and equipped with a range of zip and patch pockets to use while you explore the elements.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Impala Jacket Camel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by the past, the Impala Jacket is made from a houndstooth fabric milled in Japan. It features a light quilted lining, with front zip closure, button cuffs, and hand entry welt pockets as well as an interior patch pocket. The style is finished with a hit of embroidery at the left chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: RBI Coat Pupil
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Entire Studios designs, the RBI Coat offers a glimpse into the future of fashion, with a piece characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. A contemporary update to the classic overcoat, the garment features a premium nylon outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill to help increase warmth and comfort. Velcro adjustable sleeve tabs are then incorporated as a way to make minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Grid Vest Pupil
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Grid Vest offers a glimpse into the future of fashion. Like all Entire Studios designs, the piece is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality, featuring a polyester outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. Adjustable hem drawcords are incorporated to allow for minor alterations to the fit so the vest sits just right against the body.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fluffy Overcoat Laurel

Crafted from a bonded 380gsm polyester sherpa, the comfy outerwear is equipped with reinforcement at the sleeves in the form of nylon ripstop elbow patches, while zippered pockets at the waist provide you with a place to securely carry small everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: A-2 Bomber Swamp

Pockets are incorporated at the waist and chest to provide you with space for carrying small essentials.

The piece is finished with reflective TNF logos applied to the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Down Hooded Jacket Navy/Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Missoni's Down Hooded Jacket captivates with an eye-catching ombre effect transitioning from shades of blue to black. The winter outerwear style is predominantly crafted from a padded, non-stretch wool-blend fabric, with down feather filling for added warmth and comfort. Drawstrings are incorporated into the hood and hem to allow for minor adjustments to styling, as the jacket is then finished with a Missoni Sport logo applied to the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Jacket Medium Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Logo Jacket is a high-fashion take on the classic coach jacket. It is crafted from cotton and features a snap button closure, elasticated cuffs, and a straight hem with an integrated drawstring that allows you to make minor adjustments to the look and fit. The lightweight outerwear style is embellished with Jil Sander’s iconic logo implemented across the shoulders around back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sheridan Jacket Faux Shearling Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A cold weather gem, the Sheridan Jacket is designed for wintry conditions. It is made from a faux shearling with a soft hand feel and is fully lined. Two large pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette, which is detailed with a wide lapel and horn buttons. The garment is cut for a relaxed fit to make way for layering.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vorley Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new edition of the Vorley Jacket draws immediate attention with a captivating graphic print. The winter outerwear style is insulated for added warmth, while featuring an adjustable hood and cuffs that allow for minor alterations to styling. Additional details include two-way front zip closure, zip vents at the side seams, and exterior as well as interior pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vorley Jacket Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new edition of the Vorley Jacket draws immediate attention with a captivating graphic print. The winter outerwear style is insulated for added warmth, while featuring an adjustable hood and cuffs that allow for minor alterations to styling. Additional details include two-way front zip closure, zip vents at the side seams, and exterior as well as interior pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rankle Coat Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Rankle Coat is a staple Dries van Noten style, primed and ready to get you through the cold weather season. This particular take is offered in a neutral grey colorway for easy matching, produced in a premium wool and nylon blend fabric. The go-to winter coat is cut in an oversized fit for a more stylish look and comfortable wear, featuring dropped shoulders, front button closure, and side slit pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Packable Rain Jacket Balsam Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Snow Peak products, the Light Packable Rain Jacket is designed to help you reconnect with the outdoors. The high performance outerwear is predominantly produced in recycled polyester, boasting a stretchy, waterproof outer layer that is fully seamed to ensure maximum protection against the elements. A hood as well as heat-trapping cuffs and hem offer added defense in inclement weather, while dual front pockets are also waterproof to keep your essentials nice and dry.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Packable Trench Coat Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: ​​This trench coat arrives as part of Acne Studios’ latest collection in an inviting pink colorway. Detailed with distressed logos across the chest, back, and sleeve, the coat features slant pockets along with a pack-away pocket on the back collar that converts it into a pouch when you’re on the go.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Harter-Heighway Down Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from their love of nature, Moncler and Salehe Bembury have joined forces to create a collection that sees Bembury’s ideology infused with Moncler’s mountaineering heritage. The Harter-Heighway Short Down Jacket is crafted from lightweight nylon and features Moncler’s longue saison lining that protects against water. Along with being down-filled to keep your core warm when the temperature drops, the jacket arrives with a classic collar, flap pockets, and Salehe’s all-over quilted pattern featuring organic shapes that further embellish the overall style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ganga Jacket Coral Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Ganga Jacket from RANRA is a lightweight outerwear style made from a cotton ripstop fabric with contrasting trim. A pullover design, it features a stand collar and raglan sleeves, while being outfitted with side seam pockets, half-zip closure, and a bungee-style drawcord at the hem that allows for minor adjustments to styling and the overall fit. Whether wearing it on its own as a shirt or with another top as a jacket, the Ganga is a versatile piece fit for multi-seasonal use.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Glumur Vest Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Glumur Vest is a multi-seasonal layering piece made from a blend of cotton, linen, and nylon materials. Cut for a standard boxy fit, the garment showcases a distinctive acid wash, all while featuring contrasting black trim. It is designed with front zip closure and an adjustable drawcord hem, with deep bellows pockets implemented at the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: PFD V2 Puffer Mesa
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As Entire Studios garments offer a glimpse into the future of fashion, the SOA Puffer is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. This signature style boasts a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SOA Puffer Wood
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As Entire Studios garments offer a glimpse into the future of fashion, the SOA Puffer is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. This signature style boasts a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Diamond-Quilted Nylon Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This stealthy down jacket is produced in a midweight non-stretch nylon fabric, with polyester padding for increased comfort and warmth. It features distinctive diamond quilting, while being outfitted with two-way zip fastening that allows for minor adjustments to styling. Additional details include a flat pointed collar, curved hem, and side slip pockets, as the silhouette is cut for a loose fit to make way for layering in colder temperatures.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Giubbotto Blue 781541027
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island continues its material research with its SS23 collection. While best known for its unique garment-dyed clothing, the beloved Italian brand also offers versatile staples like this lightweight jacket in a clean matte and satin finish. Crafted from a densely woven nylon that’s suited to withstand wind and water, this jacket arrives featuring a classic collar with side and chest pockets, along with the brand’s trusted badge on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Not in Paris 5 Coach Jacket
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This stonewashed nylon outerwear style is an elevated take on the classic coach jacket, produced in a Japanese oxford nylon fabric that is stonewashed to create a rich and varied texture. Decorated with Paris-themed graphics, the jacket is cut in a slightly boxy fit and is considerably lightweight. This is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Presented at the historic gallery Palais de Tokyo, Il morso delle termiti is an exhibition that re-contextualizes the art of graffiti. This jacket has been created for the exhibition and features Palais de Tokyo’s new logo. The graphic outerwear style is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Alpha Industries MA-1 Bomber Jacket
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This jacket is made in collaboration with École Kourtrajmé, a school founded by award-winning director Ladj Ly to provide opportunities for underrepresented voices in film and image-making. Using Alpha Industries MA-1 jacket, this outerwear style includes a co-branded take on  Ecole Kourtrajme’s logo embroidered on the front and back. The bomber jacket is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Womens Vintage Menlo Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This season, Levi’s issues a re-release of the leather Menlo Jacket, famously worn by Einstein. The updated version is made for women and is crafted from supple bovine leather that's cut in a slim fit. It features front button closure and button cuffs, with adjustable tabs at the hem. Hand pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Triangle Bomber Light Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This lightweight bomber jacket from Winnie is made from a crinkled nylon and cotton blend taffeta. It arrives in an inviting soft blue colorway, outfitted with multiple zip pockets for securely carrying small essentials. Additional details include a spread collar, front zip closure with press stud placket, and ribbed trims at the cuffs and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J119-WS 2L Gore-Tex Infinium Windstopper Interops Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The J119-WS is a utility-inspired take on the classic coach jacket. Built in 2L Gore-Tex Infinium with Windstopper technology, and lined with 4-way stretch mesh, the tech-filled outerwear style performs just as good as it looks. It features two-way zip closure with web tape mounted press buttons for one-handed operation and an additional zipper at the collar that makes way for a full storm hood to unfurl out of it. Pockets are then incorporated onto the exterior as well as the interior to give you maximum storage.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Yasuf Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: We love how unapologetically "Berlin" GmbH is throughout each collection. Benjamin Huseby and Serhat Isik create clothing that blends right into the city's notorious night-life, yet feels fresh enough to wear out on a casual Tuesday.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Coated Cotton Hooded Jacket Cream
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Maison Margiela jacket is a sporty outerwear style produced in coated cotton. A pullover design, it features a relaxed fit with dropped shoulders, while being outfitted with an adjustable drawstring hood and hem that make way for minor alterations to styling. Additional details include button fastening at the hood, button cuffs, and a button kangaroo pocket on the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: PFD V2 Puffer Soot
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As Entire Studios garments offer a glimpse into the future of fashion, the SOA Puffer is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. This signature style boasts a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Giubbotto Black 781540130
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island continues its material research with its SS23 collection. While best known for its unique garment-dyed clothing, the beloved Italian brand also offers versatile staples like this lightweight jacket in a clean matte and satin finish. With over 100 threads per centimeter, the jacket is durable and comes treated with the brand’s PFC-free anti-drop agent, enabling you to maneuver through windy or wet weather with ease.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Giubbotto Ghost Green 7815437F1
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island continues its material research with its SS23 collection, adding to its roster of ghost pieces that take inspiration from camouflage. Crafted from densely woven cotton that’s been treated to be effective against wind and water, the monochrome jacket features patch pockets, adjustable cuffs, and a standard collar that can be worn upwards. Versatile for any occasion, any time of the year, this breathable jacket arrives bearing Stone Island’s Ghost badge on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Distressed Leather Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A moto-inspired leather jacket is a nice addition to any outerwear arsenal. This particular take by Acne Studios is sure to bring an edge to your look, as it is outfitted with functional zips and snap details. Crafted from supple lamb leather with polyester lining, the jacket incorporates circular padding for increased comfort, all while featuring multiple pockets for storing small essentials. The style is finished with a tonal Acne Studios logo subtly implemented on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: LVC 1879 Pleated Blouse Jacket Indigo Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from 100% organic cotton with planet-friendly natural dyes, the 1879 Pleated Blouse Jacket is a Levi’s Vintage Clothing style that draws inspiration from the late 1960s environmental movement which led to the first-ever Earth Day in 1970. The piece is a reproduction of the 1879 blouse, made using the brand’s most premium Japanese woven fabric. It is outfitted with front button closure and features two buttoned flap pockets on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J103-GTV 2.5L Gore-Tex Coat Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A technical take on the classic trench coat, the J103-GTV is tailored to move and layer. The relaxed-fitting style is predominantly crafted from polyester with 2.5L Gore-Tex technology to bring weatherproof properties to the garment. It features two-way zip closure and gusseted zip cuffs for minor adjustments to styling, while being outfitted with Acronym’s patented removable subsystems including ForceLock, JacketSling, and a storm hood. TensionZip front pockets and two interior pockets then provide plenty of space for carrying everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Xploric RAIN.RDY Jacket Shadow Olive/Olive Strata
tshirts_and_tops.Description: adidas Terrex x and wander continues to explore the universal connectivity between humanity and nature, with styles like the Xploric RAIN.RDY Jacket which helps you engage with the great outdoors. Bringing inspired style to mountain-ready weather protection, the outerwear is made using advanced waterproofing to channel rain away from your body so you can stay dry when on the go in inclement weather. Recycled nylon is used to increase overall durability, while reflective adidas Terrex x and wander logo details enhance visibility in low-light conditions.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Banned Houndstooth Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Banned Houndstooth Jacket is a workwear-inspired style produced in 100% polyester on the outer, with quilted lining. In addition to showcasing a houndstooth pattern, the exterior of the garment is further embellished with Noon Goons logo embroidery at the chest. Other features include front zip closure and button cuffs that allow for minor adjustments, and single welt hand pockets as well as an interior patch pocket. The jacket is cut in a boxy fit that is true to size for a timeless look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J95-PL Windstopper PrimaLoft Modular Liner Jacket Raf Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The self-proclaimed perfect coach jacket, Acronym’s J95-PL is defined by the utility expanding DNA of the brand. Made with PrimaLoft insulation and two-layer Gore Windstopper fabric, the style is poised to keep you comfortable and protected in all conditions. EscapeZip and web tape-mounted press buttons make way for easy on and off as well as one-handed operation, while an additional zipper converts the collar for full neck protection. Removable components including ForceLock, JacketSling, and a storm hood enhance overall performance, as the piece is outfitted with spacious pockets for maximum storage.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J1WTS-GT 3L Gore-Tex Pro Interops Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The J1WTS-GT is the physical rendering of Acronym in wearable form. A modular design, the jacket equally prioritizes function and aesthetics, for the first time ever remastered with TEC SYS webbing. The piece is constructed using Gore-Tex’s most breathable fabric technology to minimize moisture and enhance comfort in various conditions, simultaneously offering waterproof and windproof protection. Removable components including ForceLock, JacketSling, and a storm hood increase overall performance, as the style is outfitted with a series of external zip pockets for securely storing all your essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J101-GT 3L Gore-Tex Pro Interops Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The J101-GT is a compact outerwear style outfitted with Acronym’s patented JacketSling for portability, AuxZip for modularity, and EscapeZip for easy on and off. The piece is made using Gore-Tex’s most breathable fabric technology to minimize moisture and enhance comfort in various conditions, simultaneously offering waterproof and windproof protection. Optimized for higher intensity activity, the jacket is right at home in city streets, showcasing a utilitarian aesthetic that Acronym is best known for.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J1WTS-GT 3L Gore-Tex Pro Interops Jacket Raf Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The J1WTS-GT is the physical rendering of Acronym in wearable form. A modular design, the jacket equally prioritizes function and aesthetics, for the first time ever remastered with TEC SYS webbing. The piece is constructed using Gore-Tex’s most breathable fabric technology to minimize moisture and enhance comfort in various conditions, simultaneously offering waterproof and windproof protection. Removable components including ForceLock, JacketSling, and a storm hood increase overall performance, as the style is outfitted with a series of external zip pockets for securely storing all your essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J95-PL Windstopper PrimaLoft Modular Liner Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The self-proclaimed perfect coach jacket, Acronym’s J95-PL is defined by the utility expanding DNA of the brand. Made with PrimaLoft insulation and two-layer Gore Windstopper fabric, the style is poised to keep you comfortable and protected in all conditions. EscapeZip and web tape-mounted press buttons make way for easy on and off as well as one-handed operation, while an additional zipper converts the collar for full neck protection. Removable components including ForceLock, JacketSling, and a storm hood enhance overall performance, as the piece is outfitted with spacious pockets for maximum storage.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Leather Jacket Olive Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted entirely from soft lamb leather, this zip-up jacket arrives with a minimal finish that puts the focus on the fabric. Borrowing its shape from classic workwear styles, the design includes two external patch pockets. On the inside, you will find a satin lining and an internal pocket. Further detailing comes in the form of a debossed zip pull, a subtle branded flag label, and an internal hang loop at the collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J68-GT 3L Gore-Tex Pro Rider Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Redesigned from the ground up, Acronym’s Rider Jacket is now fully seam sealed and guaranteed to keep you dry thanks to 3L Gore-Tex Pro fabric technology. The style is built around the gusset and sleeve to make way for supreme range of motion, as front storm flaps are implemented for multiple styling options. An unorthodox secondary collar zip allows for complete closure when fastened, while removable components including the brand’s ForceLock and JacketSling systems let you customize your look even further. Detached entry lower pockets then provide you with plenty of space for securely storing essentials on a daily basis.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J111TS-CH Micro Twill Tec Sys Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like many Acronym outerwear styles, the J111TS-CH is made with a series of removable parts for added functionality. The garment is also characterized by stripped down, minimalist tailoring, all while being produced in a technical material combination that is water-repellent, moisture-wicking, fast-drying, and highly breathable. Hidden components are kept from view by way of front zip closure that in turn allows for easy access to the internal panel. In addition to the removable ForceLock, JacketSling, and logo tape, the style is outfitted with pockets on the exterior and interior for maximum storage.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vuskin Denim Jacket Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten’s latest collection features a hybrid of unique prints, textures, and androgynous garments that offer a fresh take on contemporary menswear. The Vuskin Denim Jacket is an elevated take on a timeless wardrobe staple, seen here crafted from black denim and overdyed to create a distinctive stain effect that’s synonymous with the Belgian designer’s aesthetics. The loose-fitting jacket comes with two front pockets as well as a front button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Spark-Fsc Hooded Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A standout Diesel style, the D-Spark-Fsc features a fix denim base that is stonewashed, printed, and coated with a shiny resin layer to give it a wet, “jelly” look. Toggled drawstrings are incorporated into the hood, cuffs, and hem to allow for minor adjustments to the relaxed fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Barcy Trucker Jacket Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The D-Barcy is Diesel’s update to the classic trucker jacket. It is bleached and distressed to create a vintage, worn-in look and detailed with traditional design elements including a spread collar, button closure, button cuffs and waist adjusters, and pockets at the chest and sides. The style is finished with a small red D logo embroidered at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: TERREX Xploric Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Winter-ready warmth meets bold creative style with the Xploric Jacket by adidas TERREX. Made in collaboration with and wander, the nature-inspired outerwear piece is designed to encourage you to get outside and explore, while staying warm and cozy in the process. The jacket is made with at least 60% recycled content, pairing a nylon ottoman shell with duck down and feather filling to ensure you remain comfortable no matter the temperature. Innovative pocket design provides safe and secure storage for everyday essentials, all within easy reach.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reversible Vintrospec Parka Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our Legacy’s Vintrospec Parka is a fully reversible design crafted from an Italian technical cotton, polyester, and nylon blend fabric, with a water-repellent coating that helps protect against the elements. The oversized outerwear style is padded with synthetic insulation for increased warmth and comfort, featuring a drawstring hood, waist, and hem for minor adjustments to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3 Layer Nylon Jacket Off-white/Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from a 3-layer nylon fabric, with taped seams and water-tight zippers, this waterproof jacket offers a functional style for wet weather. On the front, two large, zipped pockets provide ample cargo space, in a style typical of mountaineering jackets. Meanwhile, adjustable toggles on the neck and bottom of the jacket allow you to adjust the fit and keep the warmth in.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Drill Chore Jacket Natural
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by the function-first design of workwear, this jacket is a modernized take on the classic chore jacket. Arriving in neutral colors with silver-toned, branded hardware and a boxy fit, it features two large front pockets and a flag label on the left side. The jacket is crafted from hard-wearing, organic drill cotton with matching pants also available.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Drill Chore Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by the function-first design of workwear, this jacket is a modernized take on the classic chore jacket. Arriving in neutral colors with silver-toned, branded hardware and a boxy fit, it features two large front pockets and a flag label on the left side. The jacket is crafted from hard-wearing, organic drill cotton with matching pants also available.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Quilted Jacket Matt Nylon
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This stealthy down jacket is produced in a midweight non-stretch nylon fabric, with polyester padding for increased comfort and warmth. It features distinctive diamond quilting, while being outfitted with two-way zip fastening that allows for minor adjustments to styling. Additional details include a flat pointed collar, curved hem, and side slip pockets, as the silhouette is cut for a loose fit to make way for layering in colder temperatures.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: W-Oval Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Diesel’s take on the classic puffer is cut from ripstop made using organic cotton and recycled polyester. Lined and filled with insulating down, the oversized silhouette is designed to fit loose so you can pile on the layers underneath. The high neck is outfitted with a hidden hood for added protection from the elements, while drawstrings in the cuffs and hem make way for minor alterations to styling. The garment is finished with an oval D branding insert incorporated on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SOA Puffer Atlantic
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As Entire Studios garments offer a glimpse into the future of fashion, the SOA Puffer is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. This signature style boasts a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Beige Coat
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Entire Studios designs, the RBI Coat offers a glimpse into the future of fashion, with a piece characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. A contemporary update to the classic overcoat, the garment features a premium cotton and nylon blend outer shell with an enzyme wash that gives it a more distinctive look. DWR (durable water-repellent) coating makes the RBI suitable for inclement weather conditions, while ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill help to increase warmth and comfort. Velcro adjustable sleeve tabs are then incorporated as a way to make minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pillow Vest Soot
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Primed and ready to turn heads, the Pillow Vest offers a glimpse into the future of fashion. Like all Entire Studios designs, the piece is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality, featuring a peached cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. DWR (durable water-repellent) coating aids in helping you withstand the elements, as side adjuster tabs then allow you to make minor alterations to the fit so the vest sits just right against the body.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Gjof Fleece Jacket Chocolate
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Showcasing an athleisure-inspired aesthetic, the Gjof from RANRA (formerly known as Arnar Már Jónsson) is a contemporary fleece style made with contrasting trim and the designer’s functional raglan sleeves. It is cut in a regular fit with a little extra room through the chest and body, allowing you to layer it as needed come cold weather season. The jacket arrives in a neutral colorway for effortless matching, with center front zip closure, elastic cuffs, and side welt pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Unnar Reversible Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Essentially two jackets in one, the Unnar from RANRA (formerly known as Arnar Már Jónsson) is a fully reversible outerwear style predominantly constructed from cotton. The lightweight garment is RANRA’s elevated take on the classic bomber, made with zip closure and two-button fastening at the neck. It is detailed with insulating elasticated edges and rib knit cuffs, while featuring two zip pockets on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Peysa Hooded Jacket Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Peysa is characterized by RANRA’s (formerly known as Arnar Már Jónsson) trademark athleisure aesthetic, featuring paneled construction from a plush wool blend. Outfitted with a fixed hood for added coverage, the comfy jacket is made with center front zip closure and the designer’s functional raglan sleeves. Rib knit trims are implemented at the cuffs and hem for ease of movement, as the outerwear style is finished with cozy side hand pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Soft Shell Hooded Jacket Sage
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Soft Shell Hooded Jacket is a lightweight outerwear style executed in a three-ply performance material with an 8000 mm water column. The garment’s polyester stretch canvas outer face is woven with yarns using e.dye Waterless Color System technology, an innovative yarn color saturation system, to give it that distinctive Stone Island finish. The fabric is then laminated to a breathable, water- and wind-proof inner membrane, as the inner material structure caters to increased flexibility and comfort.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Kan-D Medium Jacket Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Kan-D Medium Jacket is defined by its quarter button fastening, overlaid with full zip fastening. The style is predominantly constructed using nylon that is garment-dyed to add color depth and intensity throughout, and flattened to make the fabric highly reflective and transparent. An adjustable hood and hem allow you to make minor alterations to the overall look and fit, as the outerwear garment is outfitted with kangaroo pockets as well as the brand’s signature sleeve pocket with lens detailing.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: J107-SS Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: One of the most universal softshells Acronym has ever made, the J107-SS takes design and performance cues from the brand’s functional references including industrial, military, and active sportswear. The technical style prioritizes comfort as well as protection, allowing you to seamlessly transition between inside and outside environments. Predominantly produced in a nylon-polyester blend, the garment incorporates a SpeedLock hem to compartmentalize heat, while underarm vents and mesh-lined venting pockets make way for releasing heat when necessary. It is cut in a fully articulated fit for ease of movement and features JacketSling functionality that allows you to conveniently carry the jacket over your shoulder when not in use.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Contrast Mac Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic piece of outerwear for the fall/winter season, our contrast mac jacket is a new take on a timeless piece. Created by Highsnobiety’s in-house label, it is crafted from a nylon blend fabric which has been reversed to display a matte finish. Contrasting the Beige fabric, white stitching used throughout the jacket accentuates details such as the button cuffs, slanted pockets, and concealed front closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Contrast Mac Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic piece of outerwear for the fall/winter season, our contrast mac jacket is a new take on a timeless piece.  Created by Highsnobiety’s in-house label, it is crafted from a nylon blend fabric which has been reversed to display a matte finish. Contrasting the black fabric, white stitching used throughout the jacket accentuates details such as the button cuffs, slanted pockets, and concealed front closure

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crinkle Nylon Mac Camel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Primed and ready for rainy days around town, the Highsnobiety Mac Coat is produced in a crinkled nylon material that is waterproof to ensure you stay warm and dry amidst the elements. The classic outerwear style is outfitted with concealed closure for a more streamlined aesthetic, featuring slanting hand pockets and button cuffs that allow for minor adjustments. It arrives in easy-to-match colors, in a boxy, oversized fit for a comfy yet stylish look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Detroit Jacket Hamilton Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt’s Detroit Jacket is as OG as it gets. One of the most beloved styles from the workwear brand, the silhouette is a symbol of hard-wearing design, having been adopted by the working class and fashion elite alike. Durable yet lightweight, the Detroit Jacket is constructed from 6.5 oz cotton Columbia ripstop. A blanket-lined body and quilted nylon sleeve lining provide added warmth in extreme environments, while a corduroy top collar adds a touch of stylistic flair. As with most Carhartt garments, you can easily wear this piece on the job site, in the streets, and anywhere in between.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Woven Blouson Mix Madras Check
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Included in Auralee’s latest seasonal collection, the Woven Blouson is produced in a lightweight cotton fabric with patterned texture. The outerwear style showcases a multicolored plaid design that catches the eye, featuring full-zip entry and elastic cuffs and hem, with a drawstring at the bottom band to allow for minor adjustments to the look and fit. Suitable for wear in any season, this Auralee garment is a go-to layering piece that is primed and ready for repeat use.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Trench Coat Dark Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This seasonal outerwear style by Acne Studios is crafted from durable ripstop cotton in a dark olive colorway. The long coat is detailed with a pointed collar, center front buttons, and two side welt pockets. A viscose lining can be found at the back that features woven jacquard logos, while the style is finished with a monochrome embroidered logo at the rear

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SOA Puffer Jacket Rust
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Founded by Dylan Richards and Sebastian Hunt — the creative duo behind YEEZY and the team responsible for the style of numerous high-profile celebrities — Entire Studios delivers a luxury aesthetic that is simple yet thoughtfully designed. Pieces like the SOA Puffer Jacket are characterized by their quality construction and overall functionality, as the brand’s garments ultimately offer a glimpse into the future of fashion. A first-rate puffer is a must for the cold weather season, and you of course want one that not only looks good but also performs just as well. This particular style from Entire Studios checks both boxes, boasting a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SOA Puffer Jacket Soot
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As Entire Studios garments offer a glimpse into the future of fashion, the SOA Puffer is characterized by quality construction and overall functionality. This signature style boasts a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SOA Puffer Jacket Blonde
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Founded by Dylan Richards and Sebastian Hunt — the creative duo behind YEEZY and the team responsible for the style of numerous high-profile celebrities — Entire Studios delivers a luxury aesthetic that is simple yet thoughtfully designed. Pieces like the SOA Puffer Jacket are characterized by their quality construction and overall functionality, as the brand’s garments ultimately offer a glimpse into the future of fashion. A first-rate puffer is a must for the cold weather season, and you of course want one that not only looks good but also performs just as well. This particular style from Entire Studios checks both boxes, boasting a cotton and polyester blend outer shell, with ethically sourced 90% duck down and 10% feather fill for added warmth. A DWR (durable water-repellent) coating then aids in helping you withstand the elements when things get a little dicey. Outfitted with front Velcro placket, the puffer features adjustable hood and hem drawcords that allow you to make minor alterations to the fit, while waist pockets and an internal chest pocket provide you with ample space for carrying essential items

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Overshirt Dark Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island overshirts are second to none. This new style is produced in cotton and outfitted with two-way front zip fastening that makes way for various styling options. A patch pocket with a flap and button closure is implemented at the chest, while the label's signature removable logo badge is incorporated onto the left sleeve to definitively brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Leather Tab Jacket Tan/Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Bode outerwear style draws inspiration from a vintage bag dating back to the 1930s and 1940s. The brand has in turn refashioned the original piece into a classic workwear silhouette. Predominantly made from cotton with leather trim, the jacket is outfitted with two tab buttons on the front, in addition to a trio of patch pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1996 Retro Nuptse Jacket Coal Brown/TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by the iconic lines of the 1996 Nuptse Jacket, the boxy, retro-style silhouette is back in new form for the season. Originally intended for the slopes, the Nuptse is now just as at home on the streets, with its crossover appeal that has long been at play in fashion circles. This jacket is still made for extreme temperatures, though, with its durable water-repellent finish and goose down fill that’s sure to keep you dry, warm, and cozy no matter the weather. And when you’re not wearing it, you can pack the entire thing down into its own pocket for light travel.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Verso Tris Jacket Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from classic varsity and bomber jacket styles, the Verso is constructed from a blend of wool, polyester, and nylon materials. The garment is lined and outfitted with two-way front zip closure, while being detailed with striped accents at the ribbed collar, cuffs, and hem. A defining element, the sleeves showcase a distinctive glossy effect, as the jacket then welcomes flap button pockets on the sides for securely carrying everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Saikuru Vest TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Saikuru combines heritage-inspired design with recycled fabrics. Predominantly crafted using recycled polyester, the functional garment harnesses Heatseeker Eco synthetic insulation for lightweight warmth and WindWall technology to reduce the effects of wind chill and provide flexibility and breathability. Designed for outdoor use and casual wear alike, the vest is then detailed with a standing collar, elasticated hem, and secure-zip pockets, with logo embellishments on the front and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Real Down Jacket Lavender
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Real Down Jacket is your stylish solution for those harsh winter months, boasting a resin treatment that gives the exterior a standout crinkled look. Wind- and water-resistant, the garment is capable of handling whatever comes your way, while slanting, flap side pockets provide you with ample room to carry your everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Down Puffer Jacket Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Down Puffer Jacket is your stylish solution for those harsh winter months, boasting a resin treatment that gives the exterior a standout crinkled look. Wind- and water-resistant, the garment is capable of handling whatever comes your way, while front flap pockets provide you with ample room to carry your everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleeski Y2K Jacket Khaki Stone/Utility Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Fleeski Y2K Jacket is the ultimate layering solution for year-round comfort on and off the trail as it's made of a warm, quick-drying polyester with a water-repellent finish. Nylon ripstop panels run around the mock neck collar and across the top, while two chest pockets and side pockets provide storage room on the go.  The piece is finished with an embroidered The North Face logo on the chest as well as a rubber patch on the sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Printed Denim Jacket Navy/Lilac
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An essential piece from the brand’s latest collection, the Printed Denim Jacket is seen here in a range of purple, navy, and white hues with a whiskered companion ready for action. With a tasteful eye for unique graphics and aesthetics, Gerrit Jacob’s eponymous line has quickly risen amongst the ranks of this generation's blossoming designers. Offering several silhouettes from his ready-to-wear collections, the brand utilizes imagery and motifs from the designer’s German heritage and recreates them into vibrant collections that blend kitsch with present-day luxury.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Grizzly Jacket Black Wax
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Grizzly Jacket is an elevated take on a familiar outerwear style. Produced in a water-repellent technical Italian fabric, the garment is adorned with a storm flap closure, leather buttons, and a faux fur collar. It is cut for a short, boxy fit and detailed with adjustable leather drawstrings, as well as buttoned jet pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Track Top Fall Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This season, Stockholm Surfboard Club delivers a contemporary update to the classic track jacket. The regular-fitting style is produced in a cotton poly blend fabric, with satin stripes at the sleeves. Contrasting trims emerge at the rib knit collar, cuffs, and hem, as the garment is finished with a logo patch at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Padded Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Perfect for chilly days or when a hoodie just isn’t enough, the Padded Jacket is an essential wardrobe piece. Crafted entirely from recycled polyester, the full-zip jacket arrives with a stand collar to protect you from any harsh winds, along with interior and side pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Packable Recycled Nylon Down Jacket Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: It doesn’t get any more convenient than a packable jacket. This signature style from Stone Island is produced in a lightweight recycled nylon that boasts a shiny finish for a more distinctive look. Duck down padding is used on the interior to ensure superior comfort, as the outerwear is outfitted with a hood that is edged by tape for protection from the elements. The jacket, which folds down and packs into an inner pocket, is then finished with the brand’s trademark logo badge featured on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment-Dyed Recycled Nylon Down Jacket Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Recycled Nylon Down Jacket is your stylish solution for those harsh winter months, boasting a resin treatment that gives the exterior a standout crinkled look. Wind- and water-resistant, the garment is capable of handling whatever comes your way, while slanting, flap side pockets provide you with ample room to carry your everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: OG Chore Coat Black/Aged Canvas
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A stealthy take on a classic workwear style, this version of the OG Chore Coat is constructed from Carhartt’s signature organic cotton Dearborn canvas. The outerwear is cut in a loose fit that caters to layering, featuring traditional front button closure and adjustable button cuffs. Four functional pockets are incorporated onto the front of the silhouette, which is finished with a small Carhartt label stitched to the left chest pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Light Gilet Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Converse x A-COLD-WALL* Gilet is defined by distinctive ACW* style cues and utilitarian-inspired details. It arrives in a versatile navy blue colorway, crafted from micro ripstop with poly taffeta lining. Vents are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette for enhanced breathability, while ample pockets increase the overall functionality of this style-meets-function creation.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1996 Retro Nuptse Jacket Brick House Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: When you buy The North Face, you’re investing in technically advanced outdoor products designed for everyone. This goes for everything from the brand’s signature activewear and outerwear to its cut and sew garments and accessories. Inspired by the iconic lines of the 1996 Nuptse Jacket, the boxy, retro-style silhouette is back in new form for AW21. Originally intended for the slopes, the Nuptse is now just as at home on the streets, with its crossover appeal that has long been a play in fashion circles. Don’t get it twisted, though — this jacket is still made for extreme temperatures, with its durable water-repellent finish and goose down fill that’s sure to keep you dry, warm, and toasty no matter the weather. And that’s not all — when you’re not wearing it, you can pack the entire thing down into its own pocket for light travel.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Harter-Heighway Down Jacket Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from their love of nature, Moncler and Salehe Bembury have joined forces to create a collection that sees Bembury’s ideology infused with Moncler’s mountaineering heritage. The Harter-Heighway Short Down Jacket is crafted from lightweight nylon and features Moncler’s longue saison lining that protects against water. Along with being down-filled to keep your core warm when the temperature drops, the jacket arrives with a classic collar, flap pockets, and Salehe’s all-over quilted pattern featuring organic shapes that further embellish the overall style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hulda Jacket Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Hulda Jacket is a two-tone style by RANRA, arriving this season in a neutral color scheme for effortless matching. Cut for a standard boxy fit, the outerwear garment features a spread collar with button fastening, front zip closure, and button cuffs, with eyelet vents at the underarms to increase breathability. Zip pockets are incorporated at the chest to provide space for securely carrying small essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vallow Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Vallow is Dries van Noten’s high fashion take on the classic coaches jacket. Cut for a relaxed fit, the stealthy outerwear style is produced in a polyester fabric with a noticeable sheen that doubles as a water-repellent shell. The monochrome jacket is detailed with two-way front zip closure for versatility, interior and side pockets, and adjustable velcro tabs on the sleeves to style to your liking.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: CL RGTX Coat
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This trench-style coat arrives in a stealthy all-black colorway that is synonymous with Yohji Yamamoto and Y-3. It is made using lightweight GORE-TEX for weather-proofing, with taped external seams and full inner lining. A vented back offers enhanced freedom of movement, while two-way zip closure makes way for easy on and off.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Elephant Coach Jacket Midnight Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Elephant Coach Jacket is a nod to KENZO founder Kenzo Takada and his favorite animal. Designed for multi-seasonal wear, the lightweight jacket is produced in nylon and cut in a relaxed fit. It features press stud fastenings and side hand pockets while being decorated with KENZO elephant prints on the front as well as the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crackle Leather Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Crackle Leather Jacket brings a distinctive hand distressed look to a classic outerwear style. Produced in 100% leather, the garment is cut for a regular, boxy fit, featuring a pointed collar, full zip closure, and adjustable tabs at the hem for minor alterations. Functional hand pockets are incorporated onto the front of the jacket to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Texture Nylon Zipper Shirt Jacket Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from lightweight Japanese nylon fabric, this zip-up style is characterized by the textured finish of its fabric which is caused by a heat process. The casual style has minimal branding in the form of a flag label on the left side and debossed zipper pull. Further details come in the form of adjustable button-down metal sleeve cuffs and side pockets. This zipper shirt jacket arrives along with matching shorts in the latest Highsnobiety collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Canvas Coach Jacket Sage
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stockholm Surfboard Club updates the classic coach jacket, executing the staple outerwear item in lightweight cotton canvas. It arrives in a neutral sage colorway with bright contrasting buttons lined down the center. Large flap pockets are incorporated onto the front, as the style is finished with a woven logo label at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Summer Romance Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Poised to become a timeless classic, the Summer Romance Jacket is designed to share the love and joy of life. Workwear-inspired, the outerwear style features traditional design elements like two-way zip closure, buttoned cuffs and hem, and a zip pocket at the chest. It is cut in a boxy fit for a classic look and decorated with playful patches that are incorporated onto the front as well as the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.0 Jacket Right Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A versatile addition to your outerwear arsenal, this version of the 5.0 from Korean brand Post Archive Faction can easily be dressed up or down. It is produced in a heavy-duty nylon and cotton blend, with a fluid flow on the arm and a three-dimensional pattern at the elbow for ease of movement. The jacket is outfitted with a snap button front, standard straight collar, and exterior and interior pockets, emerging in a neutral brown colorway for effortless matching.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Undir Vest Bordeaux/Coffee
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Undir Vest from RANRA (formerly known as Arnar Már Jónsson) is a multi-seasonal layering piece with a cotton corduroy shell and nylon down padding. Lined with cotton, the garment is contrasted with black trim throughout, while featuring two large zip pockets at the chest and two welt hand pockets just underneath. As with many outerwear styles from the brand, the Undir Vest showcases an elevated sportswear-inspired aesthetic.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Coat Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic long-length wool coat style, this piece of outerwear boasts a timeless look with elevated detailing. Variegated wool creates a distinctive two-tone effect across the outer, while a shirt collar, red logo detailing on the left cuff, and contrast black buttons provide the finishing touches.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wave Shorts Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Wave Short is a new and wander style produced in 100% polyester. It features the brand's signature built-in logo belt incorporated into the elasticated waistband and is made with button fastening and a zip fly. Hand pockets are implemented at the sides of the silhouette, while a single zippered pocket is applied to the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Lens Swim Shorts Total Eclipse
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These C.P. Company Swim Shorts are produced in a lightweight yet durable nylon fabric geared towards water activity. The pair is offered in a versatile blue colorway, outfitted with a comfortable elasticated waistband and a single cargo pocket at the left leg. To brand the style, C.P. Company's signature lens detail is applied to the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Bmbx-Ken-37 Swim Shorts Faded Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These standout Diesel swim shorts feature a trompe l'oeil effect designed to mimic denim bottoms with classic five-pocket construction. The pair is made from polyester and lined, while incorporating an internal drawstring in the elasticated waistband for superior comfort and a perfect fit. Pockets are implemented at the sides of the silhouette, which is finished with logo detailing on the front as well as the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Metal Swim Shorts Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island delivers summer’s must-have swim shorts. Produced using iridescent ECONYL regenerated fabric, the feathery bottoms are subjected to an intricate double-dyeing process that creates a noticeably unique finish. The pair is resin-coated as well to make the garment water- and wind-resistant, while featuring an elastic waistband with an interior drawstring that allows you to dial in the fit. With slanting hand pockets and an additional back pocket, the Nylon Metal Swim Shorts are finished with Stone Island’s trademark compass logo at the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Compass Swim Shorts Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island delivers summer’s must-have swim shorts. Produced using iridescent ECONYL regenerated fabric, the feathery bottoms are subjected to an intricate double-dyeing process to create a distinctive finish. The pair is resin-coated as well to make the garment water- and wind-resistant, while featuring an elastic waistband with an external drawstring that allows you to dial in the fit. With slanting hand pockets and an additional back pocket, the bottoms are finished with Stone Island’s trademark compass logo at the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Eco-Chrome Swim Shorts Drizzle Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Eco-Chrome Swim Shorts are produced in the brand’s signature nylon material created through the upcycling of fish nets. The water-ready pair features a regular fit and is made with an elasticated drawstring waist and functional side pockets. To finish the design, a small C.P. Company logo label is applied to the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Water Short Iron Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, these TNF bottoms are specifically designed for water activity, being made from a quick-drying nylon fabric with a Durable Water-Repellent Finish. The pair is outfitted with a mesh liner and features an adjustable drawstring in the elasticated waistband, open hand pockets, and a single back zippered pocket. TNF logos are applied to the front and back of the silhouette to definitively brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Metal Swim Shorts Rust
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island delivers summer’s must-have swim shorts. Produced using iridescent ECONYL regenerated fabric, the feathery bottoms are subjected to an intricate double-dyeing process that creates a noticeably unique finish. The pair is resin-coated as well to make the garment water- and wind-resistant, while featuring an elastic waistband with an interior drawstring that allows you to dial in the fit. With slanting hand pockets and an additional back pocket, the Nylon Metal Swim Shorts are finished with Stone Island’s trademark compass logo at the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Acid Washed Swim Shorts Blue Radiance
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Acid Washed Shorts serve as an update to Patta's Basic Swim Shorts, featuring a softer hand feel. Constructed from a cotton-nylon blend, the pair is defined by an acid wash effect that creates a more textured look. Details include an elastic waistband with an adjustable drawstring, side hand pockets, and a back Velcro pocket. The brand's signature Script logo is embroidered onto the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Spree Swim Briefs Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A unique update to the traditional swim brief, the Spree showcases a distinctive crossing design at the front, paired with an open back. The style is constructed from a recycled nylon and elastane blend fabric and embellished with a contrasting GmbH logo on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Swim Shorts Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Y-3 Swim Shorts feature a lightweight nylon shell and recycled polyester mesh lining for all your water-related activities. Available in a versatile black colorway, the pair is outfitted with an adjustable drawstring waist and a back zip pocket so you can securely carry small essentials. A heat-transferred Y-3 logo is applied to the left leg to serve as the lone branding hit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Paul Swim Shorts Dark Khaki Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Paul Swim Short is a fitted style with a low rise, cut at mid-thigh length. The pair is constructed from a fast-drying, lightweight organic cotton poplin fabric, featuring a button fly and a side slit at each outside leg seam. A zippered pocket is incorporated onto the back of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Active Jersey Swim Brief Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like many Marine Serre pieces, the brand’s moon logo takes center stage on the Active Jersey Swim Brief. The water-ready style is produced in a stretchy recycled nylon and elastane blend, featuring an elasticated waistband for optimal comfort.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Grape Swim Shorts Light Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: JW Anderson delivers a playful piece of swimwear for the new season. As the name suggests, the short is embellished with a grape motif that defines the garment. The relaxed-fitting pair is constructed from recycled polyester with mesh lining and features an elasticated waistband with an internal drawcord, as well as an internal coin pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Phibbs Swim Shorts Petrol
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Swim trunks aren’t strictly reserved for water activity anymore, as nylon shorts have become increasingly popular for everyday wear. Dries van Noten delivers a fresh pair for the new season, a style embellished with a captivating graphic print. Made from nylon, the swim shorts feature an elasticated waistband with an integrated drawstring, as well as side slip pockets. DVN is a master of artful prints and patterns, never more evident than with the Phibbs design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Phibbs Swim Shorts Ombre Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Swim trunks aren’t strictly reserved for water activity anymore, as nylon shorts have become increasingly popular for everyday wear. Dries van Noten delivers a fresh pair for the new season, a style embellished with a captivating graphic print. Made from nylon, the swim shorts feature an elasticated waistband with an integrated drawstring, as well as side slip pockets. DVN is a master of artful prints and patterns, never more evident than with the Phibbs design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Printed Swim Shorts Chambray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our second partnership pays homage to the vibrant heritage of St. Tropez, as we join forces with Vilebrequin to showcase its illustrious past in the French Riviera. The new capsule collection includes swimwear and accessories, such as these printed swim shorts that arrive with a durable mesh lining along and side pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Printed Morphing Stripes Swimsuit Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ideal for summer getaways or visiting your local beach, this Jean Paul Gaultier swimsuit arrives with morphing, anatomical stripes that wrap around the entire garment. Detailed with a mesmerizing purple and green gradient pattern, the one-piece swimsuit features a classic scoop neckline with a locker loop at the rear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Solid Swim Shorts Red Tea
tshirts_and_tops.Description: For our second collaboration and ode to St. Tropez, we teamed up with Vilebrequin to shine a light on its rich history in the French Riviera.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Phibbs Swim Shorts Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This swim shorts style is embellished with a captivating floral print. Made from nylon, the swim shorts feature an elasticated waistband with an integrated drawstring, as well as side slip pockets. DvN is a master of artful prints and patterns, never more evident than with the Phibbs design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Swimsuit Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Take your poolside look to new heights with Stockholm Surfboard Club’s captivating Swimsuit. Produced in a recycled nylon and elastane blend, the playful one-piece is sure to brighten up your day.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crackle Leather Short Distressed Damson Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Leather is for the warm weather months, too, as Guess comes through with a new pair of leather shorts for the season. Defined by hand distressing, the distinctive style features classic five-pocket construction and offers a relaxed fit with a dropped rise. A vintage Guess logo is applied to the back right pocket to minimally brand the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crackle Leather Short Amos Brown Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Leather is for the warm weather months, too, as Guess comes through with a new pair of leather shorts for the season. Defined by hand distressing, the distinctive style features classic five-pocket construction and offers a relaxed fit with a dropped rise. A vintage Guess logo is applied to the back right pocket to minimally brand the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sven Shorts Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made from a lightweight wool blend fabric, the Sven Short is Séfr's formal take on a classic wide leg short. The pair arrives in a neutral black colorway, outfitted with hook and zip fastening as well as belt loops lining the waist. Pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, in addition to the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Trek Shorts 3 Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Expertly crafted from a water-repellent, double weave stretch fabric, the Trek Shorts from and wander are perfect for urban exploration and mountain adventures alike. The hard-wearing pair makes use of a jersey material for the inseam gusset to prevent stiffness and stuffiness, and is outfitted with an integrated belt with branded, metal hardware. Reflector prints and stitches ensure nighttime visibility, while zippered pockets at the front and back provide you ample space to securely carry essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Breath Rip Shorts Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These technical and wander shorts are expertly crafted using 30-denier and 160-denier textured ripstop that is a breathable, durable, and water-repellent. The garment features a pattern design with a wide range of motion, while partially using a reflector stitch. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Diplopia Tank Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Diplopia serves as a contemporary update to the traditional tank top. Produced in 100% cotton, the sleeveless style is defined by its double neck. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Carne Döner Delights T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A nod to the sexiest, fictional Döner Shop in Berlin, this collaborative t-shirt is crafted entirely from organic cotton and features a graphic print on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Backroom Fantasy T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaborative t-shirt takes you backdoors into Carne Bollente's orgasmic universe. The tee is crafted entirely from organic cotton and is embellished with sexy graphics wishing you the best from Berlin.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Berliner Love Affair T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made entirely from organic cotton, the Berliner Love Affair T-Shirt embodies the ethos of Berlin's short and sweet summer. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Guten Tag Long-Sleeve Washed Black

tshirts_and_tops.Name: A-Shirt Two-Pack White

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Relaxed SS Tee White

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Gauze White

tshirts_and_tops.Name: No Problemo SS Tee Black

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mini Problemo SS Tee White

Zippered pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, in addition to slip pockets on the interior.
