The heavyweight tee is then finished with printed logos around the image with a few hinting at the gallery where the late artist held one of his performances.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Diop Tank Top Red/Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Diop Tank Top is a minimal Wales Bonner style produced in 100% polyester. It arrives for the season in a bright red colorway with contrasting black panels. The sleeveless style is subtly branded with a small logo patch applied to the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tropiques Polo Black/Green/Yellow
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Wales Bonner polo captures attention with a multicolored stripe pattern implemented at the body as well as the sleeves. The garment is fully knit from 100% wool and cut for a classic fit. Details include a polo collar, three-button closure, and a straight hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: S/S Strange Screw T–Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Relaxed fit. Order your regular size.The model is wearing a size M, and is 186cm / 6’1” tall with a 84cm / 33’ chest. While this piece is from the men’s collection, we shoot on female, male, and non-binary models.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heraldry Tattoo Top Beige/Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Tattoos, piercings, body adornments – all are fair play in Jean Paul Gaultier's universe of ready-to-wear pieces. The brand's latest Tattoo Collection revisits its archive of stretchy, sheer silhouettes like the Heraldry Tattoo Top that's produced entirely from tulle. Detailed with all-over printed heraldry motifs including cherubs, a coat of arms, and several animals, the nude-colored top is finished with long sleeves and a crew neck collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Calm Polo Chestnut Brown/Ivory/Ruby Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Part polo and part sweater, the Calm is a cozy Wales Bonner style produced in 100% wool. It arrives in a predominantly red and brown colorway, with a contrasting spread collar and rib knit trims. Cut for an oversized fit, the garment is then finished with a small rubber logo patch implemented at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pointelle Polo Longsleeve Cream
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Bode’s Pointelle Polo is a seasonal longsleeve style that draws inspiration from a pair of lace gloves that dates back to the 1940s. The piece’s original knit pattern is in turn replicated for the Bode garment, which is produced in a mid-weight cotton yarn. The shirt offers a semi see-through look with three-button fastening.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This minimal t-shirt style by Jil Sander is made from a technical polyester jersey fabric. Cut for a boxy fit, the short-sleeve top features a traditional crew neck and is embellished with a contrasting Jil Sander+ logo front and center.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Big Wheel T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Carne Bollente styles, the Big Wheel T-Shirt is characterized by sex-positive artwork that encourages people to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The design pairs a versatile streetwear staple with a scenic sex illustration, injecting a bit of playful energy into the elevated basic. Constructed from 100% organic cotton to lower environmental impact, the tee is unisex, with detailed artwork implemented on the front and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Long Sleeves Knit Polo Bordeaux
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Long-Sleeve Knit Polo arrives in a monochromatic colorway and is crafted from a lightweight, polyester knit fabric. The top is detailed with contrasting accents at the collar and chest pocket as well as the mother-of-pearl button closure. Further features include a ribbed knit hem and cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Long Sleeves Knit Polo Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Long-Sleeve Knit Polo arrives in a monochromatic colorway and is crafted from a lightweight, polyester knit fabric. The top is detailed with contrasting accents at the collar and chest pocket as well as the mother-of-pearl button closure. Further features include a ribbed knit hem and cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Long Sleeves Knit Polo Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Long-Sleeve Knit Polo arrives in a monochromatic colorway and is crafted from a lightweight, polyester knit fabric. The top is detailed with contrasting accents at the collar and chest pocket as well as the mother-of-pearl button closure. Further features include a ribbed knit hem and cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ali Tank Top Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: GmbH's Ali Tank Top is an organic cotton jersey style showcasing a seasonal screenprint front and center. As with many pieces from the Berlin-based brand, the ribbed tank is a unisex design, fit for wear season after season.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mesh Long-Sleeve Lilac
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Mesh Long-Sleeve is one of many standout pieces from Gerrit Jacob’s latest collection. This stretchy top arrives in a semi-sheer look that is detailed with all-over printed airbrush graphics and raw edges at the cuffs and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Lycra Top Teal/Aqua
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Gerrit Jacob’s latest collection is an ode to colorful storytelling and draws inspiration from his hometown and visual artistry as a whole. A key standout, this fitted top is detailed with unique printed airbrushed graphics and features a mock collar at the neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Printed Long-Sleeve Top Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This lightweight top from J.W. Anderson showcases the brand's digital golden boys print. Crafted from a polyester blend fabric with a sheer quality, the garment features a traditional crew neck and is cut to a fitted silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Evening Polo Candyfloss Fuzzy Alpaca
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A hybrid design of sorts, this signature Our Legacy style is part polo, part button-up, and part cardigan. Produced in a soft, fuzzy Italian alpaca and nylon blend fabric, the lavish garment features center button closure with contrasting mother of pearl buttons, a spread collar, and straight deep ribbed hem. It is cut in a relaxed, boxy fit that caters to layering from season to season.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This T-shirt pays homage to the Big Apple and its cultural influence. The short-sleeved top is embellished with contrasting graphic prints at the chest and back along with an embroidered logo below the neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This T-shirt pays homage to the Big Apple and its cultural influence. The short-sleeved top is embellished with contrasting graphic prints at the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Thermal T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This monochrome thermal t-shirt is crafted entirely from cotton and arrives as part of our tribute to the Big Apple. The short-sleeved T-shirt is detailed with a waffle knit texture that retains heat and provides breathability and is finished with printed logos at the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Chopped Cheese T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Native to New York, the Chopped Cheese is one of the city’s many culinary delights. This T-shirt arrives as part of our latest collection with At The Moment, crafted using water-based biodegradable inks, the short-sleeve T-shirt features a biodegradable graphic print at the center in a black colorway.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: With a CFDA award win under his belt, Edvin Thompson’s Theophilio has grown to become one of the most exciting emerging brands in the Big Apple. This limited edition T-shirt arrives embellished with a rhinestone logo and print across the chest from one of the brand’s earliest photo shoots in New York.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pink T-shirt arrives as part of our tribute to Sant Ambroeus, the renowned Milanese eatery that has become a staple of NYC’s dining scene since 1982. Produced in 230gsm fabric, the short-sleeve shirt is detailed with a woven brand patch on the chest and co-branded graphics at the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This white T-shirt arrives as part of our tribute to Sant Ambroeus, the renowned Milanese eatery that has become a staple of NYC’s dining scene since 1982. Produced in 230gsm fabric, the short-sleeve shirt is detailed with co-branded graphics across the chest and features the eatery’s iconic bird emblem below the back collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sanitation Truck T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An ode to the public service workers that keep the city moving, this collaborative T-shirt was made in part with Dave’s New York, a family-owned business that’s called NYC home since 1963. The short-sleeved is made from 230gsm cotton and features co-branded logos at the chest and back with an elaborate drawing of a classic sanitation truck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt Sage
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Family-owned since 1963, Dave’s NY has grown to become a staple establishment for workwear and casual apparel. This midweight T-shirt arrives as part of our collaboration with the shop and is seen here in a sage colorway that’s detailed with co-branded logos at the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt Off White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: De La Soul has established itself as hip-hop royalty since its debut album was released in 1989, garnering worldwide recognition. To celebrate the group’s success in tandem with hip-hop’s 50th anniversary, this collaborative t-shirt gives flowers to the iconic group.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: De La Soul has established itself as hip-hop royalty since its debut album was released in 1989, garnering worldwide recognition. To celebrate the group’s success in tandem with hip-hop’s 50th anniversary, this collaborative t-shirt features iconography inspired by the cult classic album De La Soul Is Dead (1991) across the back and a woven patch at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Short-Sleeve T-Shirt Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar draws inspiration from workwear. This vibrant pink T-shirt takes on our delivery ops moniker and features a contrasting print on the chest as well as a graphic print on the back of a classic Coca-Cola Zero Sugar crate.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tank Top White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar inspiration from workwear. This tank arrives with an embroidered Coca-Cola Zero Sugar logo on the chest and features a scoop neckline along with a co-branded woven brand tag.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Short-Sleeve T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar draws inspiration from workwear. This all-black tee takes on our delivery ops moniker and features a contrasting print on the chest that references the year Highsnobiety was founded as well as a co-branded graphic print on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mesh T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Mesh T-Shirt is one of many standout pieces from Gerrit Jacob’s "Raised by Wolves" collection. Cut in a slim fit and detailed with all-over printed airbrush graphics, this stretchy top arrives in a semi-sheer finish that's finished with raw edges at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mesh Long Sleeve Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The mesh long-sleeve is one of many standout pieces from Gerrit Jacob’s "Raised by Wolves" collection. This stretchy top arrives in a semi-sheer finish that's detailed with all-over printed airbrush graphics, raw edges at the hem, and thumbholes at the cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Print T-Shirt Gauze White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A minimal style, this C.P. Company t-shirt features a small brand logo printed at the chest. It is made from 100% cotton and features a traditional rib knit crew neck, while offering a comfy, relaxed fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Alko Airbrush Skull T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Alko is a seasonal Stockholm Surfboard Club style made from organic cotton. Cut for a regular boxy fit, the short-sleeve tee is defined by an airbrush skull print implemented in all-over fashion.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Alko Logo T-Shirt White/Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple Stockholm Surfboard Club style, the Logo T-Shirt is adorned with a playful graphic print on the back of the garment. The boxy silhouette is crafted from 100% organic cotton with a soft hand feel, featuring a traditional rib knit crew neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Boxy Cotton T-Shirt Off White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Yohji Yamamoto has used his Y-3 label, made together with adidas, as his playground for finding the sweet spot between fashion and sportswear for over 20 years. On this casual t-shirt, the collaborative line utilizes a boxy, oversized fit and soft cotton fabric for optimum comfort. Offered in white, the tee is accented through subtle black logo detailing on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ningen-sei Indigo Dyed T-Shirt #1 Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Indigo Dyed T-Shirt is a part of Human Made’s Ningen-sei capsule collection focusing on Japanese culture. Crafted from 100% cotton, the tee is woven with uneven slub yarn, featuring a distinctive gradient effect created through the use of indigo dye. Due to the nature of the dye, the color may be uneven, and it will gradually fade over time with repeated wear and washing.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ningen-sei Indigo Dyed T-Shirt #2 Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Indigo Dyed T-Shirt is a part of Human Made’s Ningen-sei capsule collection focusing on Japanese culture. Crafted from 100% cotton, the tee is woven with uneven slub yarn, featuring a standout tie-dye pattern with a unique texture created through the use of indigo dye. Due to the nature of the dye, the color may be uneven.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Maison Margiela flips the script with this seasonal Logo T-Shirt, as it boasts an upside-down Margiela Paris logo embroidered at the front. Around back, you will find the label’s signature four stitches moniker in tonal thread.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Classic S/S T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Per the name, this familiar style is a classic Martine Rose design, showcasing the brand’s scribble logo in contrasting print front and center. The staple tee is offered in black and white colorways for easy matching, crafted from a soft cotton jersey fabric with a traditional ribbed crew neck. A unisex style, the garment is cut for a loose or oversized fit to ensure a more comfortable wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pigment Dyed Boxy Long Sleeves Jersey Natural
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted for year-round wear, this long-sleeve t-shirt arrives in a pigment-dyed, neutral hue and is cut in a relaxed, boxy fit. The shirt is made entirely from cotton and detailed with open cuffs and a small embroidered HS 05 logo along the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pigment Dyed Boxy Long Sleeves Jersey Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted for year-round wear, this long-sleeve t-shirt arrives in a pigment-dyed, neutral hue and is cut in a relaxed, boxy fit. The shirt is made entirely from cotton and detailed with open cuffs and a small embroidered HS 05 logo along the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3 Pack Heavyweight Tank Top White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Built for year-round wear, this 3-pack of tank tops comes crafted from heavyweight 220gsm cotton and has a square neckline that accentuates your collarbone. The tops are cut in an athletic fit with no external branding, allowing you to easily add these tanks to your wardrobe.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Thermal Short Sleeve Natural
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Offered in a selection of neutral colorways, the Thermal Short Sleeve is a heavyweight waffle knit top featuring a ribbed crew neck and cuffs, complete with a small woven label on the sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Thermal Short Sleeve Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Offered in a selection of neutral colorways, the Thermal Short Sleeve is a heavyweight waffle knit top featuring a ribbed crew neck and cuffs, complete with a small woven label on the sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3 Pack T-Shirts Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This 3-pack of T-shirts comes crafted from heavyweight 220gsm cotton and a ribbed crewneck. The short-sleeve tops are cut in a loose fit with no external branding.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3 Pack T-Shirts White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This 3-pack of T-shirts comes crafted from heavyweight 220gsm cotton and a ribbed crewneck. The short-sleeve tops are cut in a loose fit with no external branding.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cats T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Cats T-Shirt is a fun seasonal graphic style from Patta. Produced in lightweight cotton, the short-sleeve top features a traditional rib knit crew neck, with a screenprinted cats graphic with a silver foil print effect on the front. Graphic tees remain as important to Patta as its sneaker drops and collaborative releases. They serve as a street canvas for the brand to get its message out there to the world.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fissato Longsleeve T-Shirt Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This longsleeve t-shirt from Stone Island is garment-dyed and treated with the “Fissato” effect, a water-soluble resin process and garment-dyeing technique, to create a distinctive three-dimensional appearance. Being subjected to such an intricate dying process, the tee doesn’t need an abundance of over-the-top details and branding. Instead, it’s simply marked with Stone Island’s signature compass logo at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hollyweird T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As Noon Good puts it, Hollywood is a place of magic, mystery, and weirdness. The Hollyweird T-Shirt draws from this notion, as it is adorned with studded logo detailing on the front of the 18/1 weight cotton jersey tee. The garment arrives this season in a black colorway featuring a traditional rib knit crew neck and a classic fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crew Neck Long Sleeves "Fleurs Petit Grand" Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic silhouette from the French maestro’s eponymous brand arrives with a seasonal Fleurs Petit Grand print with blossoming roses that wraps around the garment. The semi-sheer top is crafted from lightweight, stretchy nylon that’s ideal for warm weather or layering and is finished with raw edges and a round neckline.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Long Sleeves Crew Neck Morphing Stripes Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic silhouette from the French maestro’s eponymous brand arrives with anatomical stripes that wrap around the garment. The semi-sheer top is crafted from lightweight, stretchy nylon that’s ideal for warm weather or layering and is finished with raw edges and a round neckline.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Short Sleeves Trompe L'Œil Body White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Jean Pauls Gaultier's mesmerizing Trompe L'Œil garments are in a league of their own.  The French icon and his eponymous label have pioneered the design for decades and its craft is on full display with this short-sleeved top. Detailed with metallic thread throughout the anatomical ribbing the lightweight top is finished with a round collar and arrives in a classic slim fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Long Sleeve Logo Rashguard Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This rashguard arrives as part of our latest collaboration with the St. Tropez brand that celebrates its place along the French Riviera. A performance piece for water sports, the rashguard is resistant to sunscreen and oil, and offers SPF 50+.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ideal for all occasions, this graphic t-shirt arrives as part of our latest collaboration with the St. Tropez brand that celebrates its place along the French Riviera. Crafted from a durable cotton jersey, the t-shirt arrives with a co-branded printed logo across the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Longsleeve Logo T-Shirt Porcelain White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Logo T-Shirt is a staple Jil Sander style, here available in a clean white colorway that caters to effortless matching. It is crafted from a lightweight compact cotton jersey fabric and cut in a relaxed fit. The top features a traditional rib knit crew neck, while being branded with a contrasting Jil Sander+ logo, which is printed front and center.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Merdan Knit Dark Camel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Merdan Knit is a fuzzy cardigan produced in 100% nylon. Featuring a soft and fluffy exterior, the sweater is then outfitted with a spread collar, front button closure, and banded cuffs and hem. The garment arrives this season in a Dark Camel colorway that caters to repeat wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Varsity T-Shirt Soft Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Varsity T-Shirt is a seasonal Affix style produced in a midweight cotton jersey fabric. Cut for a standard, boxy fit, the short-sleeve top is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and embellished with a contrasting varsity print on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tank Top Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Yohji Yamamoto has used his Y-3 label, made together with adidas, as his playground for finding the sweet spot between fashion and sportswear for over 20 years. On this casual tank top, the collaborative line utilizes a relaxed, straight fit and a cotton-recycled polyester blend fabric to create a style inspired by athletic wear. A color that Yamamoto is famous for championing, it arrives in all-black with subtle logo detailing at the back yoke.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Oakley x Fragment Logo T-Shirt is a nod to Hiroshi Fujiwara’s clean lines. Available in black and white colorways, the short-sleeve tee is adorned with contrasting graphic prints on the front, back, and sleeve, where you will find co-branding, the iconic Oakley Frogskin sunglasses, and additional iconography, respectively. The limited edition tee is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a standard boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Bugs Tee Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bugs Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the short-sleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with an assortment of bugs on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Bat Tee Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bat Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the short-sleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with a playful multicolored print by artist Isabel Kang on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Aunty Nani Tee Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Aunty Nani Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the short-sleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with a colorful floral motif on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Alien Puppet Longsleeve Tee Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Alien Puppet Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the longsleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with a playful alien print on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and cuffs and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Bugs Tee Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bugs Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the short-sleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with an assortment of bugs on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Primer Longsleeve Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made for everyone, the Primer Longsleeve is an elevated Entire Studios basic. The classic top arrives in an array of neutral colors for effortless matching, cut in a slim fit for a more streamlined look. Produced in a midweight cotton fabric, the garment is ribbed and treated with an enzyme wash and potassium spray detailing for a slightly more distinctive overall look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Dart Tee Tar
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic sweatpant. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Dart Tee is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from midweight organic cotton that is treated with an enzyme wash and potassium spray detailing for a more distinctive look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Dart Tee Brunette
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic sweatpant. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Dart Tee is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from midweight organic cotton that is treated with an enzyme wash and potassium spray detailing for a more distinctive look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Primer Longsleeve Brunette

The classic top arrives in an array of neutral colors for effortless matching, cut in a slim fit for a more streamlined look. Produced in a midweight cotton fabric, the garment is ribbed and treated with an enzyme wash and potassium spray detailing for a slightly more distinctive overall look.

tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic sweatpant. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Dart Tee is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from midweight organic cotton that is treated with an enzyme wash and potassium spray detailing for a more distinctive look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rib Tank Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made for everyone, the Rib Tank is an elevated Entire Studios basic. The classic top arrives in an array of neutral colors for effortless matching, cut in a slim fit for a more streamlined look. Produced in a midweight cotton fabric, the garment is ribbed and treated with an enzyme wash for a slightly more distinctive overall look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Graphic Tee White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Rhuigi’s latest collection with Puma pays homage to New York City and its influence on youth culture, drawing from pivotal moments like the birth of hip-hop and the striking style of Walt “Clyde” Frazier. Arriving in a clean white and red look, the New York Worldwide Tee is emblazoned with a seasonal NYC-specific motif on the front, as Puma x Rhuigi iconography emerges on the back and sleeve to signal the collaboration.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Murice Knit Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A nod to decades past, the Murice is Dries van Noten’s elevated take on the knit polo shirt and arrives in a vivid red colorway. The top is crafted from merino wool and features a ribbed knit hem and cuffs with a classic three-button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Helli PR Show Jersey Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten and his eponymous label return with a new season showcasing its mastery of prints and patterns. The Helli PR ‘Show’ Jersey emerges in a tonal beige hue with a large graphic print across the front and. Cut in a spacious, loose fit for versatile wear, the t-shirt features the designer’s initials printed across the chest highlighting the recent collection, along with an additional print on the back where its AW23 show took place.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hegland PR Jersey Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten is here to take your t-shirt collection to the next level with a mature style constructed from soft cotton jersey. The oversized t-shirt is detailed with long sleeves and features a scenic print of a falcon in flight surrounded by hazy clouds and rushing waves. Arriving in a tonal beige hue, the t-shirt is finished with a classic crewneck collar and is sure to add a refined touch to your wardrobe.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Organic Cotton Logo Longsleeve T-Shirt Fluo Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Logo Longsleeve is one of many staple Acne Studios garments offered with a minimal finish. Made from organic cotton, the cozy t-shirt is cut in a regular fit for versatility and subtly embellished with a small Acne Studios logo at the center front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment-Dyed T-Shirt Vintage Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Minimal by design, this Acne Studios tee is made from organically grown cotton, with a peach garment-dyed finish that gives it a distinctive appearance. The shirt arrives this season in a light pink colorway, subtly branded with a small Acne Studios logo patch on the back. It is a unisex style that is cut in a relaxed fit for extra comfort.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Chevron T-Shirt Blue/Black/White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Chevron T-Shirt is a mature style knit from a lightweight cotton material. As with most Missoni garments, it showcases a captivating motif from the masters of prints and patterns. The top is detailed with rib knit trims at the round collar, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This seasonal t-shirt design by Acne Studios incorporates both screenprints and embroidery to spell out the brand name. The revamped logo is implemented on the front of the soft cotton tee, which is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cracked Print T-Shirt Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made from organically grown cotton with a multicolored spray finish, this Acne Studios graphic tee is brought to life with a cracked screenprint implemented on the front. The vibrant style is poised to inject color into your year-round wardrobe, as it is cut in a loose, unisex fit designed for everyone.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Short Sleeve T-Shirt Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Celebrating the most famous falafel shop in Paris, L'As du Fallafel, this T-shirt features the shop’s popular falafel dishes on the back. The graphic top is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A must-have for fans of the cult Swedish brand, the t-shirt contains the brand’s logo stamped front and center with the year it was founded. Crafted from a cotton and hemp blend with a unique sprayed finish, the tee is finished with distressed details on the neckline, cuff, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: High Density Finx Linen Weather Shirt Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Auralee’s Finx Linen Weather Shirt is designed to bolster your warm weather wardrobe. It is crafted from a linen and cotton blend, densely woven using fine finx cotton for the warp and Belgian linen for the weft. A special wash gives the garment a natural fullness and drape, while the dyed yarn creates a deep coloring. Cut in a slightly oversized, boxy fit, the style is offered in a bold green colorway for vibrant spring and summer looks.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Cotton Wool Rib Knit Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Part sweater and part shirt, this Auralee style brings cozy, mature vibes to your wardrobe. It is crafted from specially spun extra-long cotton and extra-fine count wool, characterized by its soft, brushed texture and unique elasticity. Details include front button closure and button cuffs, a classic collar, and a straight hem. The garment is cut for an oversized fit with elongated sleeves, making it ideal for layering.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Mesh Knit T-Shirt Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted with hot environments in mind, this T-Shirt is produced in a loose gauge knit cotton mesh for enhanced airflow and a semi-see-through finish. The tee features a wide, oversized fit and is accented with a subtle Highsnobiety woven tag implemented on the side. Due to the fabric and construction method, we recommend folding the sweater as opposed to hanging it to preserve its shape.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Mesh Knit T-Shirt Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted with hot environments in mind, this T-Shirt is produced in a loose gauge knit cotton mesh for enhanced airflow and a semi-see-through finish. The tee features a wide, oversized fit and is accented with a subtle Highsnobiety woven tag implemented on the side. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Mesh Knit Tank Top Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted with hot environments in mind, this tank top is produced in a loose gauge knit cotton mesh for enhanced airflow and a semi-see-through finish. The tank top features a loose fit and is accented with a subtle Highsnobiety woven tag implemented on the side. Due to the fabric and construction method, we recommend folding the sweater as opposed to hanging it to preserve its shape.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Knitted T-Shirt Digital Abyss Performance Poly
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Our Legacy top is knit from a fine technical Italian polyester fabric that will shape to the wearer and naturally distress over time. It features a boxy, cropped fit for a more distinctive look, with a bound ribbed collar and straight hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: KENZO Elephant Fitted T-Shirt Midnight Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Offering a retro sportswear look, this KENZO t-shirt draws inspiration from American university style. The embroidered elephant on the front is a nod to brand founder Kenzo Takada’s favorite animal, incorporated in the middle of KENZO Paris branding. On the back of the tee, you will find additional iconography by way of the Boke Flower 2.0 pattern, which also lines the sleeves.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Seamless Longsleeve Cotton Shirt Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple ROA style, the Seamless Longsleeve is constructed from a technical Dryarn and cotton blend with cooling and wicking properties and no seams for comfort and easy layering. It is detailed with ribbed trims at the crew neck and cuffs and minimally branded with a ROA logo at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Upcycled Pale Pink Jersey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: In an effort to reduce deadstock waste, Highsnobiety’s in-house brand is upcycling a range of its staple hoodies and T-shirts from previous seasons. The limited-edition collection arrives with nature-inspired graphics, such as this one with a butterfly print at the back. Meanwhile, the front of the top has embroidered Highsnobiety branding layered over a screen-printed design listing cities from around the world. A portion of the proceeds from this collection will be donated to The Nature Conservancy to support its work with natural climate solutions.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Upcycled Eggshell Jersey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: In an effort to reduce deadstock waste, Highsnobiety’s in-house brand is upcycling a range of its staple hoodies and T-shirts from previous seasons. The limited-edition collection arrives with nature-inspired graphics, such as this one with a flower print at the back. Meanwhile, the front of the top has embroidered Highsnobiety branding layered over a screen-printed design listing cities from around the world. A portion of the proceeds from this collection will be donated to The Nature Conservancy to support its work with natural climate solutions.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mias Knit T-Shirt Burgundy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten is here to take your t-shirt collection to the next level with a mature style constructed from soft viscose. The knit garment highlights the Belgian designer’s artful mastery of patterns, as it is adorned with a colorful striped print. Details include ribbed trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem, as the silhouette is cut for a traditional boxy, relaxed fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Perforated Details Tanktop
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Perforated Tank Top is included in Jean Paul Gaultier’s retro-futuristic Cyber collection, which consists of polarizing ready-to-wear styles that point to the house’s iconic ‘90s archives. Crafted from a stretchy nylon and elastane blend designed to form to the body, the garment features a crew neck and is characterized by circular perforations that line the front and back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Le Debardeur Macio Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Le Debardeur Macio is a more mature, luxe take on the summer tank top. Crafted from a soft cotton blend, the seasonal garment features checked jacquard and is detailed with a square neckline, wide straps, and contrasting contoured edges.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: S24-PR-C Pima Cotton T-shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The S24-PR-C is a seasonal t-shirt style crafted from ultra-soft pima cotton. The tee features short sleeves and a traditional rib knit crew neck, with silk screenprint detailing implemented on the front, back, and sleeve. It is cut in an oversized fit for an extra comfortable and fashion-forward wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: S25-PR-C Pima Cotton Sleeveless T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The S25-PR-C is a seasonal t-shirt style crafted from ultra-soft pima cotton. The tee is sleeveless and features a traditional rib knit crew neck, with silk screenprint detailing implemented on the front as well as the back. It is cut in an oversized fit for an extra comfortable and fashion-forward wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Celebrating Salone del Mobile, a yearly design and furniture fair which is the largest of its kind, this graphic t-shirt is designed with a small chest print on the front and a large back graphic that highlight the Milanese event. Arriving in an off-white, “eggshell” colorway, it has a slightly oversized fit. Having launched in 1961 and previously showcased works by the likes of Ettore Sottsass and Aldo Rossi, Salone del Mobile runs as part of Milan Design Week and has become the foremost global event for the furnishing and design sector.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Tank Top White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Prayer T-Shirt is a new seasonal graphic style from Patta. Produced in lightweight cotton, the short-sleeve top features a traditional rib knit crew neck, with illustrated artwork screenprinted on the front. Graphic tees remain as important to Patta as its sneaker drops and collaborative releases. They serve as a street canvas for the brand to get its message out there to the world.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Big Piquet
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Putting a spin on a classic knitwear style, this design from Our Legacy comes with an oversized fit for optimum comfort. Crafted from an Italian heavy cotton ribbed knit, the natural characteristics of the yarn mean that the shape of the jumper will adjust to the wearer over time. The polo collar features three mother-of-pearl buttons and a peaked, knit collar.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tanker T-Shirt
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from a Portuguese crochet mesh jersey, the loose-knit construction of this T-shirt's fabric makes it partially see-through and naturally ventilated. Cut with a slim, elongated fit, contrast flatlock seams are used across the shirt for a subtle finishing touch.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Welcum to Italy White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Carne Bollente styles, the Welcum to Italy T-Shirt is characterized by sex-positive artwork that encourages people to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The design pairs a versatile streetwear staple with a scenic sex illustration, injecting a bit of playful energy into the elevated basic. Constructed from 100% organic cotton to lower environmental impact, the tee is unisex, with screenprinted artwork implemented at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Description: Yohji Yamamoto has used his Y-3 label, made together with adidas, as his playground for finding the sweet spot between fashion and sportswear for over 20 years. On this casual t-shirt, the collaborative line uses a relaxed, slightly oversized fit and crepe cotton fabric to create a style inspired by outdoor wear. A color that Yamamoto is famous for using, it arrives in all-black with subtle logo detailing on the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Description: AGR’s luxury knitwear is characterized by bold colors and high-quality materials. Styles like the Wellness Tank Top draw from the brand’s London roots and the city’s diverse culture, all while challenging traditional knitwear themes. Made from a rib knit cotton fabric, this sleeveless top includes a vibrant ombre print design that will instantly inject color into your wardrobe. It features a scoop neckline and is cut in a standard tank fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: De-Janys-Fsc Denim Top Light Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Channeling a bold yet delicate aesthetic, the Denim Top is designed with a bra silhouette, featuring wide straps and hidden back fastening. The fabric is solarized to give it a sun-bleached look, combined with dévoré to expose the inner material construction and ultimately create a lace effect.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Spray Dyed Oversize Tee Yellow

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirts Three Pack London Grey

Cut in a regular fit, the tee is crafted from 100% organic cotton and detailed with the fashion house’s signature four stitches at the back just below the neckline.

Cut in a slim fit, the sleeveless top offers a form-fitting look you can dress up or down.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Stockholm 1996 T-Shirt Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This cotton Acne Studios tee is a nod to the founding of the luxury fashion house, featuring its year of birth and headquarters location on the front. A relaxed-fitting unisex style, the short-sleeve top boasts a sprayed finish and distressed detailing at the neckline, cuffs, and hem for an aged look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: S28-PR-B Organic Cotton T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Acronym continues to reimagine classic silhouettes like the graphic t-shirt. The S28-PR-B is characterized by a distinctive double hem, allowing you to tuck the lower hem into your pants for air-compartmentalization, leaving the upper hem loose and visible. Cut in a straight fit, the intriguing style is crafted from 100% organic cotton jersey and decorated with printed motifs at the chest and back. Leave it to Acronym to take the common t-shirt to another level.

tshirts_and_tops.Description: What appears to be two shirts is actually one unique layered design by Acronym. The S29-PR-B is a single top with asymmetric long sleeves, designed to look like one short-sleeve and one longsleeve top worn together. Cut in a straight fit, the distinctive garment is produced in 100% organic cotton jersey and decorated with printed detailing at the chest and running down the right sleeve. tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ahluwalia opts for a quarter zip instead of buttons on this new seasonal polo style. The short-sleeve top is produced in organic cotton, showcasing an artisanal chain stitching technique, as well as pistachio applique and beading details for a more eye-catching look. The design is made complete with an arching Ahluwalia logo, which is embroidered front and center.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mae Long-Sleeve Polo Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Ahluwalia’s new seasonal polos are made with a quarter zip at the neck as opposed to more traditional button placket. This particular style is brought to life with fiery bands of color implemented in a striped pattern. Produced in 100% organic cotton, the long-sleeve top is detailed with ribbed trims and cut in a boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Embroidered Strawberry JWA T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: JW Anderson’s latest collection is infused with playful strawberry artwork that has us thirsting for summer. Styles like the Embroidered JWA T-Shirt are embellished with bold designs of the fruit, here positioned overtop vibrant JWA embroidery. The short-sleeve tee is produced in cotton and offers a lightweight, relaxed fit to anyone who puts it on. This one’s best paired with shorts and sandals on sunny days when you have absolutely nothing on the schedule.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Organic Cotton Logo T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Stamp Logo T-Shirt is a staple Acne Studios style. Made from a midweight, organically-grown cotton, the short-sleeve top is decidedly minimal, simply branded with a small Acne Studios stamp logo front and center. The tee is offered in a series of  neutral colorways for easy matching from season to season.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo T-Shirt Mauve
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Much of what we do at Highsnobiety revolves around the fashion industry. Our new logo T-shirt is a celebration of such, specifically paying homage to the fashion capitals of the world. The cities of Berlin, Milan, London, New York, Los Angeles, Paris, and Tokyo are highlighted in a graphic print front and center, where our HS logo is then embroidered over top. As part of our second BeachFriendz delivery for Summer 2021, this T-shirt is for fashion enthusiasts and fans of Highsnobiety alike. Wear it loud and proud.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: CK50 T-shirt
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Lightweight cotton t-shirt with a classic fit. Screen-printed graphics designed by Fergus Purcell, the man behind the iconic Palace logo. Ribbed neckline, logo patch sewn to the back. Worldwide exclusive for Highsnobiety Shop.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: S/S Delray Shirt Glassy Pink/Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The camp shirt is summer’s must-have style. Carhartt’s Delray is a lightweight option woven from a soft cotton blend. It features a traditional camp collar and buttoned front, with intricate logo embroidery applied to the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: It's The Wurst! T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaborative t-shirt offers a new take on the classic tourist tee. Featuring the saucy glizzy and fries staple printed across the back with greetings from our home city, this organic cotton t-shirt is detailed with a washed finish for a pre-loved look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mia Problemo SS Tee White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Mia Problemo Tee arrives in celebration of Aries' new label, No Problemo. Crafted from 100% cotton, the short-sleeve top is adorned with a graphic print featuring Lebanese-American media personality Mia Khalifa on the front. Additional details include rib knit trim at the crew neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twisted Shoulder Tank Top Beige Spray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This unique Y/Project garment is a twisted take on the traditional tank top. Produced in 100% cotton, it features infinity style construction that creates a twisted effect at the shoulders, leaving you with a more distinctive look. The top is detailed with ribbed trims and embellished with a Y/Project logo, which is embroidered onto the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Touch With The Eyes Tank Top Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Carne Bollente styles, the Touch With The Eyes Tank Top is defined by sex-positive artwork that encourages everyone to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The sleeveless garment is cut for a slim, cropped fit from a tencel blend fabric and detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Home Jersey Shirt Black/Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Home Jersey Shirt is a sporty style produced in 100% polyester. It is cut for a relaxed fit and features a spread collar as well as long sleeves with rib knit cuffs. Wales Bonner iconography is applied to the chest to brand this new sportswear design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Power Dry Jersey Raglan Long-Sleeve T-Shirt Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Power Dry T-Shirt is crafted from Polartec's polyester Power Dry material using double knit construction with different knitting yarns on both sides. The garment is moisture-wicking and quick-drying, and incorporates a deodorant stitch in the sewing thread to reduce sweat odor.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Dream State Quarter-Zip Sweater Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This colorful piece by Bode draws inspiration from a floral design crocheted in the 1940s. The captivating motif is in turn replicated throughout the silhouette. The sweater is crafted from 100% cotton and features a spread collar with quarter-zip closure, in addition to ribbed trims at the collar, cuffs, and hem.
