Constructed from a soft lyocell blend, the top is cut in a cropped silhouette for a more distinctive look, with printed detailing implemented in all-over fashion.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hieroclits Long-Sleeve Top Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Carne Bollente styles, the Hieroclits Long-Sleeve is characterized by sex-positive artwork that encourages people to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The design pairs a versatile streetwear staple with a scenic sex illustration, injecting a bit of playful energy into the elevated basic. Constructed from a soft lyocell blend, the top is cut in a cropped silhouette for a more distinctive look, with printed detailing implemented in all-over fashion.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3D Knit Top Brown/Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from a lightweight nylon blend, the 3D Knit Top is designed for use as a technical layer or on its own. Contrasting knit panels are executed in insulating and breathable Dryarn fibers, as the garment also incorporates elastane to ensure a closer and comfortable fit. The sleeveless top draws attention with a distinctive all-over pattern and is further embellished with subtle logo detailing.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Thermal T-Shirt Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This monochrome thermal t-shirt is crafted entirely from cotton and arrives as part of our tribute to the Big Apple. The short-sleeved T-shirt is detailed with a waffle knit texture that retains heat and provides breathability and is finished with printed logos at the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Family-owned since 1963, Dave’s New York has grown to become the hub for workwear and casual clothing in the bustling city. Crafted from midweight 230gsm cotton, this short-sleeved tee is detailed with co-branded logos at the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Looking For Miracles T-Shirt Bone
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Looking For Miracles is a seasonal t-shirt style by Jil Sander. Defined by a layered design, the short-sleeve tee is produced in cotton and features a classic rib knit crew neck. A contrasting print is applied to the back of the garment to brand the piece and signal the new collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ningen-sei Plant Dyed T-Shirt Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Plant Dyed T-Shirt is a part of Human Made’s Ningen-sei capsule collection focusing on Japanese culture. Crafted from 100% cotton, the tee is woven with uneven slub yarn and features a unique texture created through the use of plant-based dye. The brand’s iconic heart logo is incorporated onto the front and back of the silhouette to definitively brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fissato T-Shirt Lead Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island continues its material research with its latest seasonal collection. Crafted from organic cotton, this short-sleeve t-shirt is treated with the brand's "Fissato" effect that creates a three-dimensional appearance. The tee is finished with overlock seams and a Stone Island badge at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: It Does Matter What You Think T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The It Does Matter What You Think T-Shirt is a seasonal graphic style from Patta. Produced in lightweight cotton, the short-sleeve top features a traditional rib knit crew neck, with a large screenprinted graphic on the front and screenprinted Patta branding on the back. Graphic tees remain as important to Patta as its sneaker drops and collaborative releases. They serve as a street canvas for the brand to get its message out there to the world.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Oversize Laced T-Shirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A standout design from the French designer's archives, the oversized lace tee is just what your wardrobe is missing. Detailed with laces that run along the back to the sleeves, this oversized tee arrives in a versatile white finish with a contrasting logo at the center.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Bat Tee Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bat Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the short-sleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with a playful multicolored print by artist Isabel Kang on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Cotton Animal Eyes Tee Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Animal Eyes Tee is made exclusively for Story mfg.’s seasonal Gentle Fullness collection. Constructed from 60% recycled cotton and 40% organic cotton, the short-sleeve top is eco-dyed, decorated with a multicolored print of animal eyes on the front of the silhouette. The shirt is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and features a relaxed, boxy fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cropped T-Shirt Dusty Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A switch-up from your standard t-shirt, this seasonal Acne Studios style offers a cropped fit. It is crafted from organically-grown cotton that is garment-dyed to create a fade-out effect. The short-sleeve top is cut for a relaxed fit and minimally branded with Acne’s face logo patch, which emerges at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tania Mouraud T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Presented at the historic gallery Palais de Tokyo, Il morso delle termiti is an exhibition that re-contextualizes the art of graffiti. This T-shirt has been created for the exhibition and features a piece by Tania Mouraud, one of the artists presenting work as part of the show. The graphic top is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: T-Shirt Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Having started life in the ‘50s as a comic strip, Le Petit Nicolas has grown to become one of the most recognizable children's characters. With an estimated 20 million books sold worldwide as well as having its own movie adaptations, we’ve collaborated with the iconic French series. Featuring original illustrations from the books, this graphic top is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Degrade Linen T-Shirt Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Winnie top is produced in a cotton-linen blend and showcases a vibrant gradient design. It is detailed with a traditional rib knit crew neck and defined by a zip vent that is incorporated at the left shoulder.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Optimist Polo Shirt
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Optimist Polo is a signature Wales Bonner style produced in 100% cotton. Offering a cropped fit, the short-sleeve shirt is brought to life with textured stripes in vibrant tones. Details include a classic polo collar and three-button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Scale Tank
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Scale Tank is a vibrant Wales Bonner design made from 100% cotton with contrasting yarns for added texture. The style is cut for a slim fit and brought to life with alternating stripes in orange and emerald hues.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sbagliato T-Shirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving with a small co-branded, woven label at the chest, the back of this t-shirt presents Bar Basso’s most iconic drink: the Negroni Sbagliato. Invented by owner Maurizio Stocchetto, it is served in a massive scenographic glass, as shown in the graphic print. As part of our celebration of all things Italian for Milan Design Week, we’ve paired up with Bar Basso, one of the oldest and most influential cocktail bars in Milan. Over the years, the historical establishment has become closely associated with the city’s art and fashion scenes, further solidifying it as a true cultural fixture in Milan.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: AWD Graphic T-Shirt Alumina
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made in collaboration with and wander, this adidas Terrex tee highlights the connection between humans and Earth, featuring bold graphics and reflective prints. The loose-fitting top is crafted from an ultra-soft cotton blend that balances the natural feel of cotton and the utility of recycled polyester, as adidas partners with Better Cotton to support more sustainable farming.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Horse Airbrush T-Shirt Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Horse Airbrush T-Shirt is a fun, vibrant style by Stockholm Surfboard Club. Crafted from organic cotton single jersey, the short-sleeve top is decorated with a colorful all-over airbrush print that is sure to draw immediate attention and liven up any outfit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Digi Printed Gradient Tank Top Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: AGR’s luxury knitwear is characterized by bold colors and high-quality materials. Styles like the Digi Printed Tank Top draw from the brand’s London roots and the city’s diverse culture, all while challenging traditional knitwear themes. Made from a rib knit cotton fabric, this sleeveless top boasts a vibrant gradient print design that will instantly inject a splash of color into your wardrobe. It features a round neckline and is cut in a standard tank fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Skyline Tee Tinto Capo Cream
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Skyline Tee is a direct nod to Lourdes’ New York City roots, as the seasonal top is emblazoned with a graphic depicting the city’s skyline. Also incorporated in the design is a classic Lourdes logo, one that features a shadow effect. The short-sleeve t-shirt is produced in 100% cotton and cut in a boxy fit for a cozy look and wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Bjorn Logo Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bjorn Hoodie is defined by a playful Stockholm Surfboard Club insignia implemented on the back of the garment. Made from a soft organic cotton loopback jersey, the cozy pullover is detailed with traditional hoodie design elements like an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Dry Breathable Hoodie Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This and wander outerwear style is made using a water-repellent, stretch polyester material, featuring a pattern design that improves freedom of movement. Ventilation holes are incorporated throughout to enhance breathability, as the style is then outfitted with a stand collar, fixed hood, front button fastening, and button cuffs. A flap pocket is applied at the chest, where you will also find a branded carabiner attached.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: One Point Hooded Sweatshirt Heather
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple Gramicci style, the One Point Hoodie is crafted from a highly durable French terry fabric that doesn’t lose its shape and forms to the wearer with use. It is made with classic hoodie design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, front pouch pocket, and ribbed trims, and is minimally branded with the brand’s running mono logo, which is embroidered at the left chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ich bin ein Berliner Hoodie Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carne Bollente's latest collection is an ode to borderless origins and sees Berlin as the theme of its latest drop. Ideal for any season, this classic navy hoodie is crafted from organic cotton and features a kinky embroidered graphic on the front as a nod to its sex-positive ideology, as well as images of the Berlin skyline at night.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Berghain Days Hoodie Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carne Bollente's latest collection is an ode to borderless origins and sees Berlin as the theme of its latest drop. Ideal for any season, this classic gray hoodie is crafted from organic cotton and features a kinky embroidered graphic on the front as a nod to its sex-positive ideology. On the back, an image of currywurst and pommes emerges in line with its Greeting from Berlin collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Lens Detail Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This cozy C.P. Company pullover is defined by the brand's signature lens detail, which is incorporated into the left sleeve pocket. Made from 100% cotton, the garment is cut for a relaxed fit and features traditional hoodie design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front kangaroo pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleece Sweatshirt Ivy Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This staple C.P. Company sweatshirt is made with lightweight cotton fleece for a flexible fit and garment-dyed to increase chromatic depth and intensity throughout. It features a traditional crew neck and is detailed with ribbed trims at the neckline, cuffs and hem, while showcasing the brand’s signature lens applied to the left sleeve pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: No Problemo Sweatshirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The No Problemo Sweatshirt arrives in celebration of Aries' new label of the same name. Crafted from 100% cotton, the long-sleeve garment is adorned with a contrasting No Problemo graphic print on the front. Additional details include rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mini Problemo Sweatshirt Ecru
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Mini Problemo Sweatshirt arrives in celebration of Aries' new label, No Problemo. Crafted from 100% brushed back cotton, the long-sleeve garment is adorned with a contrasting No Problemo graphic print on the front. Additional details include rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crewneck Sweatshirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Crewneck Sweatshirt is a staple style from Nigo and Human Made. Adorned with the brand's signature heart emblem on the front, the comfy crewneck is heavily vintage-inspired. The garment is knit from a polyester blend fabric and features traditional design elements including rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Alieno Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Alieno Hoodie arrives in celebration of Aries' new label, No Problemo. Crafted from 100% cotton, the cozy pullover is adorned with a contrasting No Problemo graphic print on the front, in addition to complementary artwork on the back. Other details include an adjustable drawstring hood and rib knit trims at the cuffs and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: No Problemo Sweatshirt Grey Marl
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The No Problemo Sweatshirt arrives in celebration of Aries' new label of the same name. Crafted from 100% cotton, the long-sleeve garment is adorned with a contrasting No Problemo graphic print on the front. Additional details include rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Hoodie Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Maison Margiela hoodie is decorated with the fashion house's numerical logo, which is embroidered onto the front of the garment. Constructed from 100% cotton, the cozy pullover features a brushed interior, in addition to a fixed hood and ribbed trims at the cuffs and hem. It is cut for an oversized fit to ensure a more comfortable wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Evergreen Pinched Logo Sweatshirt Evergreen Vintage Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This crewneck sweatshirt from Y/Project is characterized by the brand’s signature pinched embroidered logo, implemented on the front. The staple garment is produced in 100% organic cotton and detailed with traditional crewneck design elements including ribbed trims. It is a genderless design fit for wear all year round, from brisk fall mornings to breezy summer nights and everything in between.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Essential QZ Crew TNF Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Designed for year-round comfort both on and off the trail, this TNF Quarter-Zip is constructed from a warm, soft cotton-polyester blend fabric. It features a mock neck collar with a reverse coil quarter-zip, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket. The piece is finished with The North Face logos embroidered at the left chest and back right shoulder.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Full-Zip Sweatshirt Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This versatile Stone Island outerwear style arrives in a neutral gray colorway that caters to repeat wear. Crafted from cotton, the garment is detailed with rib knit trims at the cuffs and bottom band, while featuring full-zip fastening at the front. Buttoned pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette, which is finished with the brand's signature removable logo badge applied to the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Always On Top Hooded Sweater Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Always On Top style blends two pieces into one. The inner hoodie is produced in a 400gsm loopback cotton sweat, paired with an outer layer t-shirt produced in a 300gsm single jersey with an all-over camouflage print. The hoodie is outfitted with an adjustable drawstring hood and features a ribbed hem, while the t-shirt is branded with the Patta Script logo at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Some Like It Hot Hooded Sweater Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Some Like It Hot Hoodie is crafted from a 450gsm soft brushed back cotton and arrives in a relaxed, boxy fit with ribbed cuffs and hem. Detailed with Patta's signature script logo on the chest, the heavyweight hoodie features a large embroidered graphic on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Classic Zip Up Hooded Sweater Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Classic Zip Up Hooded Sweater is a basic Patta style offered in neutral colorways with minimal branding. Constructed from 450gsm soft brushed back sweat in a cotton and polyester blend, the garment is cut for a relaxed fit with dropped shoulders. It features an adjustable drawstring hood, two-way front zip fastening, ribbed cuffs and hem, and a front pouch pocket. The brand's signature Script logo is screenprinted onto the chest to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Baker Hoodie Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This navy hoodie is made in collaboration with Beigel Bake, the famed East End eatery known for its salt beef bagel and 24/7 access. The heavyweight hoodie is crafted entirely from cotton and features co-branded logos on the chest along with a print on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: FIRE Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This black hoodie is made in collaboration with Chiltern Firehouse, the celebrated hotel that’s housed in one of London’s first firehouses. The heavyweight hoodie is crafted entirely from cotton and features a print on the back along with co-branded logos on the chest.This hoodie is made to celebrate Not in London, our first "Not In" city series in the English cultural capital. The multimedia event curated by Highsnobiety includes some of our favorite brands, musicians, and creators across the world.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Not In London Fleece Hoodie Dark Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This heavyweight hoodie is made entirely from 400 gsm cotton fleece and arrives in a dark gray colorway. Detailed with a Not In London graphic print across the front, the hoodie also features a pouch pocket and a contrasting embroidered logo on the chest.This hoodie is made to celebrate Not in London, our first "Not In" city series in the English cultural capital. The multimedia event curated by Highsnobiety includes some of our favorite brands, musicians, and creators across the world.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Diamond Life Knit Sweater Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This KNITWRTH sweater is detailed with an allover print resembling the Nigerian-born, British superstar Sade. Crafted entirely from cotton in an oversized fit, the knit sweater is embellished with portraits of the singer that were captured months before the release of her band’s iconic album Diamond Life (1984).

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sex Hoodie Navy Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Carne Bollente styles, the Sex Hoodie is characterized by sex-positive artwork that encourages people to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The design pairs a versatile streetwear staple with a scenic sex illustration, injecting a bit of playful energy into the elevated basic. Constructed from 100% organic cotton to lower environmental impact, the pullover is unisex, with standout iconography implemented on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sex Hoodie Melange Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like all Carne Bollente styles, the Sex Hoodie is characterized by sex-positive artwork that encourages people to embrace their own sexuality and kinks. The design pairs a versatile streetwear staple with a scenic sex illustration, injecting a bit of playful energy into the elevated basic. Constructed from 100% organic cotton to lower environmental impact, the pullover is unisex, with standout iconography implemented on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleece Hoodie Navy Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island’s brushed cotton fleece sweatshirt is designed as an alternative to the array of graphic hoodies that fill most closets. Free from branded clutter, the pullover simply boasts the label’s signature compass logo patch at the left arm. As with many Stone Island styles, the hoodie is garment-dyed to give it a distinctive look that further distinguishes it from other pullovers.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleece Hoodie Musk
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island’s brushed cotton fleece sweatshirt is designed as an alternative to the array of graphic hoodies that fill most closets. Free from branded clutter, the pullover simply boasts the label’s signature compass logo patch at the left arm. As with many Stone Island styles, the hoodie is garment-dyed to give it a distinctive look that further distinguishes it from other pullovers.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Half-Zip Sweatshirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This cozy Stone Island half-zip is knit in a soft cotton fabric, arriving in a versatile white colorway that makes way for repeat wear. It is outfitted with a funnel neck collar, half-zip fastening, and rib knit trims. To subtly brand the garment, a Stone Island logo badge is incorporated onto the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment-Dyed Crewneck Sweatshirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: While best known for its technical outerwear, Stone Island also offers versatile staples like this fleece sweatshirt in an array of monochromatic colorways that match virtually everything. This particular style is crafted from 100% cotton and showcases the brand’s signature garment-dyeing technique. The body is absent of SI branding; instead, you will find the label’s removal logo badge implemented at the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment-Dyed Crewneck Sweatshirt Natural Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: While best known for its technical outerwear, Stone Island also offers versatile staples like this fleece sweatshirt in an array of monochromatic colorways that match virtually everything. This particular style is crafted from 100% cotton and showcases the brand’s signature garment-dyeing technique. The body is absent of SI branding; instead, you will find the label’s removal logo badge implemented at the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment-Dyed Crewneck Sweatshirt Navy Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: While best known for its technical outerwear, Stone Island also offers versatile staples like this fleece sweatshirt in an array of monochromatic colorways that match virtually everything. This particular style is crafted from 100% cotton and showcases the brand’s signature garment-dyeing technique. The body is absent of SI branding; instead, you will find the label’s removal logo badge implemented at the left sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Minimal Hoodie Chocolate Fondant
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Lemaire top is a minimalistic reinterpretation of a classic garment. It is crafted from a blend of cotton and linen materials with a very soft hand, ultimately enhancing the overall comfort level. The loose-fitting style is pocketless but does feature a classic hood that can be adjusted with flat cotton drawstrings. Double topstitching is implemented at the collar, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double-Faced Piqué Hoodie Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our collection with Lacoste celebrates the pioneering athleisure brand, uniting our love for casual competition and the lifestyle that surrounds it. The Logo Hoodie is one of many pieces from the drop, crafted from a custom double-face piqué fabric constructed specifically for this collection. The boxy fit is accented with thick ribbing at the hem and cuffs while an appliqué Lacoste logo is embroidered on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tri-Tone Crewneck Sweatshirt
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Order your regular size.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Haffel Sweater Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Quintessential and crafted for any occasion, Dries van Noten's Haffel Sweater arrives in an all-black hue that's made from heavyweight 320gsm cotton. The long-sleeve pullover is cut in an oversized fit and features a ribbed crewneck collar, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Haxel Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Haxel Hoodie showcases Dries van Noten’s avant-garde craftsmanship, with contemporary updates to a wardrobe staple. The pullover style is constructed from 100% cotton, defined by an exaggerated hood with two sets of drawstrings. More traditional design details include a front pouch pocket and ribbed trims, as the garment is cut in a boxy, oversized fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Zip-Up Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new Human Made garment is a full-zip hoodie style predominantly knit from cotton. It features a fixed hood, rib knit trims at the cuffs and hem, and front pockets. The brand's signature heart logo emerges on the front of the silhouette, while complementary printed branding is showcased on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavyweight Logo Hoodie Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Nigo and Human Made deliver a new playful graphic hoodie style adorned with colorful iconography on the front. The brand's signature heart logo is then embroidered on the left sleeve to serve as additional embellishment. Knit from 100% cotton, the heavyweight pullover features traditional hoodie design elements including a fixed hood, rib knit trims at the cuffs and hem, and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Sweatshirt White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Logo Sweatshirt is a staple style from Nigo and Human Made. Adorned with the brand's signature heart emblem on the front, the comfy crewneck is further embellished with a small logo tag on the left sleeve. The garment is predominantly knit from cotton and features traditional design elements including rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Hood Soot
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic hoodie. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Heavy Hood is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit for a more fashion-forward wear, detailed with ribbed trims and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Standardized Hoodie Muted Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Basic Pigment Dye Pocket Crewneck Sweater Delicioso
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Patta is responsible for delivering some of the most sought-after basics in streetwear. Styles like the Basic Crewneck arrive season after season in new and returning colorways, produced from high quality materials. This particular version of the sweater is constructed from a 450gsm brushback cotton, featuring the brand’s trademark script logo screen printed at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Mohair Hoodie Hazel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Jil Sander elevates the timeless silhouette with a brushed alpaca-wool blend that falls in line with the brand's minimalist aesthetics. The hoodie arrives in a versatile hazel colorway with contrasting drawstrings at the hood, a kangaroo pouch, and tonal embroidery at the ribbed cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hug The Earth Hoodie Heather Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This seasonal hoodie style by Fucking Awesome is adorned with a custom "Hug The Earth" graphic print that incorporates the brand logo front and center. Available in a classic Heather Gray colorway, the cozy pullover is constructed from a soft cotton-polyester blend fabric and features traditional hoodie design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 Hoodie Center Olive Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An update on PAF's 4.0+ hoodie, this new sweater arrives with an enhanced fit in a tonal olive hue. Made with a cozy polar fleece shell, the hoodie is detailed with a ribbed hem and a two-way asymmetric zip opening that wraps across the chest and hood.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SW Gargoyle Hoodie Ash Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, the Gargoyle Hoodie is adorned with a screeprinted graphic depicting a gargoyle on the front of the 100% cotton pullover. The garment then features traditional design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: You Go Hoodie Natural
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The You Go Hoodie is made in Canada from 100% cotton. It features traditional design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket. The style is defined by a multicolor S graphic with a Saintwoods logo implemented on the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: SW Sweatshirt Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The SW Sweatshirt is a staple Saintwoods style made in Canada from 100% cotton. Cut for a standard boxy fit, the garment is detailed with traditional rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem, and minimally branded with a small contrasting hit of embroidery at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Run 4 Yer Life Hoodie Alpine Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Run 4 Yer Life Hoodie is a playful Saintwoods style decorated with graphic detailing depicting a person being chased by a bear. Underneath, you will a complementary brand logo in a contrasting shade. The garment then features traditional design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Arch Hoodie Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An embroidered Saintwoods logo decorates the front of the Arch Hoodie, which arrives this season in a classic navy colorway. It is made in Canada from 100% cotton, with traditional design elements that include an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a front pouch pocket.

Acne Studios delivers accordingly with a minimal pullover hoodie that reappears from collection to collection. Offered in neutral colorways with small branding on the front, the garment is easy to match with just about anything.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Hoodie Black

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Smooth Soft Pullover Hoodie Blue/Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Though it may appear to be your average hoodie, this relaxed-fitting pullover by Auralee is crafted with high-quality cotton. The sweatshirt is slowly made on a hang knitting machine, giving it a rich and luxurious texture with lots of elasticity.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Mohair Knit Hoodie Jade Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An elevated take on the traditional pullover hoodie, this lightweight sweater by AURALEE is crafted from soft South African super-kid mohair with a natural fiber wool core. Cut in a relaxed fit and detailed with long pile hair in a pleasant brushed texture, the hoodie is finished with a front pouch pocket, ribbed cuffs and hem, and adjustable drawstrings at the hood.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hooded Sweatshirt Vintage Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This cozy Acne Studios hoodie is crafted from a soft organic cotton fabric with a faded finish that gives it a vintage, worn appearance. Cut for a boxy, relaxed fit, the hoodie offers a timeless wear suited for everyone.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hooded Taos Sweat Flint/Garment-Dyed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Taos is a seasonal hoodie style from Carhartt WIP. Crafted from a midweight cotton fabric, the cozy pullover is garment-dyed for a more distinctive look. It features traditional design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and front pouch pocket, with a small logo label incorporated into the seam. The garment is cut for a loose fit to ensure maximum comfort.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nuts To Soup Crewneck Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This fleece crewneck is part of our collaboration with NTS and features the music platform’s full name printed across the chest. The top arrives with a ribbed crewneck, cuffs, and hem and features embroidered graphics on the right sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleece Flower Hoodie Ivory/Black

tshirts_and_tops.Name: AFFXWRKS Hoodie Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Luxo Jr. Sequence Hoodie Off-white
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our collaboration with Pixar explores its archival history and pays homage to its enduring innovation throughout the years. The Sequence Hoodie features scenes from the short film Luxo Jr. (1986). The heavyweight hoodie is finished with a co-branded woven label on the chest and arrives with ribbed cuffs and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Hoodie Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This graphic hoodie is part of our collaboration with Pixar which commemorates decades of technological innovation and explores its legendary archives. The Logo Hoodie is crafted from 320gsm cotton and is detailed with co-branded logos. The heavyweight hoodie is finished with a ribbed hem and cuffs, with Pixar’s Lamp and Ball embroidered on the right sleeve.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Climbing Gear Hooded Sweatshirt Brown Pigment
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A relaxed-fitting pullover style, the Climbing Gear Hoodie is adorned with a print of a mountain silhouette and the "Gramicci Climbing Gear" logo on the left chest and back. It is constructed from a soft cotton French terry material and detailed with traditional hoodie design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, ribbed trims, and front kangaroo pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: One Point Hooded Sweatshirt Ash Heather
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple Gramicci style, the One Point Hoodie is crafted from a highly durable French terry fabric that doesn’t lose its shape and forms to the wearer with use. It is made with classic hoodie design elements including an adjustable drawstring hood, front pouch pocket, and ribbed trims, and is minimally branded with the brand’s running mono logo, which is embroidered at the left chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fleece Hoodie Lemon
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A fluffy fleece style, this Jil Sander hoodie is sure to keep you warm and cozy all winter long. It is produced in a natural cotton fleece and arrives in a light Lemon colorway for adding a touch of color to your cold weather outfits. Details include a fixed hood and elasticated cuffs and hem, with zippered pockets incorporated onto the front of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Quarter-Zip Hoodie Navy

Detailed with a quarter-zip closure at the collar, the heavyweight hoodie is crafted from French terry cotton and features embroidered logos on the chest and above the cuff.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Paris' Best Embroidered Sweatshirt Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This heavyweight crewneck style from Y/Project is decorated with the brand's Paris' Best logo, which is embroidered at the chest in contrasting thread. Cut for a regular fit, the top is detailed with traditional rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Washed Crewneck Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Heavy Washed Crewneck arrives as part of our latest collaboration with BAPE in soft fleece fabric. The long-sleeved top is embellished with tonal co-branded logos printed at the rear and embroidered on the chest. Traditional elements like the ribbed crewneck collar, hem, and cuffs complete the style while woven brand tags provide a contrast in color.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Washed Crewneck Ivory
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Heavy Washed Crewneck arrives as part of our latest collaboration with BAPE in soft fleece fabric. The long-sleeved top is embellished with tonal co-branded logos printed at the rear and embroidered on the chest. Traditional elements like the ribbed crewneck collar, hem, and cuffs complete the style while woven brand tags provide a contrast in color.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Crewneck Eggshell

Cut for a regular fit in a light yellow hue, the long-sleeve top is detailed with a tonal Neu York print across the chest, an embroidered logo at the back, and traditional rib-knit trims at the crew neck and cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Hoodie Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pullover hoodie arrives in a soft brown hue with an embroidered chest logo and Neu York printed across the back. The midweight hoodie features a traditional front pouch pocket, adjustable drawstrings, and ribbed trims at the hem and cuffs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Hoodie Orange
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pullover hoodie arrives in a vibrant orange colorway with Neu York printed across the chest and back. The midweight hoodie features a traditional front pouch pocket, adjustable drawstrings, and ribbed cuffs and hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This black hoodie arrives as part of our tribute to Sant Ambroeus, the renowned Milanese eatery that has become a staple of NYC’s dining scene since 1982. Crafted from a midweight 320gsm cotton, this pullover hoodie features co-branded logos at the back center detailed with graphic prints and chain-stitched embroidery along with a woven brand tag on the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hoodie Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This gray hoodie arrives as part of our tribute to Dave’s New York, a family-owned shop that has remained a staple for workwear and casual clothing since 1963. Crafted from midweight 320gsm cotton, this pullover hoodie features co-branded logos at the chest and back center detailed with graphic prints.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crewneck Burgundy

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Classic Crew Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Per the name, this familiar style is a classic Martine Rose design, showcasing the brand’s scribble logo in contrasting print front and center. The staple crewneck is offered in a black and white colorway for easy matching, crafted from a soft cotton jersey fabric with traditional rib knit trims. A unisex style, the garment is cut for a relaxed fit to ensure a more comfortable wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Oversized Piped Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Piped Hoodie is an elevated pullover style that blends sportswear and streetwear sensibilities. Made from 100% cotton, the cozy garment is cut for an oversized fit and features an adjustable drawstring hood, rib knit trims, and a kangaroo pocket. Tonal Reebok logos are embroidered at the chest and hood to subtly embellish the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Oversized Piped Hoodie Sand
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Piped Hoodie is an elevated pullover style that blends sportswear and streetwear sensibilities. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Kicker Hoodie Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Kicker is a classic-fitting hoodie style arriving this season in a vibrant green colorway. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fluffy Fleece V2 White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios delivers a luxury aesthetic that is simple yet thoughtfully designed, with pieces like the Fluffy Fleece that are characterized by their quality construction and overall functionality, ultimately offering a glimpse into the future of fashion. This cozy style gives you a pullover option that features a hood for added protection. Crafted from a bonded 380gsm polyester sherpa, the comfy outerwear is equipped with reinforcement at the sleeves in the form of nylon ripstop elbow patches, while a zippered pouch at the waist provides you with a place to securely carry small everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hoodie Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This graphic style is made in celebration of one of Paris’ oldest and most beloved coffee houses. The Café de Flore x Highsnobiety hoodie is decorated with embroidery inspired by the typographic branding on the exterior awning of the Cafe. A Parisian landmark, Café de Flore is known for its famous clientele and close ties to the fashion industry, as each Paris Fashion Week attendees flock to the establishment like clockwork. The hoodie style is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Upcycled Pale Pink Hoodie

A portion of the proceeds from this collection will be donated to The Nature Conservancy to support its work with natural climate solutions.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sbagliato Hoodie Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving with a large red print, highlighting Bar Basso’s most iconic drink, and an overlaying co-branded label, this hoodie is part of our celebration of all things Italian for Milan Design Week. It is well known for its signature cocktail Negroni Sbagliato, a drink invented by owner Maurizio Stocchetto, which comes served in a massive scenographic glass. Over the years, the historical establishment has become closely associated with the city’s art and fashion scenes, further solidifying it as a true cultural fixture in Milan.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Face Logo Hoodie Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Acne Studios’ new seasonal collection is filled with staple garments that are primed and ready for repeat wear with each passing year. The Face Logo Hoodie is one key style you can rock for a cozy day around the house or out and about on the town — it’s comfy and stylish for either scenario. Offered in monochromatic colorways, the relaxed-fitting hoodie is designed to match pretty much everything. It’s crafted from organic cotton and embellished with the brand’s playful Face logo which is embroidered at the chest.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Hood Tar
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic hoodie. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Heavy Hood is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit for a more fashion-forward wear, detailed with ribbed trims and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Hood Brunette
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic hoodie. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Heavy Hood is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit for a more fashion-forward wear, detailed with ribbed trims and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Box Crew Cork
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the crewneck sweatshirt. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Box Crew is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit, detailed with ribbed trims and a V-notch sweat catcher.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Box Crew Brunette
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the crewneck sweatshirt. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Box Crew is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit, detailed with ribbed trims and a V-notch sweat catcher.

Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Heavy Hood is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit for a more fashion-forward wear, detailed with ribbed trims and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Box Crew Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the crewneck sweatshirt. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Box Crew is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The pullover style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit, detailed with ribbed trims and a V-notch sweat catcher.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Full Zip Cork
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic full zip fleece. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Full Zip is perfect for year-round wear, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The style is cut in a boxy, oversized fit, detailed with a hood, two front pockets, and ribbed trims.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Out Of Office Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Tongue-in-cheek expressions have become a signature part of HO HO COCO’s identity which can be found embroidered onto its range of headwear and the occasional piece of clothing, such as this hoodie. With a classic email sign-off embroidered on the chest, the hoodie is made from heavyweight organic cotton which is pre-shrunk.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment Dyed Hoodie Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A hoodie is a certified wardrobe staple, and our latest design focuses on subtle details which elevate the look. With its green colorway being produced through a garment dyeing process, white stitching on the body provides a contrasting pop of color. Meanwhile, on the bottom of the hoodie, a gradient color scheme is added to a stitched logo tab that indicates this is part of the Highsnobiety Giftshop: a curated selection of products showcasing our favorite gifts to exchange over the holiday period.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Garment Dyed Hoodie Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A hoodie is a certified wardrobe staple, and our latest design focuses on subtle details which elevate the look. With its navy colorway being produced through a garment-dyeing process, white stitching on the body provides a contrasting pop of color. Meanwhile, on the bottom of the hoodie, a gradient color scheme is added to a stitched logo tab that indicates this is part of the Highsnobiety Giftshop: a curated selection of products showcasing our favorite gifts to exchange over the holiday period.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Fleece Hoodie Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: When it’s time to ditch the graphic styles, opt for this mature monochromatic design by Winnie. The classic hoodie is produced in an ultra-soft cotton fleece fabric and made with quintessential design details including a drawstring hood and front pouch pocket. Cut in an oversized fit that is true to size, Winnie’s Cotton Fleece Hoodie is a cozy style perfect for lounging around and casual outings alike.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Eunify G-Dye Hoodie Potting Soil
tshirts_and_tops.Description: With its Eunify initiative, Souvenir Official has taken the blue and yellow flag of the European Union — an emblem of peace and unity — and turned it into a wearable conversation piece. This opinion-wear, as art director David Mallon calls it, allows the label to express its own views and subsequently convey powerful social messaging to fans. The pro-E.U. hoodie is a symbol of freedom and acceptance, as a single star from the European Union flag has been removed and placed on the back of the fleece pullover alongside the E.U. hotline number in hopes of starting a dialogue.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: HS Sports Logo Hoodie Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The epitome of casual cool comfort, the heavyweight Logo Hoodie is done up in an inviting green colorway with contrasting HS Sports branding implemented front and center. The cozy style is cut in a boxy fit, best worn one size up for a more comfy, laid-back look and feel. Highsnobiety’s newest flagship, Highsnobiety Sports explores the intersection between sport and style with in-house apparel and accessories, as well as collaborations alongside leading brands specializing in athletics and lifestyle. The inaugural drop largely delves into the worlds of running, cycling, hiking, climbing, and swimming, encompassing everything from tees, hoodies, and shorts, to footwear, swimwear, bags, water bottles, and more.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Hoodie Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Maison Margiela flips the script with the familiar Logo Hoodie, which showcases an upside-down Margiela Paris motif embroidered front and center. Around back, you’ll find the luxury fashion house’s signature four stitches moniker in white thread. A staple Margiela style, the Logo Hoodie arrives season after season, yet always sells out in a hurry. Do yourself a favor and snag the ever-in-demand piece before it disappears once again.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Staples Hoodie Sky Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The versatile pullover is crafted from a 400gsm heavyweight cotton that is noticeably breathable and an embroidered Highsnobiety logo brands the hoodie in a contrasting shade front and center. You can opt for the heather grey and black colorways for a more neutral look, while the baby blue and lush green iterations help to brighten things up a bit. Either way, each color can easily be combined with past Highsnobiety collections as you continue to build your wardrobe with our selection of staples. The fit here is true to size, but we like the look of going one size up for a more relaxed, comfortable wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: CK50 Women's cropped Hoody
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Cropped, mid-weight cotton hoodie with a classic fit. Screen-printed graphics designed by Fergus Purcell, the man behind the iconic Palace logo. Branded eyelets, ribbed cuffs and hem, logo patch sewn to the back. Worldwide exclusive for Highsnobiety Shop.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Patch Hooded Jacket Lead Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island’s Logo Patch Hooded Jacket is a versatile staple primed and ready for year-round use. Offered in a neutral lead grey colorway, you can wear it with pretty much everything, as it is free from over-the-top branding — instead opting for a subtle logo badge at the left sleeve, a design element that is completely removable. The jacket is made from 100% cotton and has been subjected to Stone Island’s trademark garment-dyeing process to give it a more distinctive look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Washed Zip Hoodie Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Taking cues from BAPE’s classic silhouettes, our fourth collection with the brand arrives in a trio of colorways. The Heavy Washed Hoodie is detailed by its tonal palette and soft fleece texture. Embroidered logos can be found on the chest, while co-branded woven tags appear on the ribbed cuffs, seams, and front pocket. A full zip closure completes the look while branded aglets on the drawstring add the finishing touches.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Satin Padded Hoodie Lilac
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to the classic hoodie, this standout Gerrit Jacob style is defined by a distinctive graphic print. The comfy pullover is made from 100% viscose and fully lined, while featuring a fixed hood, dropped shoulders, balloon sleeves, and elasticized cuffs. It is cut for a relaxed, boxy fit with elongated sleeves for an eye-catching look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Flatiron Building Hoodie Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Renowned for its unique triangular shape and becoming a National Historic Landmark in 1989, it’s fair to say the Flatiron Building has achieved icon status. This limited-edition hoodie was made in collaboration with At The Moment and is detailed with biodegradable graphic prints on the chest and back with a small text that alludes to the building’s history.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crewneck Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This black crewneck arrives as part of our tribute to Dave’s New York, a family-owned shop that has remained a staple for workwear and casual clothing since 1963.  This midweight crewneck arrives as part of our collaboration with the shop and features printed co-branded logos at the chest and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Classic Fleece Hoodie Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An elevated take on traditional winterwear, our classic fleece hoodie is sure to keep you warm during the cold season ahead. Coming in a boxy, subtly oversized fit, the only piece of branding comes in the form of a pull tab which sits on the left side.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Varsity Sweatshirt Soft Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Varsity Sweatshirt is a seasonal Affix style produced in a midweight fleece-back cotton jersey fabric. Cut for a relaxed fit, the cozy garment is detailed with rib knit trims at the crew neck, cuffs, and hem, and embellished with a contrasting varsity print on the front.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hoodie Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This graphic style is made in celebration of one of Paris’ oldest and most beloved coffee houses. The Café de Flore x Highsnobiety hoodie is decorated with a back print inspired by the design of the physical menu you receive in the cafe. A Parisian landmark, Café de Flore is known for its famous clientele and close ties to the fashion industry, as each Paris Fashion Week attendees flock to the establishment like clockwork. The hoodie style is one of many pieces specifically designed to commemorate the fifth edition of Not In Paris, a multi-media event hosted by Highsnobiety featuring a selection of our favorite brands, artists, musicians, and other creators leading the charge in pushing culture forward. Coinciding with men’s fashion month, Not In Paris 5 hones in on the defining aspects of Paris, its people, and institutions, with collaborative capsules and inline releases spanning cut and sew, graphic styles, accessories, and collectibles.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Here To Stay Hoodie Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Here To Stay is a no-frills graphic hoodie emblazoned with a screenprinted Noon Goons logo front and center. Cut for a standard fit, the garment is made from a heavyweight cotton brushback fleece, as it is garment-dyed and pre-shrunk to ensure a long-lasting, consistent fit. Traditional hoodie design elements include an adjustable drawstring hood, ribbed trims, and a front pouch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hard Twist Finx Linen Chino Slacks Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of Auralee slacks is crafted from a high-quality cotton-linen blend, arriving in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear. The style is cut for a straight leg fit with a mid rise and features four-pocket construction, with slanting hand pockets and back slip pockets. Additional details include button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pleats at the legs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Aperture Trackpant Black/Dark Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Aperture is a contemporary update to the classic trackpant style. Made in Italy from ultralight nylon and mesh, the pair features pleated detailing and set back paneling at the knee for added breathability. Additional design elements include button fastening, belt loops, and side welt pockets, as the pant is cut for a wide leg fit that enhances freedom of movement.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 3 Stripes Track Pants Black/White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to a classic style, the Y-3 3 Stripes Track Pant is cut for a regular, straight leg fit from a nylon blend fabric. The pair is detailed with contrasting 3 Stripes running down the legs, while also being branded with a matching Y-3 logo on the back of the silhouette. Details include an elastic drawcord waist that incorporates button fastening and a zip fly, as well as pockets at the sides and back of the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brandon Pant Blue/Heavy Stone Bleached
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This version of Carhartt's Brandon Pant is made from a heavyweight cotton fabric known as Smith denim. The style's inseam is slightly shorter than most Carhartt bottoms to allow for more active movement. It features traditional five-pocket styling, button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops, and a woven square Carhartt label on the back of the silhouette. The pant offers a loose, straight fit with a low crotch.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Five-Pocket Jeans Caviar
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Maison Margiela denim style features traditional five-pocket styling, made from 100% cotton. The pair is cut for a relaxed fit and made with classic design elements including button fastening and belt loops lining the waist, with an adjustable cinch back that allows you to make minor adjustments to the fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sune Trousers Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Sune is Stockholm Surfboard Club's update to the classic dress pant. Offered in neutral colors that are easy to match, the long-lasting pair is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a relaxed boot-cut fit. Details include zip and hook and bar fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets at the sides and back of the silhouette. A small logo label is applied at the waist to subtly brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Elaine Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stockholm Surfboard Club offers a contemporary update to the classic dress pant with its Elaine model. Arriving in a versatile black colorway, the pair is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a relaxed fit. An elastic waistband ensures superior comfort, while press folds add a more formal touch. Pockets are then incorporated at the sides and back of the silhouette, which is subtly branded with logo detailing at the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Trouser Short Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Jil Sander short style draws from classic trouser options. Cut for an oversized fit for a more distinctive look, the stealthy black pair is produced in 100% cotton. The short features an elasticated waist and concealed fastening, with large flap pockets incorporated onto the sides of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Belted Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This standout Jil Sander pant style arrives in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear, constructed from 100% cotton. The pair is cut for an oversized fit with a wide leg to ensure a more distinctive look, all while coming with a matching belt. Pockets are incorporated at the sides and back of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cargo Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A technical update to the classic cargo style, this ROA pant is made in Romania from a durable, heavy cotton twill fabric. The regular-fitting pair is defined by its paneled inserts, while also featuring large slanted open hip pockets and open back pockets with one accessory loop. The style is then finished with a contrasting ROA graphic on the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wide Cut Jeans Washed Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Wide Cut Jean is produced in Italy from 12oz cotton denim. The pair is cut for a relaxed, wide leg fit, featuring traditional five-pocket construction. Details include button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist, as the style is then embellished with laurel wreath metal buttons and a suede logo patch on the back of the waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Jiro Trouser Black Wool
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Jiro Trouser is expertly crafted from a wool blend twill that originates from Bulgaria. The pair is cut for a wide fit with a high rise and features classic five-pocket styling. Traditional design elements include button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vent Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Vent Pant is a loose-fitting style made from a combination of polyester and nylon that is highly breathable and water-repellent. As with many and wander garments, the pair features reflector stitching for nighttime visibility, while also coming with an integrated, branded belt. The length of the pant can be adjusted by a drawcord that is incorporated into the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pip Pants Khaki
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pinot Short Lime
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Pinot is a standout denim short style made from 100% cotton that is dyed to create a distinctive finish. Offered in a vibrant Lime colorway, the regular-fitting pair features traditional design elements that include button fastening and a concealed fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets incorporated at the front and back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Paulson Pants Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Paulson is a signature Dries van Noten trouser style, arriving for the new season in a versatile navy colorway. Cut for a relaxed, straight leg fit, the pair is produced in a polyester-wool blend fabric and is unlined. The bottoms feature side hand pockets as well as back flap pockets and come with a matching pin buckle belt.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pooles Shorts Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Pooles is a casual short style produced in a lightweight viscose fabric. A wide silhouette cut above the knee, it features an elasticized waistband with an internal drawstring that allows you to dial in the fit. Vented side seams are implemented to enhance breathability, as pockets are incorporated onto the front and back of the short.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Oversized Cargo Pants Khaki
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Oversized Cargo Pant by and wander is a loose and wide silhouette, produced in a water-repellent lip material that uses split fiber yarn and has a unique firmness and coloring properties. As with many styles from the brand, the pair features an elasticated waistband with an integrated belt, in addition to drawcords at the hem that allow for minor adjustments to styling. Flap pockets are incorporated throughout to provide you with plenty of space to securely carry daily essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: OG Single Knee Pant Black/Stone Washed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt’s Single Knee Pant is a modified take on the classic work silhouette, boasting a relaxed, straight fit that makes it a loose version of the Ruck Single Knee Pant. The style is made from the brand’s midweight cotton denim, which is considerably durable yet surprisingly comfortable at the same time. Offered here in a blue stone wash, the pair becomes softer with wear, ultimately forming a fit that is unique to you.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Midland Pant Dark Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Constructed from midweight cotton twill, the Midland Pant draws from utilitarian styles. It features double stitching and tool pockets, while being cut for a relaxed, straight fit with a mid rise. Additional details include button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and slant hand pockets as well as two back pockets. Carhartt's signature square logo label is applied to the back right pocket to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wide Panel Pant Wax/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving in a clean light colorway, the Wide Panel Pant is defined by its wide, angular panels at the knee, which add reinforcement and point to classic workwear styles. The pair is produced in a midweight cotton fabric that is triple stitched and detailed with tool pockets and a hammer loop. The pant features a loose, voluminous fit for an extra comfortable and fashion-forward wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: OG Single Knee Pant Blue/Stone Washed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt’s Single Knee Pant is a modified take on the classic work silhouette, boasting a relaxed, straight fit that makes it a loose version of the Ruck Single Knee Pant. The style is made from the brand’s midweight cotton denim, which is considerably durable yet surprisingly comfortable at the same time. Offered here in a blue stone wash, the pair becomes softer with wear, ultimately forming a fit that is unique to you.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Midland Pant Dollar Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Constructed from midweight cotton twill, the Midland Pant draws from utilitarian styles. It features double stitching and tool pockets, while being cut for a relaxed, straight fit with a mid rise. Additional details include button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and slant hand pockets as well as two back pockets. Carhartt's signature square logo label is applied to the back right pocket to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pop-Up Pants Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Pop-Up is a wide leg pant style by Y/Project, arriving this season in a washed black look. The distinctive pair is constructed from a nylon blend fabric and outfitted with a partial elasticated waistband. On the front of the legs, you will find zippered cargo pockets, as more traditional pockets are incorporated on the sides and back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Evergreen Maxi Cowboy Cuff Jeans Evergreen Vintage Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Maxi Cowboy Cuff Jean is a hybrid Y/Project style defined by Western-inspired thigh cuffs that are removable, thus allowing you to wear the pair as shorts, too. The bottoms are produced in 100% organic cotton in a classic vintage black shade and cut for a loose and roomy fit with a wide leg. Details include traditional five-pocket styling, button fastening, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Evergreen Cut-Out Jeans Evergreen Vintage Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Y/Project is known for its distinctive denim styles like the Cut-Out Jean, which features a unique cut-out detail at the front of the silhouette. The pair is made from 100% organic cotton and designed for a wide leg fit with a high rise. To brand the jean, a leather logo patch is incorporated onto the back of the waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Peace Pants Bark Brown Slub
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Peace Pant is a slouchy, relaxed fitting style with a wide leg. A signature Story mfg. design, the pair is hand-embroidered from organic cotton, while also being hand-dyed from natural dyes. Large pockets are incorporated onto the side of each leg, as the waist and hem are outfitted with adjustable drawstrings to allow for minor alterations to styling and overall fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Third Cut Pink Cast Chain Twill
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to classic wide leg jean styles, this pair of trousers from Our Legacy is elevated thanks to its subtle details. Most noticeably, the bottoms showcase a distinctive piece-dyed finish that creates a vintage effect. On the back of the pair, you will find an embossed logo patch and two reinforced pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Deadstock Denim Baggy Pants Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of Marine Serre denim is produced in 100% cotton and defined by twisted cuts at the front and back panels that showcase the label's signature moon icon. The style features button fastening and belt loops lining the waist, with slip-in hand pockets and a single patched embroidered back pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Le Pantalon Marrone Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Le Pantalon Marrone is a belted workwear pant by Jacquemus, produced in 100% cotton with metal hardware. The pair is cut for a relaxed fit with a straight, wide leg and a mid rise. It features a hidden zip fly and clip fastener, J belt loops, and a removable grosgrain belt with an engraved metal buckle. Slash pockets are incorporated at the sides of the silhouette, while a cargo pocket is applied to the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rock Slide Pant Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Rock Slide is a casual pant style constructed from 100% cotton. Offering a classic straight leg fit, the pair features the brand's signature built-in webbing belt incorporated into the elasticated waistband, in addition to a series of pockets for carrying everyday essentials, including front hand pockets, back welt pockets, and an additional pocket at each leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Weather Trek Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Trek Pant is made for everyday wear and outdoor activities alike. Crafted from a high density stretch weather material, the pair is cut for a relaxed fit with a classic straight leg. It features the brand's signature built-in webbing belt incorporated into the elasticated waist, in addition to side hand pockets as well as a back zippered pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ground Up Pant Wax
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Ground Up Pant is a casual Gramicci style that is great for streetwear as well as outdoor wear. Woven from 100% cotton drill, the pair has a roomy fit from thigh to hem. It features a double-pocket design, with a total of seven pockets of varying sizes implemented throughout. The brand's signature built-in belt is then incorporated into the elasticated waist to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Track Pant Dark Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, the Nylon Track Pant is made from a durable nylon material with a dry touch. The pair is water-repellent, making it perfect for outdoor activities. The style has a slightly loose silhouette to aid in freedom of movement, while incorporating the brand's signature built-in belt at the elasticated waist. Zippers are then featured at the ankles to allow for minor adjustments to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hard Twist Polyester Satin Laminate Field Pants Light Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Auralee's Hard Twist Field Pant is crafted using a specially laminated material featuring satin made from ultra-fine, tightly twisted polyester for high functionality with water repellency, water resistance, and breathability. Featuring a smooth texture and a graceful drape, the oversized pair is fully lined and detailed with tucked knees, a drawcord waist and ankles, belt loops, and flap pockets at the sides and back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tailored Extended Wide Leg Trouser Brown Houndstooth
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This trouser style is a distinctive Martine Rose design defined by extended wide legs. It boasts a houndstooth pattern, with concealed front button, hook and zip fastening, and belt loops lining the waist. The wool pair incorporates pockets at the sides and back of the silhouette, which is finished with a small logo tag at the left pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Gusa Contrast Flare Pant Gusa Aged Black Wash
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This standout pair of Guess denim is defined by a distinctive double waistband. Constructed from 100% cotton, the style is cut for a regular fit with a flared leg and a dropped rise. It features classic five-pocket styling, with button fastening and belt loops lining the waist. The buttons and rivets are branded, as a triangle logo patch is applied to the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vast Cut Washed Black Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple Our Legacy style, the Vast Cut Pant features a high waist with a loose, oversized fit and a wide straight leg. The pair is made with traditional five-pocket styling and showcases a vintage wash for a worn-in look. An embossed Our Legacy patch is applied to the silhouette to brand the design at the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Canvas Trouser Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: ROA's Canvas Trouser is a workwear-inspired style constructed from a durable, heavy cotton fabric. Designed to be worn as a technical garment or an everyday item, the pair is defined by large open pockets at the hips as well as open back pockets. Details include button fastening and belt loops lining the waist, as the pant is minimally branded with a logo graphic applied to the left hip pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Pants Royal Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Stone Island pant style is produced in a soft and lightweight cotton fabric. The pair is cut for a straight leg fit, featuring button fastening and a snap button fly, in addition to an internal drawstring at the waist. Pockets are incorporated onto the sides and back of the silhouette, which is branded with a contrasting Stone Island Marina logo at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cantering Trousers Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Thames' Cantering Trouser is a sophisticated style defined by its shaped back waistband. Suspender imitation horn engraving buttons are incorporated at the waist, while red stitching details are showcased at the pockets and inside the legs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hayworth Pant Dollar Green/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Hayworth Pant is a comfy Carhartt WIP style produced in 100% cotton twill. The pair is cut for a relaxed fit and outfitted with an elasticated waistband with a built-in adjustable belt. Drawstrings are incorporated into the ankle hems to allow for minor adjustments to styling, as pockets are then featured on the front and back of the silhouette. The brand's signature square woven label is applied to the back right pocket to subtly brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Denim Jeans Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of CAMPERLAB denim is defined by a seasonal contrast color print that gives it a bold urban look. The style is cut for a relaxed unisex fit with a straight leg and long length, as the brand recommends sizing up for a loose fit that sits lower on the hips. Details include zip and button fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets on the front and back of the silhouette. A logo label is incorporated onto the back of the waistband to brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Denim Jeans Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of CAMPERLAB denim is defined by a seasonal contrast color print that gives it a bold urban look. The style is cut for a relaxed unisex fit with a straight leg and long length, as the brand recommends sizing up for a loose fit that sits lower on the hips. Details include zip and button fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets on the front and back of the silhouette. A logo label is incorporated onto the back of the waistband to brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twisted Belted Pants Denim Acid Snow Bronze
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Lemaire is the perfect brand for anyone looking to elevate their pant game. One of the standouts from the luxury label’s latest seasonal collection arrives in the form of the Twisted Belted style. As the name suggests, the pair is constructed from cotton with twisted side seams that give the legs a slightly curved shape. The elongated silhouette comes with a removable belt and is outfitted with slip-in side pockets as well as patch pockets at the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Cargo Pants Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Stone Island bottoms are crafted from a wrinkled metal nylon material for a distinctive finish. The pair is outfitted with an elasticated waistband and ankles for superior comfort, while also featuring zips at the ankles that make way for minor styling adjustments. Cargo pockets are incorporated at each leg, in addition to the traditional side hand pockets and back pocket. Stone Island's signature compass logo badge is showcased at the left leg to brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Denim Casual Pants Light Indigo Denim Wash
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These playful TNF bottoms feature hybrid construction from woven fabric and denim using a combination of cotton and polyester materials. The close-fitting pair is defined by contrasting panels at the legs, with details that include an elasticated waistband with an integrated belt, front and back pockets, and a D-ring attachment at the back right pocket for clipping accessories. Contrasting TNF logos are applied to the front and back of the pant to brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: No Problemo Sweatpant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The No Problemo Sweatpant arrives in celebration of Aries' new label of the same name. Crafted from 100% cotton, the cozy bottoms are adorned with a contrasting No Problemo graphic print on the left leg. Additional details include an elasticated waistband and ankles for comfort, as well as hand pockets at each side.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: M66 Tek Twill Wide Leg Pant Forest Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The M66 Tek Twill Pant is a technical style made with an exclusive hydrophobic cotton material that uses molecular covalent bonds at the yarn level to produce a water-resistant fabric. A Durable Water-Repellent Finish then enhances water-repellency, while articulated seams are incorporated for mobility. The pant is cut for a loose fit that caters to freedom of movement, while featuring an exposed webbing belt and cinch cord at the leg openings for adjustability.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: GTX Casual Pant Summit Navy/TNF Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Casual Pant is made using GORE-TEX fabric for full waterproofness.
