It features an elasticated waistband with an integrated belt and flap pockets at each leg, in addition to traditional hand pockets and back pockets. Logo detailing is implemented on the front and back of the pair to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Voronoi Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Characterized by its clean overall design, the Voronoi Pant is made for all landscapes. Crafted from recycled nylon with a water-repellent finish that helps shed moisture, the style offers ample stretch, durability, and comfort. The garment's laminated construction and three-dimensional patterning create clean lines and enhance freedom of movement no matter the situation.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Evergreen Asymmetric Waist Jeans Evergreen Ice Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The name tells all, as this polarizing Y/Project style is defined by an asymmetric waistline that curves around the front left of the body and levels out on the right side. You can in turn wear the asymmetric panel flipped over to reveal a new printed lining and the brand’s signature denim label, which is typically featured on the back of the waist. The pair arrives in an Evergreen Ice Blue colorway with five-pocket styling, a button fly, and belt loops. It is cut in a regular fit with a straight leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ghost Piece Pants Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Ghost Piece Pant is a monochromatic style produced in 100% cotton. Cut for a regular fit with a mid rise, the beige-colored pair then features button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets incorporated at the sides and back of each leg. Stone Island's signature removable logo badge is applied to the left leg to definitively brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Otis Trousers Coated Crackle Cotton
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Otis Trouser is a luxe pant style made from a coated cotton blend cloth originating from Italy. The fabric is in turn crinkled and creased to create a distinctive vintage look. Cut for a straight leg fit, the pair features traditional five-pocket construction, with button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Belted Tactical Chino Nine Iron
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, Patta's Belted Tactical Chino is defined by an integrated belt that allows you to dial in the fit. The loose-fitting pair is produced in a technical cotton-nylon blend fabric and features two side pockets with zippers and an additional zippered pocket on the back. The brand's iconic Script logo is incorporated onto the front of the left leg to minimally brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Whiskers Jeans Vintage Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Patta's Whisker Jeans are defined by custom branding implemented on the back of the silhouette. The Vintage Blue pair is produced in 100% cotton denim and cut for loose fit. It features traditional five-pocket styling, a button fly, and belt loops lining the waist. The buttons and rivets are branded, as a leather logo patch is then incorporated onto the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Judd Pant Black/Garment Dyed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Judd is a casual Carhartt pant style produced in lightweight cotton poplin. Cut for a loose fit with a regular waist, the pair is then detailed with double-layer pleated knees for added volume. Pockets are incorporated at the sides and back of the silhouette, which is finished with the brand's signature square logo label on the rear right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Bib Overall Black/Stone Washed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from 11.25 oz Norco denim and stone washed for a worn-in appearance, this version of the Bib Overall boasts triple stitching at vital stress points to withstand years of wear. The pair is in turn detailed with contrasting thread and outfitted with numerous pockets for carrying everyday essentials. Elastic suspenders offer a comfortable and adjustable fit no matter if you’re wearing the overalls on the job site or around town.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fadir Cotton Mix Twill Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This unisex pant style by GmbH opts for a single zip front instead of the brand’s trademark double zip. Produced in a polyester-cotton blend fabric, the pair is cut for a regular fit with a straight leg. It features classic five-pocket construction and is detailed with embossed hardware and buttons, as well as a leather logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: LVC 1947 501 Jeans Dark Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The 1940s ushered in some welcomed changes to Levi’s iconic 501 jean. Adhering to the times and an emerging middle class, the silhouette was cut for a slimmer fit, as extraneous details like the cinch and suspender buttons were removed. For the first time since the start of the war, the 501 was made with watch pocket rivets and double-needle technology, which could now be mass-produced. Constructed entirely using selvedge denim, the jeans were finished with a logo patch at the back waist and a Levi’s flag label at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Leggur Pants Lime Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A designer track pant style, this version of the Leggur is made from a combination of lightweight cotton twill and nylon material. The pair is cut for a regular fit with a tapered leg, all while featuring an elasticized waistband with an internal drawstring that allows you to easily adjust the fit. The ankle cuffs are also elasticized, as the bottoms are then finished with zippered pockets at the sides of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Is Pants Khaki/Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Is is a sporty pant style by RANRA, emerging this season in a two-tone khaki and gray colorway. It is predominantly crafted from a lightweight nylon fabric, with an elasticated waistband to enhance overall comfort. The ankle cuffs are also elasticated, as the pair is then outfitted with side hand pockets to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Elaine Shorts Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stockholm Surfboard Club delivers a short variation of its signature Elaine style. Arriving in a versatile beige colorway, the pair is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a relaxed fit. An elastic waistband ensures superior comfort, while press folds add a more formal touch. Pockets are then incorporated at the sides and back of the silhouette, which is subtly branded with logo detailing at the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Gabriel Cargo Forest Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Gabriel is Winnie's contemporary update to the classic cargo pant. This particular pair is crafted from cotton and cut for a relaxed fit with a wide leg. Details include button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets incorporated at the sides, back, and legs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brandon Pant Black/Stone Washed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This version of Carhartt's Brandon Pant is made from a heavyweight cotton fabric known as Smith denim. The style's inseam is slightly shorter than most Carhartt bottoms to allow for more active movement. It features traditional five-pocket styling, button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops, and a woven square Carhartt label on the back of the silhouette. The pant offers a loose, straight fit with a low crotch.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Martians Track Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Part track pant part denim, the D-Martians is a unisex style featuring a light blue wash, medium treated for an authentic vintage look. The silhouette is cut for a loose fit with a straight leg, outfitted with an elasticated waist and an adjustable drawstring for optimal comfort. Large pockets are implemented on the front of the pair, with a single welt pocket incorporated onto the back. The brand’s oval D logo is applied to the front to subtly brand the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Hugh Cargo Pants Tree House
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This version of Diesel's P-Hugh Pant is defined by a distinctive all-over print created using sublimation technology. The original light brown hue of the fabric is revealed as the garment is pressed flat during the process, and the color is unable penetrate into the creases and folds. The pair is cut for a loose fit and detailed with multiple patch pockets as well as back welt pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tropical Wool Trousers Blue/Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Tropical Trouser is a signature Marni style, arriving this season in a dark-colored virgin wool execution. Cut for a regular fit with a straight leg, the pair features a zip fly and belt loops lining the waist, all while being outfitted with a series of pockets including side slip pockets, a side flap pocket, and a back flap pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Drawstring Trousers Leaf Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Marni's Drawstring Trouser arrives this season in a new green colorway, woven from 100% cotton with calf leather application. The pair is flared with a mid waist and features traditional five-pocket styling. Details include button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and an accompanying lace belt that is removable. A leather logo patch is applied to the back of the waist to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ed Unlined Cotton Drawstring Trousers Weimaraner Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Ed Unlined Drawstring Trouser is a signature Meta Campania Collective pant style, arriving for the season in a versatile gray colorway. The pair is crafted from a midweight Italian cotton fabric and cut for a relaxed fit with a straight leg and a mid rise. A thin cotton drawstring is incorporated into the waistband to make way for a more comfortable fit. Pockets emerge at the side seam as well as the back to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Embroidered Denim Knolly Brook Trouser Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made in India from 100% cotton, this Bode trouser is based on a vintage denim smock circa the 1970s to 1980s. The brand in turn reproduced the defining embroidered detail at the waist, hem, and back pockets for this elevated workwear style. The denim is detailed with button fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and logo labels at the front right pocket as well as the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Cargo Pants Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Like many other styles from the brand, the Stone Island Cargo Pants feature a garment-dyed treatment to deliver a more distinctive overall look. This particular pair is produced in a stretch cotton gabardine and cut in a regular straight leg fit. Each leg is outfitted with a bellows pocket that has a flap with hidden snap fastening. To finish the design, Stone Island’s trademark logo badge is implemented at the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fatigue Pants Musk
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing from classic workwear, the Stone Island Fatigue Pants are constructed from durable gabardine that has been treated with a water-repellent agent. The fabric is tear- and abrasion-resistant as well to enhance the overall durability, ensuring the pair withstands the test of time. Cut in a regular straight leg fit, the SI bottoms are outfitted with slanted hand pockets and back patch pockets with metal snaps, branded with the Stone Island compass patch at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Drawstring Pants Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A comfy style, these Maison Margiela bottoms are crafted from 100% cotton and cut for a relaxed fit. The pair is outfitted with a drawstring waist that allows you to dial in the fit, while featuring frayed edges at the ankles and the house's signature four stitches moniker on the back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hard Cargo Gravel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Two styles in one, the Hard Cargo by Entire Studios features a zip-off leg that allows you to convert the bottoms into shorts. Crafted from a cotton heavy canvas, the pair is outfitted with multiple pockets running down the legs, in addition to traditional side hand pockets and two back pockets. The Hard Cargo features a regular-fitting waist and a wide leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Freight Cargo Gravy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Freight Cargo is constructed from 210gsm cotton canvas and features a vintage wash treatment that gives the garment a unique appearance. Cut for a wide leg fit that is slightly large, the pair has button fastening and a zip fly, in addition to a drawstring waist and bottom hem that allow for minor alterations to styling. Pockets are incorporated at the legs and waist to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Freight Cargo Iron
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Freight Cargo is constructed from 210gsm cotton canvas and features a vintage wash treatment that gives the garment a unique appearance. Cut for a wide leg fit that is slightly large, the pair has button fastening and a zip fly, in addition to a drawstring waist and bottom hem that allow for minor alterations to styling. Pockets are incorporated at the legs and waist to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tropical Suiting Pants Navy Striped
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These classic suit pants are made from a lightweight fabric that’s ideal for year-round wear. Detailed with pleats and cut in a relaxed fit, the pants feature a slight taper and arrive with side and back pockets as well as a zip fly with a branded button closure.  A matching suitjacketandshortsare also available in this collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ripstop Cargo Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An update to our heavyweight cargos, the pants are constructed from densely woven ripstop with reinforced layers at the knees and rear.  The spacious pair is cut with a slight taper and is detailed with a soft, washed texture. Cinch cords at the ankle and waist allow you to alter the shape on the fly, while a wide array of pockets allow for ample storage space.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ripstop Cargo Pants Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An update to our heavyweight cargos, the pants are constructed from densely woven ripstop with reinforced layers at the knees and rear.  The spacious pair is cut with a slight taper and is detailed with a soft, washed texture. Cinch cords at the ankle and waist allow you to alter the shape on the fly, while a wide array of pockets allow for ample storage space.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Reverse Piping Elastic Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our updated Reverse Piping Trousers are lightweight and made from a tightly woven blend with a washed finish. The loose-fitting pants are detailed with external butt stitching at the seams and feature a drawstring waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Pleated Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These loose-fitting pants are crafted entirely from cotton and are characterized by their smooth, brushed texture. Detailed in a classic ivory hue with front pleats, the pants arrive with side and back pockets as well as a zip fly with a button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tropical Suiting Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These classic suit pants are made from a lightweight fabric that’s ideal for year-round wear. Detailed with pleats and cut in a relaxed fit, the pants feature a slight taper and arrive with side and back pockets as well as a zip fly with a branded button closure. A matching suitjacketandshortsare also available in this collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Reverse Piping Trouser Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our updated Reverse Piping Trousers are lightweight and made from a tightly woven blend with a washed finish. The loose-fitting pants are detailed with external butt stitching at the seams and feature a drawstring waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Pleated Trousers Ivory
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These loose-fitting pants are crafted entirely from cotton and are characterized by their smooth, brushed texture. Detailed in a classic ivory hue with front pleats, the pants arrive with side and back pockets as well as a zip fly with a button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Super Loose Fit Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to the classic dress pant, this Bonsai style is produced in a lightweight cotton-nylon blend fabric that has a unique appearance. The pair arrives in a versatile black colorway, detailed with front pleats and a concealed fly, while featuring side hand pockets as well as back pockets. The silhouette's relaxed, wide leg fit ensures a more stylish overall look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wide Leg Trackpant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A familiar Martine Rose style, the Wide Leg Trackpant returns for the new season, with contrasting panel detailing that defines the garment. The relaxed-fitting pair is constructed from 100% polyester and features an elasticated waistband with an internal drawstring, as well as side hand pockets. A seasonal Martine Rose logo is embroidered onto the left leg to serve as added embellishment for the pant.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double-Faced Piqué Sweatpants Eggshell
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Our collection with Lacoste celebrates the pioneering athleisure brand, uniting our love for casual competition and the lifestyle that surrounds it. The Logo Sweatpants are crafted from double-face piqué fabric and detailed in a tonal eggshell colorway. Cut in a relaxed fit from a custom double-face pique fabric constructed specifically for this collection, the sweats are finished with side pockets and co-branded logos on the leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double Knee Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Double Knee Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt’s seasonal collections, offered in neutral colorways that you can wear over and over again. The brand utilizes its signature organic cotton dearborn canvas on the pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Double Knee Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the double layer at the knee in a tonal application.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sune Trousers Ulster Navy Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Sune is Stockholm Surfboard Club's update to the classic dress pant. Offered in neutral colors that are easy to match, the long-lasting pair is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a relaxed boot-cut fit. Details include zip and hook and bar fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets at the sides and back of the silhouette. A small logo label is applied at the waist to subtly brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sune Trousers Mid Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Sune is Stockholm Surfboard Club's update to the classic dress pant. Offered in neutral colors that are easy to match, the long-lasting pair is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a relaxed boot-cut fit. Details include zip and hook and bar fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets at the sides and back of the silhouette. A small logo label is applied at the waist to subtly brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Elaine Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stockholm Surfboard Club offers a contemporary update to the classic dress pant with its Elaine model. Arriving in a versatile black colorway, the pair is crafted from 100% polyester and cut for a relaxed fit. An elastic waistband ensures superior comfort, while press folds add a more formal touch. Pockets are then incorporated at the sides and back of the silhouette, which is subtly branded with logo detailing at the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 2001 D-Macro-S Trousers Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new pair of the D-Macro-S is defined by a distinctive distressed effect that creates a worn-in appearance. Cut for a straight leg fit, the denim is made from 100% cotton and features traditional five-pocket construction. Additional design details include button fastening and a concealed zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and a Diesel logo patch incorporated onto the back of the pair.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 2010-D-Macs Straight Jeans Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The 2010-D-Macs is a staple Diesel denim style constructed from 100% cotton. This particular pair is cut for a straight leg fit and features traditional design details that include five-pocket styling, button fastening and a concealed fly, and belt loops lining the waist. The denim is finished with a Diesel logo patch, which is applied to the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Livery Trousers Total Eclipse
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P-Livery is a workwear-inspired style from Diesel, arriving this season in a heavily washed look. Predominantly constructed from cotton, the canvas pair features paneled construction and is cut for a relaxed fit with a mid rise and a wide leg. Design details include button fastening and a concealed zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, tool pockets and a hammer loop, and additional pockets at the sides and back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Single Knee Pant Black/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Carhartt’s Single Knee Pant is a modified take on the classic work silhouette, boasting a relaxed, straight fit that makes it a loose version of the Ruck Single Knee Pant. The style is made from the brand’s signature 12oz Dearborn canvas, which is considerably durable yet surprisingly comfortable at the same time. A defining characteristic, the pair becomes softer with wear, ultimately forming a fit that is unique to you.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Corduroy Cargo Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Acne Studios combines corduroy trousers and cargo pants to deliver this new elevated style. Predominantly constructed from organic cotton, the relaxed-fitting pair arrives in a versatile black colorway detailed with a light stonewash finish. The bottoms feature traditional button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets at the sides and back. Acne Studios' small Face logo patch is incorporated onto the front of the silhouette to subtly brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Washed Heavy Canvas Pants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Auralee trousers are made from a cotton canvas that is densely woven with thick, uneven yarns. The fabric is stiffened by processing, beaten, and washed multiple times to create a softer texture. The matte color and uneven texture then give the straight leg pair a vintage look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double Knee Pant Black/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Double Knee Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt WIP’s seasonal collections, offered in neutral colorways that you can wear over and over again. The brand utilizes its signature polyester/cotton Denison twill on the pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Double Knee Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the double layer at the knee.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Huges-New Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to the classic cargo pant, Diesel's P-Huges-New Trouser arrives for the season in a stealthy all-black colorway, predominantly constructed from stretchy cotton. The wide leg pair is characterized by a series of cargo pockets incorporated onto the legs, while being minimally branded with a small oval "D" logo patch on the back. Additional design details include concealed front fastening, belt loops, and drawstring ankles that allow for minor adjustments to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1998 D-Buck Jeans Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, the 1998 D-Buck draws from vintage denim styles, all while incorporating a slightly wider hem for a modern twist. The pair is cut for a slim fit with a mid waist and a boot-cut leg, ensuring a decidedly standout look. Traditional design elements include five-pocket styling, a button fly, and belt loops lining the waist. The denim is finished with a Diesel logo tag applied to the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Fish-Cargo-S Trousers Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The D-Fish is a wide leg cargo pant by Diesel, offering a contemporary update to a classic style. The loose-fitting pair is made from a cotton and true hemp blend fabric, featuring cargo pockets at each leg. Traditional design elements include button fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and a branded logo patch applied to the back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cargo Jogpant
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Primo Pants Ombre/Lime
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Primo is a loose-fitting pant style by Dries van Noten, one that features an elasticated waistband and a visible mid-front zipper that decorates the silhouette. Detailed with an allover ombre effect, the fit can be dialed in with an external drawstring, while pockets are incorporated at the sides and back to provide you with space for carrying daily essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Packard Pants Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten offers an artisanal take on the traditional workwear silhouette with its Packard Pants crafted from a hardwearing cotton and linen blend. The heavyweight pants are detailed with a unique allover pattern accented with front patch pockets, utility pockets, and a handy hammer loop.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: W.U. Boot-Cut Pant Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Cozy and primed for all occasions, these boot-cut pants are made from a durable and stretchy cavalry twill weave similar to Needles' Cavalry Twill Sports Jacket. The tapered pants are detailed with side and back zip pockets and feature an elasticated waistband with an internal drawcord along with the brand's papillon logo embroidered on the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hamer Sweatpants Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Dries van Noten Hamer Pants are sweats with a high-fashion edge. Produced in 100% cotton, the cozy pair arrives in a versatile gray colorway that can be paired with virtually anything. An elasticated waist enhances comfort, while an integrated drawstring allows you to dial in a more precise fit. Side pockets and an additional back pocket then provide you with adequate space to carry daily essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hama Cotton Jersey Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Hama is a comfy Dries van Noten pant style produced in a midweight cotton jersey fabric. This particular pair arrives in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear, featuring side hand pockets as well as back pockets. A drawstring is incorporated into the waistband to allow you to dial in a more precise fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Penning Pants Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Penning Pants offer a distinctive wide-leg fit to stand apart from the other denim offerings in your wardrobe. Produced in 100% cotton, the style arrives in a deep indigo shade, detailed with front pleats. The pair features classic five-pocket construction, button fastening, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Primo Nylon Pants Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Primo is a loose-fitting pant style by Dries van Noten, one that features an elasticated waistband for superior comfort. An external drawstring allows you to dial in the fit, while pockets are incorporated at the sides and back of the silhouette to provide you with space for carrying daily essentials. This particular pair is constructed from 100% nylon that is garment-dyed and water-repellent to offer protection from the elements.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-MACS-LTH Leather Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Diesel gives you the edge you've been looking for with its new leather trousers. Predominantly crafted from sheepskin leather and lined in cotton, the stealthy pair boasts a high shine finish that ensures a standout look. The bottoms are made with traditional five-pocket styling and detailed with a concealed fly and button fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and an applique logo.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Beach Pants Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Nigo and Human Made draw from classic Americana to deliver the Beach Pant. Arriving in a versatile beige colorway, the wide leg pair is woven from 100% cotton. The style showcases a center press crease, all while being outfitted with traditional design elements that include button fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets at the side in seam, back, and right leg. A small woven brand patch is applied to the leg to minimally brand the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Elastic Waistband Trousers Blue Kyanite
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Marni trouser is a comfy style primarily knit from cotton with polyester application. The straight leg pair is defined by an elastic waistband that is adorned with a repeat Marni logo. Double knee paneling offers reinforcement, as the bottoms are then outfitted with hand pockets at the sides and a single patch pocket at the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1955 501 Jeans Dark Indigo Flat Finish
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Levi’s 501 dates all the way back to the 1800s, with the 1955 variation designed as an homage to bikers, the ultimate thrill-seekers of the '50s. Defined by a distinctive "anti-fit" in the seat, the jean has a slightly loose, straight cut that is fuller around the leg and overall boxier. The pair features classic five-pocket styling, with other traditional design elements including a button fly and the Levi’s logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Show Pony Trousers Brown Multi
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These standout Bode bottoms draw inspiration from an embroidered Western shirt that dates back to the 1960s. The garment's embroidered horses and contrasting stitching at the waistband, hem, and pockets have in turn been reproduced to create the Show Pony style. The pair is outfitted with side buckle adjusters that allow you to dial in the fit, as well as pockets at the sides and back. The fit is straight leg with a mid rise.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Task Pant Military Mud
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Task Pant is a straight leg style crafted from 100% cotton heavy canvas. It features a stone wash treatment that gives it a worn look, offered in a versatile brown colorway for effortless matching. Additional details include traditional five-pocket styling, button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Gocar Brunette
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios blends traditional sweatpant and cargo styles to create the Heavy Gocar. Crafted from 100% organic cotton brushed back fleece, the bottoms feature a heavy enzyme wash that can cause slight variances in appearance. Unlike most cargo pants, the Gocar incorporates two cargo pockets at each leg. The baggy pair is then fit with an elasticated waistband and cotton drawcord that allows you to dial in the fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Utility Sweats Soot
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Cargos meet sweatpants with the Utility Sweats by Entire Studios. This particular pair is crafted from 100% organic cotton brushed back fleece with panel detailing. An elasticated waistband enhances comfort, while a cotton drawcord allows you to dial in the fit. The baggy pair is then outfitted with a series of pockets including four cargo pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: String Fatigue Pant Back Sateen Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A classic style suited for all seasons, the Fatigue Pant from Needles is produced in a light ounce back sateen material. The pair is cut for a loose fit and outfitted with a comfortable elastic waist with an adjustable drawstring that allows for minor alterations. The ankle cuffs also incorporate a drawstring, while pockets are featured on the front and back of the silhouette. Needles' butterfly logo is then embroidered onto the left leg to playfully brand the bottoms.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Jersey Lounge Pants Khaki Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Acne Studios bottoms are a comfy style crafted from a cotton jersey fabric. Featuring an all-over camouflage pattern, the pair is cut for a relaxed fit with a wide leg. A concealed drawstring is incorporated into the elasticized waistband, allowing you to dial in the fit. Pockets then emerge at the sides and back of the silhouette, which is finished with subtle logo detailing at the rear pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Loose Fit Jeans 2021 Vintage Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These loose-fitting jeans from Acne Studios are crafted from rigid denim made of organic cotton. The pair has been subjected to a deep black overdye with a washed finish and features traditional five-pocket construction, a button fly, and belt loops lining the waist. A leather logo patch is incorporated onto the back of the waist to minimally brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Patch Canvas Trousers Carbon Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Acne Studios trousers are defined by a patch construction. The unisex pair is cut for a regular fit, showcasing a pigment-dyed finish for a more distinctive look. Distressed details are implemented throughout the pants, which are outfitted with front and back pockets. Additional details include button fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and a leather Face logo patch incorporated onto the back waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Patch Canvas Trousers Toffee Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Acne Studios trousers are defined by a patch construction. The unisex pair is cut for a regular fit, showcasing a pigment-dyed finish for a more distinctive look. Distressed details are implemented throughout the pants, which are outfitted with front and back pockets. Additional details include button fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and a leather Face logo patch incorporated onto the back waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1991 Toj Vintage Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of rigid denim from Acne Studios has been lightly washed to achieve that coveted worn-in look. Coming with a matching thin belt, the jeans feature a wide, straight leg and loose fit designed to be unisex.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: WRKS Pant Washed Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Boot-Cut Track Pant - Poly Smooth
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Order your regular size.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Boot-Cut Track Pant - Poly Smooth
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Order your regular size.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: PBS Cargo Pants Olive
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Fucking Awesome delivers a fresh cargo design with the PBS Pant. Arriving for the season in a versatile Olive colorway, the baggy-fitting pair is crafted from 100% cotton and detailed with a custom "Spiral" logo antique tack button as well as branded embroidery on the back of the silhouette. In addition to a cargo pocket at each leg, the pant features slanting hand pockets and two back pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 Technical Pants Right Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple silhouette based on the brand's 5.0+ Technical Pants, these all-black trousers are made using a stretchy, heavy duty cotton-nylon blend. Cut in a flare fit with an elasticated waistband, the pants are equipped with six concealed zip pockets at the front and one at the rear, all lined with a contrasting fabric that can be used to embellish your outfit when unzipped.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.1 Technical Pants Right Olive Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A staple silhouette based on the brand's 5.0+ Technical Pants, these all-black trousers are made using a stretchy, heavy duty cotton-nylon blend. Cut in a flare fit with an elasticated waistband, the pants are equipped with six concealed zip pockets at the front and one at the rear, all lined with a contrasting fabric that can be used to embellish your outfit when unzipped.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Lod Denim Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Similar to the brand'sMokollur Jeans, this denim pair is detailed in a light-colored indigo wash with contrast stitching. The pair is cut for a stretchy, straight fit while featuring five-pocket styling, button fastening, and a zip fly.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Patch Raw Denim Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Saintwoods pant style is made in Los Angeles from selvedge denim in raw indigo. Cut for an oversized fit, the pair features classic five-pocket styling, with button fastening and belt loops lining the waist. Tonal patchwork with contrasting stitching is implemented throughout the silhouette, while a raised logo is showcased on one of the back pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Sweatpants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An elevated take on the traditional sweatpant, this Acne Studios style arrives in a versatile black colorway with a distinctive garment-dyed finish. The pair is cut for a relaxed unisex fit and outfitted with an elasticated waistband that incorporates an adjustable drawcord that allows you to dial in the fit. Pockets are featured at the side seams and back, as the pant is subtly branded with a small logo tab to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Tailored Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Tailored Trouser is a comfy pant style by Acne Studios, arriving this season in a versatile black colorway. The pair is constructed from a wool blend fabric and fully lined, while being cut for a relaxed fit with a mid waist and a straight leg. The waistband is elasticated for comfort and incorporates a drawcord that allows you to dial in the fit. Pockets are then featured at the sides and back of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Regular Fit Jeans 1992 Indigo Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of Acne Studios jeans is crafted from rigid denim made of cotton. Cut for a regular fit with a mid waist and boot-cut leg, the style features traditional five-pocket construction, with a button fly, belt loops lining the waist, and a leather logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Field Maple Trousers Brown/Red
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Field Maple is a standout pant style by Bode, defined by a distinctive embroidered motif implemented throughout the legs. The straight leg pair is constructed from 100% cotton and features three-pocket styling, with button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist. A cinch tab is incorporated at the back of the trouser to allow for minor adjustments to sizing.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: HIGHArt Mixed Panel Canvas Painter Pants Off-White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Canvas Painter Pants utilize both mid- and heavy-weight cotton drill fabric in a panel construction. A reference to classic workwear styles, they also feature utility and side pockets as well as a hammer loop. The utilitarian design is finished with a zip fly, a script woven flag at the seam, and a HIGHArt flag at the back pocket. Drawing inspiration from a blank canvas, these pants arrive as part of a larger HIGHArt collection including a matching painter jacket and limited-edition adidas sneakers.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Super Milled Sweat Pants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Auralee Sweat Pants are the result of continuous prototyping to achieve an enduring, tight-knit weave that's built to last. Crafted with a blend of cotton and bulky yarn on the exterior with soft non-twisted yarns inside, the sweats arrive with a luxurious, dense texture featuring side pockets, a single patch back pocket, and an elasticated waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Fluid Jersey Baggy Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Fluid Jersey Pant is a comfortable yet stylish Marine Serre garment crafted from recycled jersey fabric. Offering a baggy fit, the pair features contrasting striped detailing, while being outfitted with an elasticated waistband with an external drawstring that allows you to dial in the fit. Hand pockets are incorporated at the sides of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Regenerated Denim Straight Leg Pants Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This Marine Serre style is made from cotton denim pants that have been disassembled and reassembled to breathe new life into the fabric. The high-waisted, straight leg pair is further defined by the brand's signature crescent moon print, which is applied to the legs through laser-engraving. More traditional design elements include button fastening and belt loops lining the waist, with two pockets at the front and one at the back of the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Lush Carpenter Pants Scarecrow Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A nod to classic workwear styles, the Lush Carpenter Pants are crafted from organic cotton and are characterized by their wide, tapered fit. The pants are detailed with handwoven patches and feature side and back pockets, a hammer loop and drawcord at the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Paco Pants Sage Slub
tshirts_and_tops.Description: STORY mfg.'s Paco Pants are characterized by their wide, slouchy silhouette. Detailed in a tonal sage slub hue and made using organic cotton, the pants feature a drawstring at the hem and waist, a single back pocket, and an embroidered logo on the leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twist Seam Tailored Trouser Black/White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Twist Seam Trouser is a signature Martine Rose pant style, here produced in a soft wool blend fabric. Cut for a relaxed fit, this particular pair showcases a pinstripe look and is defined by seams that twist around to the knee. Additional details include front zip and clasp closure, belt loops lining the waist, and pockets incorporated at the waist and back. The taping in the waistband is then branded to subtly label the garment.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double Knee Pant Hamilton Brown/Rigid
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Double Knee Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt WIP’s seasonal collections, offered in neutral colorways that you can wear over and over again. The brand utilizes its signature organic cotton Dearborn canvas on the pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Double Knee Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the double layer at the knee.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Jet Cargo Pant Cypress/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Jet is a loose-fitting cargo style from Carhartt WIP. This particular pair is executed in a durable cotton Columbia ripstop fabric, with bartack stitching at vital stress points. An elasticated waistband ensures maximum comfort, while drawstrings at the ankle cuffs allow for minor adjustments to styling. In addition to the cargo pockets at each leg, the pair is fit with side hand pockets as well as back flap button pockets. As with most Carhartt WIP styles, the pant is finished with a square logo label, applied to the right cargo pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double Knee Pant Tobacco/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Double Knee Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt WIP’s seasonal collections, offered in neutral colorways that you can wear over and over again. The brand utilizes its signature polyester/cotton Denison twill on the pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Double Knee Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the double layer at the knee.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double Knee Pant Zeus/Rigid
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Double Knee Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt WIP’s seasonal collections, offered in neutral colorways that you can wear over and over again. The brand utilizes its signature organic cotton Dearborn canvas on the pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Double Knee Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the double layer at the knee.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rider Leather Denim Mix Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Rider Pant is a signature KUSIKOHC style. This particular pair arrives in a predominantly black colorway crafted from cotton with olive-colored leather inserts. The pant offers a mid-rise fit with a straight leg and is made with traditional five-pocket styling. Additional details include button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist. The pair is set off with contrasting embroidery applied at the leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Double Knee Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Double Knee Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt WIP’s seasonal collections, offered in neutral colorways that you can wear over and over again. The brand utilizes its signature organic cotton dearborn canvas on the pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Double Knee Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the double layer at the knee in a tonal application.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pleated Twill Pants
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Made in collaboration with Noah as part of the duo's ongoing partnership, these Twill Pants are crafted entirely from cotton and are detailed with stitched-down pleats. Contrasting side piping accentuates these regular-fitting trousers that also feature two side pockets, a drawstring waistband and hem, as well as a single back pocket with co-branded logos.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Nylon Trackpants Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Brushed Nylon Trackpants are part of our collaboration with NTS, the online radio station and media platform that's been at the forefront of obscure music since 2011. Detailed with a smooth, matte texture, the pants are crafted from a cotton and nylon blend with embroidered graphics designed by artist George Addy throughout. A co-branded logo at the front pocket along with a single back pocket further embellish the look, while two side pockets and an elasticated waistband complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Brushed Nylon Trackpants Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Brushed Nylon Trackpants are part of our collaboration with NTS, the online radio station and media platform that's been at the forefront of obscure music since 2011. Detailed with a smooth, matte texture, the pants are crafted from a cotton and nylon blend with embroidered graphics throughout. A co-branded logo designed by artist George Addy at the front pocket along with a single back pocket further embellish the look, while two side pockets and an elasticated waistband complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Knit Track Pant Mystery Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A fixture within the adidas x Wales Bonner collections, the Track Pant emerges this season in an inviting Mystery Brown colorway. This particular variation is knit from soft recycled polyester fabric and features an elasticated waistband. Zippered hand pockets are incorporated onto the sides of the pair, which is finished with Three Stripes detailing along the legs, in addition to Wales Bonner iconography at the front of the left leg and the adidas Trefoil logo on the back.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: WRKS Jogger Washed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: None

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Y Belt Leather Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Y/Project’s Leather Pant is a distinctive style that incorporates an attached, “floating” Y belt at the waist. The wide leg pair is produced in vegan leather and features traditional five-pocket styling. On the back of the silhouette, a leather logo patch is applied to brand the polarizing design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Biker Trousers With Exposed Zips Black Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This new version of GmbH's Biker Trouser is produced in a recycled nylon fabric. The straight leg pair arrives in a black and grey colorway, with contrasting colors on the front and the back. Details include button fastening and a hidden zip fly, belt loops, and side hand pockets, as the stye is then finished with a GmbH logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cavaty Pants Dark Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Cavaty is a technical pant style from J.L-A.L, one that is made from woven nylon, with ripstop mesh panels at the sides of the silhouette. The pair is cut for a classic straight leg fit and features an elastic drawstring waistband that allows you to dial in the fit. Pinned pleats provide the pant with a bit of character, as curved slip-in pockets then extend from the front to the sides of the legs to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Corduroy Loose Cargo Pant Dark Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As with most Gramicci pant styles, the Cargo bottoms are designed to maintain functionality during climbing and other adventurous activities. This particular pair is produced in a stretch corduroy material for freedom of movement and breathability. Cut in a loose fit, the pants have plenty of space to hold maps, pens, and other outdoor-related materials, while carabiners can conveniently be attached to the built-in webbing belt.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Kola Trackpants Brown/Ivory
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Nobody does trackpants like Wales Bonner. This particular pair is produced in a polyester blend fabric, featuring contrasting paneling and an elegant front pleat that allows you to dress the style up a bit. An inner drawstring is incorporated into the elasticated waistband, as pockets emerge at the sides and back of the silhouette. The pant is finished with a small embroidered logo implemented at the front of the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Loose Fit Jeans 2021 Yellow/Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These loose-fitting jeans from Acne Studios are crafted from rigid denim made of cotton. The pair features traditional five-pocket construction, with frayed detailing, a button fly, and belt loops lining the waist. A leather logo patch is incorporated onto the back of the waist to minimally brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Denim Trompe L'oeil Jeans Black/Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A statement piece from the brand's latest collection, the Denim Trompe L'oeil Jeans further exemplify the maison's mastery of couture. The black jeans are adorned with a print of gray denim jeans at the front and back with offset proportions to create the visual effect. The loose-fitting jeans are finished with an Eiffel Tower patch at the waist and a button fly with JPG engraving.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wool Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing from classic skater style, these Wool Pants by Marni come with a branded shoe lace belt for an alternative look. As the name notes, the pair is crafted from virgin wool, while being cut for a straight leg fit with a mid rise. The bottoms are made with front pleats and have side slip pockets as well as back welt pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 70s Cut Mole Grey Exquisite Wool
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This season, Our Legacy's 70s Cut style arrives in Mole Grey Exquisite Wool, crafted from an Italian virgin wool suiting fabric. The pair is high waisted with a boot cut leg and features creased lines, brass rivets, and a zip fly. A logo patch is incorporated onto the back of the waistband to brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P53-WS Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Acronym's take on the active lifestyle silhouette, the P53-WS, is technical wizardry in its purest form. The shell is made from 2-layer GORE-TEX WINDSTOPPER fabric that is designed to combat wind, repel water, and offer loads of breathability with each wear. The lining utilizes military-grade Polartec Alpha Direct fabric that's detailed with brushed fibers to improve ventilation and assist with regulating body temperature. Further specifications include a QLQR® Web Waistband that allows for adjusting the fit on each side, an array of seam and zip pockets, and an adjustable zip hem with embroidered logos.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P15-DS Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: ACRONYM's P15-DS is constructed for daily wear and arrives in a minimal monochrome hue. The technical pants are constructed using Schoeller 3XDRY® fabric that features a wind and water-repellent finish on the exterior with an interior hydrophilic finish that subdues perspiration and moisture, while working to keep your body cool. In addition to the loose fit, tapered cut, and mid-rise exhibited in these breathable and technical trousers, the pants also feature a two-way adjustment belt at the waist to dial in your preferred fit along with five external and three internal pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P30AL-DS Pant Alpha Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P30AL-DS is Acronym's take on cargo pants that's characterized by its drop crotch and loose-fitting silhouette. The utility pants are constructed from hardwearing Schoeller® Dryskin fabric that protects against wind and repels water and features 3XDRY technology that ensures you remain dry. The trousers are finished with the brand's Deep Pockets subsystem, ten external and four internal, along with an adjustable QLQR® Web Waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P47-DS Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P47 arrives in a close-cut silhouette that is emphasized by its technical precision and 4-way stretch capabilities. Minimally detailed, the pants are crafted using heavyweight Schoeller® 3XDRY® Dryskin fabric that boasts abrasion-resistant and water-repellent features. The all-black pants are also adept at moisture management and feature the brand's Deep Pockets subsystem with five external pockets and three internal.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Air Hold Pants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Air Hold Pants are made using INVISTA's Thermolite fabric, which is considerably lightweight, warm, and insulating. As with many And Wander styles, reflective stitching is incorporated to increase nighttime visibility. The pair then features an elasticated waistband with an integrated belt and side zip hand pockets for securely carrying small essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Washed Sweat Pants Charcoal
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Heavy Washed Sweat Pants are part of our most recent collaboration with BAPE and arrive in a muted, monochromatic color with a soft fleece feel. The heavyweight sweats are detailed with woven brand tags at the back pocket, printed logos at the lower leg, and embroidery at the thigh.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Trouser D 09 AW 20 Mahogany
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This midweight polyester pant from Jil Sander is made with an elasticated waistband to ensure a more relaxing overall fit. A pressed crease adds character to the silhouette, which is outfitted with two side slit pockets and two back flap pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pine Pants Choco
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten’s latest collection features a hybrid of unique prints, textures, and androgynous garments that offer a fresh take on contemporary menswear. The Pine Pants are an elevated take on a timeless wardrobe staple, seen here crafted from brown and grey denim and over-dyed to create a unique stain effect that’s synonymous with the Belgian designer’s aesthetics.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twist Seam Cargo Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Twist Seam Cargo Trouser is a distinctive Martine Rose style defined by extra large cargo pockets and seams that twist around to the knee. Cut for a relaxed fit, the pair is made from nylon and lined with cotton, and features adjustable straps at the waist. Additional details include front button fastening, a zip fly, belt loops, and side as well as back pockets. A rubber seasonal branded tab is applied to the waist to subtly mark the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Evergreen Y Belt Jeans Vintage Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Y/Project applies its distinctive touch to the classic jean style, here implementing a polarizing cut-out at the front and a pin buckle belt with logo hardware. The pair arrives in a vintage black wash, with five-pocket styling and a leather logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Washed Sweat Pants Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Heavy Washed Sweat Pants are part of our most recent collaboration with BAPE and arrive in a muted, monochromatic color with a soft fleece feel. The heavyweight sweats are detailed with woven brand tags at the back pocket, printed logos at the lower leg, and embroidery at the thigh.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Washed Sweat Pants Ivory
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Heavy Washed Sweat Pants are part of our most recent collaboration with BAPE and arrive in a muted, monochromatic color with a soft fleece feel. The heavyweight sweats are detailed with woven brand tags at the back pocket, printed logos at the lower leg, and embroidery at the thigh.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Softshell Technical Trousers Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name implies, ROA's Technical Softshell Trousers are crafted from a densely woven nylon shell with a cozy fleece lining. The pants are detailed in a neutral brown colorway and implement adjustable waist cinches to dial in your preferred fit. Storage space is no issue as the lined pants are outfitted with an array of pockets at the seams, rear, and thighs to keep your belongings secure The pair is finished with zippered ventilation openings at the lower leg along with a snap closure, allowing you to adjust the pair to your liking.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cargo Trouser Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: ROA updates the classic cargo style with contrasting paneled inserts along the leg, calve, and cargo pockets to ensure you remain protected wherever you're at. The lined trousers are engineered from a technical poly-cotton twill that features large, slanted open pockets at the front and rear, accessory loops at the hip, and a printed logo at the cargo pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 2010-D-Macs Straight Jeans Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of Diesel denim is defined by strategically-placed cut-outs at the things. Cut for a straight leg fit, the style features traditional five-pocket construction, with button fastening and belt loops lining the waist. A Diesel logo patch is applied to the back of the waistband to brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wool Dress Pants Dark Gray
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These dress pants are produced from a heavyweight wool and polyester blend fabric. Detailed in a monochrome hue with slant and back pockets, the pleated dress pants feature traditional elements such as belt loops, a zip fly, and a slight crop at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Re-Inforced Nylon Cargo Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These heavyweight cargo pants are built with durability in mind, constructed from a densely woven nylon and cotton blend that features a double layer at the rear and knees.  The pair features a textured finish with a vertical weave and is detailed with buckles at the waist to dial in your fit, along with ankle cinch cords to further adjust the shape to your preference. The pants are finished with button-down cargo and back pockets along with a small HS05 label at the rear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reverse Twill Baggy Trouser Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Constructed from densely woven cotton twill, the Reverse Twill Baggy Trouser arrives in a neutral colorway. The loose-fitting trousers are detailed with a lightly brushed texture, silver-toned hardware, and a slight taper at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wool Dress Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These dress pants are produced from a heavyweight wool and polyester blend fabric. Detailed in a monochrome hue with slant and back pockets, the pleated dress pants feature traditional elements such as belt loops, a zip fly, and a slight crop at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hard Twist Denim 5P Pants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Auralee produced this seasonless style with the intention of making denim that maintains the crisp texture of raw denim, even after washing. Made from uneven American cotton yarn, the denim has a rope-dyed brown warp and an undyed, unbleached, raw-edged weft, leading to a crisp texture with natural elastic stretch. Traditional design elements including five-pocket construction, button fastening, and belt loops at the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Printed Jeans Teal/Aqua
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Printed Jeans are one of many standout pieces from Gerrit Jacob’s latest collection. Detailed with his signature airbrushed graphics in an allover print, the wide leg bottoms are finished with side and back pockets, belt loops, and contrast stitching along the seams.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Signature Low Rise Jeans Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Signature Low Rise Jean arrives this season in a classic indigo colorway, defined by a custom sound-wave print that is laser etched into the fabric. To complement, the iconic smiley face and "A" iconography are also printed onto the garment, which is cut from recycled organic cotton denim. The style is designed for a regular fit with a straight leg and detailed with button fastening and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Work Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar draws inspiration from workwear. The Work Pants arrive in a flexible all-black finish that’s detailed with embroidered logos at the hammer loop, and both the back right and extra pocket. The pants are finished with a zip fly closure and feature a woven brand tag bearing the year that Highsnobiety and Coca-Cola Zero Sugar were both founded.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Dungarees Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This collaboration with Coca-Cola Zero Sugar draws inspiration from workwear. Crafted from durable cotton in a jet-black colorway, the dungarees are outfitted with traditional workwear details including adjustable buckles, tool pockets, and a hammer loop. The pair is finished with woven brand patches on the chest and an embroidered Coke Zero logo on the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Nylon Metal Pants Maroon
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pant style from Stone Island is made from the brand's signature Nylon Metal material that boasts a metallic and iridescent look when garment-dyed. The regular-fitting pair features nylon mesh lining and is outfitted with an elasticized waistband and ankle cuffs to allow for minor adjustments to fit and styling. To finish the garment, the iconic Stone Island logo badge is applied to the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Neu York Carpenter Pants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These workwear pants have been garment-dyed in an earthy brown hue and sun-dried so no two pairs are identical. The pants arrive featuring practical details such as a hammer loop at the left leg, extra pocket space, and a zip fly. Crafted from hard-wearing, Japanese cotton, the pants are accented with white contrast stitching and feature an embroidered Neu York logo on the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Marble-Dyed Trousers Maize
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Marble-Dyed Trousers are produced in a durable cotton drill that is garment-dyed to ensure each pair is unique. Cut in a wide-leg fit, these Marni pants feature five-pocket styling, with two hip and back pockets. The style is detailed with a button fastening and belt loops, alongside subtle branding found through a leather logo label on the rear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Utility Cord Easy Pant Sulphur Moss
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Utility Easy Pant is a comfy corduroy style made from a cotton-elastane blend fabric. The relaxed-fitting pair is outfitted with adjustable drawcords at the waist and leg openings to allow for minor alterations to fit and styling. In addition to side hand pockets and back pockets, the garment features a single snap button cargo pocket incorporated onto the left leg. A tonal The North Face logo is embroidered onto the back of the silhouette to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Revol Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P-Revol is an edgy Diesel pant style cut from a technical polyester fabric with a smooth polyurethane coating. Designed for a regular fit with a straight leg, the pair features traditional five-pocket construction, with a button fly and belt loops lining the waist. A logo patch is incorporated onto the back of the waist to minimally brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wide Panel Pant Salt/Rinsed
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving in a clean white colorway, the Wide Panel Pant is defined by its wide, angular panels at the knee, which add reinforcement and point to classic workwear styles. The pair is produced in a midweight cotton fabric that is triple stitched and detailed with tool pockets and a hammer loop. The pant features a loose, voluminous fit for an extra comfortable and fashion-forward wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5-Pocket Jeans Light Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The 5-Pocket Jeans from Maison Margiela’s new seasonal collection arrive in a blue colorway with a vintage stone wash. The pair is outfitted with five pockets and detailed with the house’s clasp fastening as well as the iconic four stitches at the back just below the waistline.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P41-DS Schoeller Dryskin Articulated Cargo Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Technical fabrics and utilitarian details, that’s what Acronym is best known for. Items like the P41-DS Trouser are sure to come in handy for year-round wear, whether you’re out and about around the city or traversing mountain terrain. Abrasion-resistant and water-repellent, the bottoms are made using Schoeller 3XDry Dryskin that allows you to better manage moisture and take advantage of quick-drying properties. The pants are designed to flow along with the natural curvature of the leg, ensuring a comfortable wear no matter the activity. If you’re someone who likes to carry plenty of small accessories, the P41 style is most certainly for you, as you have 10 external pockets and 2 internal pockets to utilize.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Re-Inforced Nylon Cargo Trouser Khaki

A tonal Reebok logo is embroidered onto the left leg to subtly embellish the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Organic Cut Track Pants Anthracite
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Organic Cut Track Pant is an elevated style that blends sportswear and streetwear sensibilities. A contrasting Reebok logo is incorporated onto the left leg to subtly embellish the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reverse Piping Elastic Trouser Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Reverse Piping Trousers are crafted from a dense cotton and nylon blend that has a slight sheen throughout the fabric. The trousers are detailed with reverse piping running down the outside of the leg and feature a drawstring waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sun Dried Canvas Carpenter Pants Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These workwear pants have been garment-dyed in an earthy brown hue and sun-dried so no two pairs are identical. The pants arrive featuring practical details such as a hammer loop at the left leg, extra pocket space, and a zip fly. Crafted from hard-wearing, Japanese cotton, the pants are accented with white contrast stitching and feature a removable logo tag on the right back pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reverse Piping Elastic Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Reverse Piping Trousers are crafted from a dense cotton and nylon blend that has a slight sheen throughout the fabric. The trousers are detailed with reverse piping running down the outside of the leg and feature a drawstring waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sun Dried Canvas Carpenter Pants Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The classic carpenter design gets a garment-dyed makeover in a tonal blue hue that’s been sun-dried so no two pairs are identical. tshirts_and_tops.Name: Contrast Stitch Loose Denim Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This loose-fitting pair of Patta denim is constructed from 15oz mid-heavyweight cotton. Featuring a rinse wash, the style is then detailed with contrasting stitches and branded buttons and rivets. The denim boasts traditional five-pocket construction and is subtly branded with a Patta flag label at the coin pocket, in addition to a leather back patch.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pantalone Loose Pink 31019
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Stone Island’s loose fit pants are crafted from ECONYL® regenerated yarns that are subjected to the brand's unique double-dyeing process, which gives it a rich metallic finish.. Lightweight and easy to match, the pants arrive with zip side pockets, an additional back pocket, and the brand’s signature badge on the left leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Gocar Cargo Lizard
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The future of the cargo pant is here, thanks to contemporary-minded label Entire Studios. Offering a standout look, the Gocar model is made with two large cargo pockets on each leg, with metal snap closure for added security. The pair is produced in cotton and nylon poplin with a distinctive enzyme wash, cut in a regular fit with a wide leg. Instead of traditional belt loops, the pant is outfitted with a drawstring waist that allows you to dial in the fit, while a drawstring hem makes way for minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Profile Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Profile is Noon Goons' take on the classic black dress pant. Produced in a polyester-rayon blend fabric, the pair is cut for a relaxed fit, finished with a center pressed crease. Additional design details include blind hook and eye closure, belt loops, and side hand pockets as well as back welt pockets with button closure. A small Noon Goons tag is incorporated onto the back of the waistband to subtly brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Impala Pant Camel
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by the past, the Impala Pant is made from a houndstooth fabric milled in Japan. It features very light lining through the thigh, with traditional design elements such as hook and eye closure at the waistband, a zip fly, belt loops, and side hand pockets as well as back welt pockets. The straight leg style is then finished with a hit of embroidery implemented at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Panelled Straight-Leg Jeans Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This distinctive pair of jeans from Winnie New York is made using contrasting patches of denim to create a workwear-inspired look. Offering a straight-leg fit with a high rise, the bottoms feature traditional five-pocket styling, detailed with metal rivets, button fastening, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Gocar Cargo Onyx
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The future of the cargo pant is here, thanks to contemporary-minded label Entire Studios. Instead of traditional belt loops, the pant is outfitted with a drawstring waist that allows you to dial in the fit, while a drawstring hem makes way for minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hard Cargo Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Two styles in one, the Hard Cargo by Entire Studios features a zip-off leg that allows you to convert the bottoms into shorts. Crafted from a cotton heavy canvas, the pair is outfitted with multiple pockets running down the legs, in addition to traditional side hand pockets and two back pockets. The Hard Cargo features a regular-fitting waist and a wide leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hard Cargo Carbon

tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Marni trousers are constructed from a lightweight virgin wool fabric, with woven cotton-nylon lining. The straight-leg pair is defined by a single cargo pocket on the left leg, paired with slanting hand pockets as well as a back button flap pocket. Additional design details include button fastening and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twisted Cut Jeans Two Split Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: As the name suggests, this style is defined by a distinctive twisted leg seam. The straight leg pair is made from a two-tone 13oz denim originating from Italy and further detailed with a raw fringed hem. The jeans feature traditional five pocket construction and button fastening, with belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Rider Cut Jeans Punk Wash
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This version of the Rider Cut Jean is produced in a heavily washed 13oz Italian cotton denim. It features traditional five pocket construction, with a high waist and a slightly flared leg. To brand the style, a suede logo patch is incorporated onto the back waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wide Panel Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Wide Panel Pant is generally featured heavily in Carhartt WIP’s seasonal collections, offered in a series of neutral colorways. The brand utilizes its signature Marshall canvas on this pair, which is triple stitched at vital stress points as a nod to prototypical workwear styles. Utilitarian details include tool pockets and a hammer loop, making the Wide Panel Pant perfect for work and play. The pair is set off by the wide panel at the knee in a tonal application.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pine Pants Pink
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Dries van Noten’s latest collection features a hybrid of unique prints, textures, and androgynous garments that offer a fresh take on contemporary menswear. The Pine Pants are a perfect example of the Belgian designer’s mastery of dyed and bleached garments. The pair features a loose fit with five pockets as well as a front button closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Hama Cotton Jersey Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Hama is a comfy Dries van Noten pant style produced in a midweight cotton jersey fabric. This particular pair arrives in a versatile black colorway that caters to repeat wear, featuring side hand pockets as well as back pockets. A drawstring is incorporated into the waistband to allow you to dial in a more precise fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pepper Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Pepper is a definitively wide-leg pant style by Dries van Noten. This season, the bottoms arrive in a lightweight cupro-cotton blend, detailed with front pleats. Addition design elements include button fastening and a zip fly, belt loops, and side as well as back pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wide Panel Pant Rinsed Hamilton Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving in Carhartt’s signature Hamilton Brown colorway, the Wide Panel Pant is defined by its wide, angular panels at the knee, which add reinforcement and point to classic workwear styles. The pair is produced in a midweight cotton fabric that is triple stitched and detailed with tool pockets and a hammer loop. The pant features a loose, voluminous fit for an extra comfortable and fashion-forward wear.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Panel Pant Deep Purple
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This edition of the Panel Pant is produced in midweight powder-touch nylon with a water-repellent finish. Cut in a straight fit, the Affix bottoms feature three-pocket styling, with two crescent side pockets and one oversized coin pocket within the right side pocket. The style is detailed with custom snap fastening and wide format, angled belt loops.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Padded Pants Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from their love of nature, Moncler and Salehe Bembury have joined forces to create a collection that sees Bembury’s ideology infused with Moncler’s mountaineering heritage. Crafted from jacquard woven nylon and featuring a drawstring waistband with zip pockets, these cozy pants also have a down lining with quilted sides.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 501 Original Stonewash Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: To celebrate Levi’s and 150 years of its 501 jeans, we’ve teamed up with the renowned brand to release our own pair and pay tribute to years of innovation. Limited to only 150 pairs with each numbered on the inside label, the jeans arrive in a classic stonewash finish with a contrasting HS logo embroidered below the right pocket. On the back, you’ll find a woven QR code patch that leads to a video explaining our affinity with Levi’s iconic and timeless designs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Straight Leg Sweatpant Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic sweatpant. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Heavy Sweatpant is perfect for lounging around the house and casual outings with friends, being crafted from a brushed-back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The cozy style features an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord that allows you to dial in the fit and a single back patch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Description: Fancify your look with the Tailored Trousers from Acne Studios. The classic dress pant arrives in a versatile grey colorway, made from a soft wool blend. The style features concealed fastening, belt loops lining the waist, and side hand pockets as well as back welt pockets. Reach for these for all those dressy occasions from season to season.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Felted Wool Suit Pants Dark Grey

As the name suggests, the pair is predominantly constructed from wool, featuring a wide cut and low rise. The dark grey style is made with front pleats, belt loops, side adjusters, and a classic four-pocket design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Denim Cargo Pants Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A standout pant style, this Marni pair is produced in coated blue denim with a bleached effect wash.
