More traditional design elements include button closure and a zip fly, as well as belt loops at the waist, one of which is subtly branded with a small Marni logo.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P46-DS Schoeller Dryskin Vent Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P46-DS is a flight suit-inspired vent pant produced in a nylon and elastane blend. The relaxed-fitting pair arrives in a stealthy black colorway with four mesh-lined concealed zip vents for enhanced breathability. Like many Acronym styles, the P46-DS is outfitted with the brand’s Deep Pockets system including eight pockets total, six external and two internal, designed for carrying personal items like your phone, wallet, and other everyday accessories.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1955 501 Jeans Silent Spring Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Slam Jam’s second collaboration with Levi’s serves to celebrate the American brand’s 150th anniversary. This pair of 1955 501 jeans find Slam Jam exploring multiple intersections of old America through 19th-century-inspired items that are now a part of the brand’s archive. Made in Japan, this commemorative model is defined by a silver silk pattern screenprint applied to each leg. Aside from that standout detail, the denim is made with more traditional features including five-pocket styling, button fastening, and belt loops at the waist. A Levi’s logo label is incorporated onto the back of the waist, while small Slam Jam and Levi’s branded tags are stitched to the back pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P41-DS Schoeller Dryskin Articulated Cargo Trouser Raf Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Technical fabrics and utilitarian details, that’s what Acronym is best known for. Items like the P41-DS Trouser are sure to come in handy for year-round wear, whether you’re out and about around the city or traversing mountain terrain. Abrasion-resistant and water-repellent, the bottoms are made using Schoeller 3XDry Dryskin that allows you to better manage moisture and take advantage of quick-drying properties. The pants are designed to flow along with the natural curvature of the leg, ensuring a comfortable wear no matter the activity. If you’re someone who likes to carry plenty of small accessories, the P41 style is most certainly for you, as you have 10 external pockets and 2 internal pockets to utilize.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Priya Trouser
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Since launching in 2018, Ahluwalia has become well-known for crafting unique patchworked garments that blend the designer’s heritage with vintage and various textiles. For its latest collection, Ahluwalia comes through with a pair of lightweight trousers for both formal and casual settings alike. The trousers feature pleats at the front along with side and back pockets and is finished with contrasting stripes akin in line with the brand’s signature designs.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Relaxed Fit Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A comfy pant style, the Relaxed Fit Trouser is made from lightweight polyester with contrasting side panels for a standout look. An elasticated waist increases overall comfort, while drawstring ankle cuffs allow you to make minor adjustments to styling. The pair is outfitted with side zip pockets as well as a back patch pocket and minimally branded with a seasonal Acne Studios monogram flag label.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Le De-Nimes Suno Silver
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This isn’t your average pair of Jeans. Jacquemus reinvents the classic pant style by utilizing unbleached cotton denim that features a shimmering silver film finish. The style does incorporate more traditional design elements, however, including five-pocket styling, button fastening, and belt loops at the waist. A bootcut model, the jeans are cut in a straight fit with a mid rise and finished with a paper logo patch on the back waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P23Q-DS Schoeller Dryskin Cargo Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P23Q-DS is a classic Acronym pant style redesigned with optimal storage. Crafted from a technical nylon blend using Schoeller 3XDry Dryskin fabric technology, the bottoms feature 10 exterior pockets and 2 interior pockets, including TensionZip cargo pockets and Acronym Deep pockets, to ensure you have plenty of space for carrying all your essentials. The pair is made with a beltless drawcord waist that cinches down, cut in a wide fit with a drop crotch and layered, low-profile cuff.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P48-CH Micro Twill Pleated Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Designed for all situations, the P48-CH is a luxurious and supremely comfortable pant style crafted from a technical cotton and nylon blend using Schoeller Shape 3XDry fabric technology to make it water-repellent, moisture-wicking, fast-drying, and highly breathable. The pair is cut for a wide fit and features a double-pleated front, integrated web belt, and shock cord adjustable hems. As with most Acronym bottoms, the style incorporates a number of pockets including six on the exterior and four on the interior for optimal storage.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 1901 501 Jeans Dark Indigo Flat Finish
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Levi’s 501 dates all the way back to the 1800s, with the 1901 variation originally being referred to as overalls. Made with a cinch back and buttons along the waist that allowed you to attach suspenders, the style welcomed the addition of a second back pocket, adhering to consumer demand and men’s fashion at that time. The pair features classic five-pocket styling, with other traditional design elements including a button fly and the Levi’s logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Penny Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Built for comfort, the Penny Pants are constructed from a breathable, overdyed linen blend and feature an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawstring that allows you to dial in the fit. Belt loops are implemented as well to give you the option to add a belt to the mix whenever the mood strikes. The neutral-colored bottoms are cut in a loose fit with a mid rise that further enhances the overall comfort level.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cargo Trousers
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Arriving with a generous fit, inspired by baggy cargo pants that were popular in the ‘90s, the fit of these pants can be customized by the wearer through drawstrings on the hem of each leg. Cargo pockets on both legs offer extra carrying space, with the right pocket also including contrast KENZO branding.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Chino-Work-Fsc Trousers Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from classic chino pants, this contemporary Diesel style is produced from 100% lyocell with denim accents. The silhouette is cut in a loose fit with a straight leg, featuring belt loops and side hand pockets as well as two back pockets. A distinctive alternative to your standard pair of chinos, the Diesel style elevates a wardrobe staple.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.0 Technical Trousers Right Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The 5.0 Trouser is a standout technical style from Korean brand Post Archive Faction, perfect for outdoor adventure and urban exploration alike. Cut in a straight fit, the pair features a cutting line design from the waist to the knee, characterized by a three-dimensional pattern at the knee for increased volume and ease of movement. More traditional details include belt loops at the waist, a zip fly, and front and back pockets, as the bottoms arrive in neutral colorways for easy matching from season to season.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Drill Trouser Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by the function-first design of workwear, these pants arrive with a wide, straight fit. Arriving in neutral colorways, the classic four-pocket design features silver-toned, branded hardware. The pants are crafted from hard-wearing, organic drill cotton with a matching jacket also available.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Argy Cargo Trousers Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P-Argy is a contemporary update to the classic cargo style. Cut in a regular fit with a straight leg, the pair is constructed from a durable double-twisted twill in organic cotton and treated with a light rinse wash. The utility-inspired trouser features belt loops and adjustable buckles at the waist, in addition to drawstring hems that allow you to make minor alterations to styling. Diesel’s oval D logo is incorporated onto the back of the pair to minimally brand the silhouette.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Sports-Mon Trousers Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An elevated sportswear style, the P-Sports-Mon is constructed from jacquard weave nylon with a vintage-effect finish. A subtle all-over monogram motif brands the pair throughout, with additional iconography emerging on the back in the form of an oval D logo patch. The silhouette is cut to a regular fit with a wide leg, featuring an elasticated drawstring waist that allows you to dial in a precise and comfortable fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Chart Trousers Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The P-Chart is a wide leg silhouette from Diesel, one that is cut from a substantial cotton canvas that is garment-dyed to give it a dirty look. The regular-fitting pair is styled with horizontal panels and snap button waist adjusters, while also featuring more traditional design elements like button fastening, a zip fly, and belt loops. Pockets are implemented at the front and back, as the brand’s signature oval D logo is incorporated onto the left front pocket to subtly brand the pair.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Shadow Plaid Side-Tie Trousers Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Inspired by plaid suiting fabric from the 1940s, these Bode bottoms represent a historical reproduction of a classic ombre shadow plaid material evocative of mid-century American workwear. The straight leg pair is updated with elevated design attributes, namely side-tie detailing which brings a distinctive element to the silhouette. More traditional features are incorporated by way of button closure, two side hand pockets, and two back buttoned flap pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Fleece Pant White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Highsnobiety Fleece Pant is a classic sweatpant style produced in a heavyweight cotton fabric. Featuring a full fit with a slightly tapered leg, the garment is made with an elasticated waistband and ankle cuffs for optimal comfort, with an adjustable drawstring at the waist that allows you to dial in a precise fit. Pockets are implemented at the side seams and back, as the pair is subtly branded with a small Highsnobiety flag label. Note: The colorways for the Heavy Fleece Pant don’t match those of the Heavy Fleece Hoodie.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Heavy Sweat Cork
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Entire Studios is known to elevate the simple, with contemporary updates to traditional silhouettes like the classic sweatpant. Offered in neutral colors for effortless matching, the ES Heavy Sweatpant is perfect for lounging around the house and casual outings with friends, being crafted from a brushed back cotton fleece that is treated with an enzyme wash for a more distinctive look. The cozy style features an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord that allows you to dial in the fit and a single back patch pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Pants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Wet Pant is a standout Entire Studios garment, one that offers us a glimpse into the future of fashion. Cut in a regular fit with a wide leg, the pair is produced in 100% polyurethane leather to deliver a glossy finish that ensures these bottoms catch the eye. The style features traditional five-pocket construction with side and back pockets, as well as standard button closure with a zip fly.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twill Trousers Black 1
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Acne Studios’ Twill Trouser is a versatile pant geared towards dressier occasions. Arriving in a neutral black colorway for effortless matching, the pair is cut to a regular fit and length, made from an organically grown cotton. Traditional design details include button closure and a zip fly, belt loops at the waist, and side hand pockets as well as back welt pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Madur Corduroy Trouser Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A crisp pair of corduroy bottoms can provide the switch-up you’ve been needing this cold weather season. RANRA (formerly known as Arnar Már Jónsson) comes through accordingly with its latest collection, as the Madur is a cotton blend corduroy style, available here in a versatile beige colorway that’s easy to match. Cut in a regular fit with a straight leg, the pants are made with pockets on the front and back, while being embellished with an intricately embroidered logo on the bottom of the right leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Moleskin Cargo Pant Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Designed with ample pocket space to carry the day’s essentials, these pants from the Highsnobiety brand deliver the practicality of cargo pants with an elevated, textured finish. Produced entirely from a mid-weight cotton moleskin, the densely woven fabric has a soft hand with a feel that is comparable to suede or fur. This pair is outfitted with two large cargo pockets on either leg, the left of which includes a small logo tag, along with additional front and back pockets. To adjust the fit, buckles have been included at the waist along with ankle cinch cords to further personalize the look and feel of this relaxed-fitting, straight-leg pant. For a full moleskin outfit, there is a matching shirt also available from Highsnobiety.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Generate Straight Jeans Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Diesel’s Generate Jean is a moto-inspired silhouette outfitted with a series of zippers for a biker-style aesthetic. This particular pair is executed in a mid-blue wash with minor abrasions to deliver a natural, well-worn look. Constructed from non-stretch cotton denim, the jeans are reinforced at the knees and incorporate zippers at the cuffs that allow for minor adjustments to the look and fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P44-DS Cargo Pant Grey
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A newer, looser version of the P24A, the P44-DS is a semi-oversized style with a wide spectrum body shape and a straight leg. As with most Acronym bottoms, it’s all about the pockets, as the pair features the brand’s signature raid pocket layout with 14 pockets, 10 external and 4 internal. Adjustability is also key, as the P44-DS is made with an integrated rapid adjust split-drawcord waistband and internal drawcords in the cuffs, making way for minor alterations to the look and fit. Heavy-duty Dryskin nylon construction ensures these pants can handle whatever comes their way year after year.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P43-GT Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A dual-purpose pant, the P43-GT is capable of functioning as a breathable, fully waterproof storm overpant, in addition to being worn on its own on a daily basis. Predominantly constructed using nylon, the pair is made with waterproof and windproof Gore-Tex Pro technology to enhance breathability and minimize moisture buildup in extreme conditions. Alterations to the look and fit can be made by way of an integrated web waistband with mil-spec webbing, removable release tab, and excess web retainer loop, as well as a rapid adjust drawcord hem with lace hook tethers for shoe coverage in inclement weather. The P43-GT is cut in a semi-oversized fit with a wide spectrum body shape and a straight leg, and features an array of secure zip pockets for carrying small essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cotton Nylon Elastic Pants Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Designed for wear all year long, these Highsnobiety bottoms are produced in a heavyweight cotton and nylon blend that is resistant to water, making them a go-to option for rainy days. The style is offered in neutral colors for easy matching, featuring side seam pockets and an adjustable drawstring waist that allows you to dial in a more precise and comfortable fit.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Five-Pocket Jeans Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Five-Pocket Jeans from Maison Margiela’s SS22 collection arrive in a classic blue colorway with a medium wash. As the name notes, the pair is outfitted with five pockets and detailed with the house’s hook and eye closure as well as the brand’s iconic four stitches at the back just below the waistline..

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Drawstring Leg Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Maison Margiela’s AW21 collection is indicative of the times, largely drawing from the chaotic nature much of the world has been subjected to in recent months and years. At the forefront, the seasonal assortment includes traditional pieces with iconic parts noticeably altered to deliver reborn styles for a transformed wardrobe. Featured in the latest drop is a comfy pant option in the Drawstring Leg Trousers. As the name suggests, the bottoms are outfitted with drawstrings at the ankles, as well as around the waist, allowing you to better adjust the fit. The flannel pants are then branded with Margiela’s M-embroidered button at the front flap pocket — a signifier of the ICONS collection — in addition to its iconic four-stitches moniker on the back. For both casual and semi-formal occasions, the Drawstring Leg Trousers are a luxe high fashion option with a cozy feel.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Recycled Sports Trousers
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Lightweight sporting trousers featuring a paneled polyamide/nylon construction. Modeled after the design of ski salopettes, the piece comes complete with an elasticated waist and ankle cuffs. With two slip pockets over the front and a buttoned flap pocket over the back, the trousers feature signature tricolor branding along the side seam, and a rubberized stamp above the ankle cuff.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Third Cut Digital Denim Print Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to classic straight-leg jean styles, this pair of trousers from Our Legacy has been elevated thanks to its subtle details. Most noticeably, the bottoms showcase a distinctive trompe l'oeil vintage denim print. On the back, you will find a translucent belt patch and two reinforced pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crinkled Sailor Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Not your average dress pant, Our Legacy’s Sailor Trouser is produced in a unique viscose and polyester blend fabric that has a distinctive crinkled effect. The wide leg pair is made with an elasticated waistband, while still featuring traditional belt loops to offer a classic look. Offered in a versatile black colorway, the silhouette boasts a flat front and pressed creases, as these bottoms excel on dressier occasions.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Le Pantalon Piccinni Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Le Pantalon Piccinni is a high-fashion take on the classic black dress pant. Made from virgin wool with cotton-polyester lining, the soft tailored style is cut for a loose fit with a mid rise. Design elements include hidden zip and button fastening, double belt loops, and slanted hand pockets as well as a back welt pocket. A D-ring attachment is connected to one of the front belt loops to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Jean Printed With 325 Indigo
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Jean Paul Gaultier distorts the classic jean silhouette by flipping the legs inside out. The straight leg pair arrives in a versatile indigo colorway, featuring traditional five-pocket styling, but fastening, and belt loops lining the waist. Logo detailing is printed onto the legs to definitively brand the polarizing style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cut-Out Jeans Rinsed Black/Rust
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Y/Project is known for its distinctive denim styles like the Cut-Out Jean, which features a unique cut-out detail at the front of the silhouette. The pair is made from 100% cotton and designed for a wide leg fit. To brand the jean, a leather logo patch is incorporated onto the back of the waistband.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 2010 D-Macs Jeans Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of Diesel denim is outfitted with a metal oval D buckle that ultimately defines the style. Offering a straight leg fit, the jeans showcase a washed effect, with traditional five-pocket construction, a zip fly, and belt loops lining the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Reverse Twill Baggy Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Constructed from densely woven cotton twill, the Reverse Twill Baggy Trouser arrives in a neutral colorway. The loose-fitting trousers are detailed with a lightly brushed texture, silver-toned hardware, and a slight taper at the hem.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Third Cut Digital Rust Denim
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to classic wide leg jean styles, this pair of trousers from Our Legacy is elevated thanks to its subtle details. Most noticeably, the bottoms showcase a distinctive digital print that draws inspiration from a collection of vintage denim designs. On the back of the pair, you will find a translucent belt patch and two reinforced pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sweatpants Brown
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This season, Bode elevates the classic sweatpant, delivering a more luxe, contemporary option. Produced in heavyweight cotton jersey, the relaxed-fitting pair is outfitted with an elasticated waistband for optimal comfort, side seam pockets, and a single back patch pocket. A tonal hit of embroidery is incorporated onto the back pocket to subtly brand the style.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Water-Repellent Cotton Trousers Midnight
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Jil Sander comes through with a technical water-repellent pant that’s outfitted with numerous pockets for proper storage on the go. Made from textured and washed cotton, the style comes with a belted waist that eliminates the need for a traditional belt. Side zip pockets and back jet pockets with hidden zip closure then ensure you have plenty of room for carrying your everyday essentials.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cargo Pant Silver Sage
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These C.P. Company cargos arrive for the new season in an enticing Silver Sage colorway. Made from cotton, the relaxed-fitting pair is outfitted with a cargo pocket at each leg, in addition to side hand pockets as well as back pockets. Adjustable tabs are incorporated at the ankle cuff to allow for minor alterations to styling.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Primo Tape Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Primo Tap Pant is an elevated take on the classic cargo style. Cut for a relaxed fit, the pair features a nylon shell and cotton lining, with an elasticated drawstring waistband that allows you to dial in the fit. In addition to side hand pockets and back pockets, the silhouette is outfitted with flap patch pockets at the thighs. The pant is further embellished with calf strap detail.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Sako Trouser Deep Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A contemporary update to the classic leather pant, the Sako is produced in a faux leather fabric with a light grain finish. The straight leg pair arrives this season in an inviting Deep Blue colorway, with panel detailing at the knee and a suede logo patch at the back waist. The style features traditional five-pocket construction and a metal button and zip closure.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crease-Dye Duty Pant Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This edition of the Duty Pant is produced in a midweight cotton twill that is crease-dyed to ensure each pair is unique to itself. Cut in a straight fit, the Affix bottoms feature four-pocket styling, with two hip and back pockets. The style is detailed with custom snap fastening and wide format belt loops, and subtly branded with utility embroidery at the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Padded Pants Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Drawing inspiration from their love of nature, Moncler and Salehe Bembury have joined forces to create a collection that sees Bembury’s ideology infused with Moncler’s mountaineering heritage. Crafted from jacquard woven nylon and featuring a drawstring waistband with zip pockets, these cozy pants also have a down lining with quilted sides.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 5.0+ Technical Pants Right Green
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The 5.0+ Technical Pant Right is made using a lightweight and stretchable cotton-nylon blend fabric, with a comfortable elasticated waistband. Distinctive shades in the pocket lining provide a pop of color when unzipped, as mesh fabric is utilized on the interior for enhanced ventilation.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Vintage Denim Straight Leg Pant Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Vintage Denim Pant from Guess is characterized by a distinctive hand stained treatment throughout. Cut for a straight fit with a mid rise, the pair features traditional five-pocket construction made from 100% cotton. Details include button fastening and belt loops at the waist, as the style is branded with a vintage Guess logo implemented at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Bottom Closure Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bottom Closure Trouser is a cotton canvas pant style from Winnie’s latest seasonal collection. It arrives in a versatile black colorway for effortless matching, detailed with a pleated front and button tabs at the ankles cuffs. Concealed fastening creates a more streamlined look, as the pair is outfitted with button side pockets as well as two back pockets.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Y Belt Arc Jeans Faded Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Y/Project applies its distinctive touch to the classic jean style, here implementing a polarizing cut-out at the front and a pin buckle belt with logo hardware. The pair arrives in a faded black wash, with five-pocket styling and a leather logo patch incorporated onto the back of the waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Y Belt Leather Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Y/Project’s Leather Pant is a distinctive style that incorporates an attached, “floating” Y belt at the waist. The wide leg pair is produced in vegan leather and features traditional five-pocket styling. On the back of the silhouette, a leather logo patch is applied to brand the polarizing design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Chalk Selvedge Utility Jeans White
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Maison Margiela jeans are produced in 100% cotton and showcase a distinctive chalky look. The pair is cut in a relaxed fit with a straight leg and comes with the maison’s lace belt tied around the waist. Utilitarian details emerge in the form of a tool pocket and hammer loop.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: 501 Original Fit Indigo Stonewash
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An iconic style, the Levi’s 501 is the blueprint for virtually every pair of jeans, dating all the way back to 1873. The silhouette is cut with a straight leg for a timeless look. Offered in an array of washes, the 501 features classic five-pocket construction, woven with a hint of stretch. Subtle details include a leather logo patch incorporated onto the back waist and a Levi’s flag label at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Easy Pleated Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A cozy update to the traditional dress trouser, Lemaire’s Easy Pleated Plant is constructed from light cotton twill with a soft hand that is slightly shiny. The pair is cut for a relaxed fit with a mid rise, featuring a single pleat below the elasticated waistband. Additional details include an interior drawstring and a button fly with corozo buttons, in addition to welt pockets incorporated onto the sides and back of the bottoms.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Forager Pants Olive Slub
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A standout Story mfg. style, the Forager Pant is the spawn of the brand’s forager bag and lush pants. The pair is big and slouchy with a darted taper at the hem, produced in 100% naturally dyed organic cotton. Forager pockets are incorporated onto each leg, implemented in addition to the side hand pockets and back flap pocket. The waist is fit with button fastening and belt loops, as well as an external drawstring.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Cropped Straight Leg Trousers Beige
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Cropped Straight Leg Trouser is a casual pant style you can wear all year long. Crafted from cotton, the pair arrives in a neutral beige colorway for effortless matching, featuring an elasticated waistband, concealed fly and button fastening, and functional side and back pockets. As the name of the style notes, the silhouette is cropped with a straight leg and a mid rise.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Crackle Leather Flare Pant Jet Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This beiged-out Guess pant is produced in 100% leather with hand distressing. It features a flare fit with a relaxed rise and traditional five-pocket construction. To brand the pair, a vintage Guess logo is applied to the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Ripstop Cargo Pant Rinsed Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These Carhartt cargos are made from lightweight cotton Columbia ripstop that is rinsed for softness. The style is cut in a regular fit with a low waist, featuring numerous patch pockets throughout, pointing to the pant’s military influence. Details include a double layer at the knee, belt loops, and drawstring cuffs that allow for minor adjustments to styling. The pair is finished with a woven Carhartt label applied to the right leg.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Twill Stretch Cargo Pants Total Eclipse Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: This pair of C.P. Company cargos is cut in a loose fit from a stretchy cotton fabric that is garment-dyed to create increased chromatic depth and intensity throughout. The style features reinforced belt loops, multiple pockets including slanted hand pockets, back flap pockets, and twin cargo pockets, and the brand’s signature lens detail incorporated at the left thigh.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Texture Nylon Pants Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Crafted from lightweight Japanese nylon fabric, this casual legwear style is characterized by the textured finish of its fabric which is caused by a heat process. The loose-fit style has side seam pockets along with two back pockets with a small flag label on the left side. An elastic waist with an internal drawstring enhances overall comfort and lets you dial in the proper fit. This pair of pants arrive along with a matching shirt jacket in the latest Highsnobiety collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: GP Faux Leather Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Give your look a punk rock edge with the GP Faux Leather Pant from Noon Goons. Cut for a slim fit, the all-black style features classic five-pocket construction, with a tack button closure fly and a tack button closure waistband. The devil is in the details, as branding emerges by way of the rivets, a leather patch on the back of the waist, and a small woven flag tag label incorporated into the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: P-Koll-H3 Tights Light Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Mimicking the look of denim trousers, the P-Koll-H3 is a distinctive tight style cut from fluid lycra. It is defined by a standout trompe l'oeil print with signature "tiger fraying" from Diesel’s new seasonal collection.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Five-Pocket Twisted Tapered Jeans Blue Rigid
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A standout Trussardi style, these jeans are defined by the brand’s original off-center topstitching, which gives the silhouette a twisted appearance. The pair is produced in a blue-colored pure cotton denim, with metal rivets, zip fastening and a logo button, and logo detailing at the back waist. Featuring traditional five-pocket construction, the jeans are cut with a tapered leg to deliver a timeless look.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: D-Pend Jeans Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Diesel’s D-Pend Jean is defined by a low cut-off waistband and frayed detailing to the pockets, equating to a decidedly contemporary look. Featuring a light wash, the pair is cut to a regular fit with a straight leg for an easy wear that is timeless. Traditional design elements include five pocket styling, a button fly, and belt loops at the waist, as the style is minimally branded with a logo flag at the fifth pocket and an embroidered D logo at the back right pocket.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Boucle Jersey Trousers Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: These luxe Trussardi dress pants are expertly crafted from a soft, solid-color boucle jersey, featuring a tailored cut with a medium waist. Arriving in a versatile black colorway for effortless matching, the pair is finished with a central pleat and a cuff at the ankle, back welt pockets, and concealed front fastening. Offering a decidedly timeless look, the Trussardi Boucle Trousers are sure to be at your disposal for years to come.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Formal Moto Cut Trouser Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: An edgy, moto-inspired style, the Formal Moto Cut Trouser is executed in a Chinese faux leather fabric with a noticeable sheen. The stealthy all-black pair is cut in a relaxed, loose fit with a slight taper and higher rise, offering a timeless look that is sure to be in rotation for years to come. Details include belt loops, a zip fly, and five pockets, as the silhouette is finished with an embossed Our Legacy patch at the back waist.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Bjarkan Ripstop Trouser Wren
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Bjarkan is an elevated sportswear-inspired style from RANRA (formerly known as Arnar Már Jónsson), one that is produced in a lightweight micro ripstop with cotton poplin inserts. Feathery and breathable, the regular-fitting pair is outfitted with an elasticated waistband and drawcords at the waist and hem that make way for minor adjustments to styling and the overall fit. Pockets are implemented at each side seam, as well as a single option on the back to complete the design.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Gadget Pant Black
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Designed to hold your essentials, while maintaining functionality during climbing and other adventurous activities, the aptly-named Gadget Pant is made with large wraparound pockets that extend from the front to the back. These Gramicci bottoms are constructed from a highly durable organic cotton twill fabric that is washed to give it a vintage look and soft hand feel. A flexible waistband with the brand’s easy-adjust belt increases overall comfort, as the pair is outfitted with a branded D-ring attachment that allows you to conveniently carry keys and other similar items.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Wool Twill Trousers Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: A good pair of navy trousers is a versatile must-have for any wardrobe. This pleated style by Maison Margiela is produced in wool twill, featuring turned-up hems and the house’s hook and eye closure. Belt loops allow you to go with or without a belt, as the style is finished with the iconic Margiela four stitches moniker at the back. Keep these handy for all those semi-formal and formal occasions for years to come.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Alvan Denim Trousers Navy
tshirts_and_tops.Description: The Alvan Trouser is a signature style from GmbH, outfitted with the Berlin-based brand’s trademark double front zips. This particular pair is produced in 100% organic cotton, featuring classic 5-pocket denim styling. Anything but your average denim, though, the Alvan is finished with a GmbH-branded leather patch implemented at the back waistband. The pant style is unisex, primed and ready to bring a playful edge to anyone’s wardrobe.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Seamless Pants Light Taupe
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Lemaire’s Seamless Pants are made in Italy from a heavy cotton with a dense, satin-like texture. Offering a regular fit with a mid rise and tapered, slightly rounded leg, the pair is detailed with denim-inspired elements ranging from a back yoke and metal zipper, rivets, and studs, to classic five-pocket styling. The pants are offered in a neutral colorway that ensures repeat wear this season and beyond.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Mens Straight Leg Utility Pant Amparo Blue
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Heron Preston’s creative partnership with Calvin Klein extends to Fall 2021 with a new collection of seasonless styles, many of which are gender neutral. Preston continues to reimagine signature CK pieces while telling the brand’s story through a new lens, delivering reinterpreted essentials sourced from more sustainable fabrics. Ranging from fleece and denim to outerwear and underwear, these everyday items are meant to serve as a new uniform for the style conscious consumer, featuring subtle details that elevate classic Calvin Klein silhouettes. Orange stitching is implemented as a signature element on the streetwear designer’s CK garments, featured here on the Straight Leg Utility Pant. Boasting a reinforced double knee, the bottoms are outfitted with additional workwear details including a tool pocket with a welt opening and orange box stitch.

tshirts_and_tops.Name: Logo Fleece Staples Pants Acorn
tshirts_and_tops.Description: Offered in a selection of neutral colorways, the Logo Fleece Staples Pants are produced in a 410gsm heavyweight brushed fleece that is pigment dyed, featuring an elasticated waist and cuffs to ensure a comfy wear. The Highsnobiety mini arch logo is implemented on the left leg to brand the pants and round out the design details. The tonal bottoms are part of our staples collection that provides fans of HS with elevated basics in neutral colors that allow for easy matching. They can be paired with high fashion threads, streetwear staples, and everything in between so you have plenty of ways to let your personal style shine through.
